ot%3BWhat%20has%20happened%20is%20that%20the%20ground%20support%20computer%20doing%20this%20function%20has%20withheld%20the%20launch%20given%20the%20anomaly%20observed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ISRO%20chairman%20added%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20agency%20was%20immediately%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20anomaly%20and%20moved%20the%20launch%20to%2010%20am%2C%20which%20is%20when%20the%20test%20was%20successfully%20conducted%20and%20smiles%20came%20back%20on%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20ISRO%20scientists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EKudos%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FISRO%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ISRO%3C%2Fa%3E%2Cfor%20successfully%20accomplishing%20maiden%20Test%20Vehicle%20Flight%20TV-D1.%3Cbr%3E%20This%20is%20the%20first%20step%20in%20the%20last%20leg%20of%20journey%20towards%20India's%20Crewed%20Human%20Spacecraft%20mission%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGaganyaan%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Gaganyaan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20enabling%20milieu%20provided%20by%20PM%20Sh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ISRO%3C%2Fa%3E%20achieving%20one%3Cbr%3E%201%2F2%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FydL3InvwUV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FydL3InvwUV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh%20(%40DrJitendraSingh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrJitendraSingh%2Fstatus%2F1715589322102210728%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-mission-test-flight-live-updates-live-news-isro-to-carry-out-first-test-today-4501625%5C%22%3Esuccessful%20launch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Somanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20monitoring%20anomaly%20in%20the%20system.%20We%20could%20identify%20and%20rectify%20it%20very%20fast.%20It%20took%20some%20time%20to%20refill%20the%20gases%20and%20once%20that%20was%20completed%2C%20the%20team%20went%20through%20the%20proper%20automatic%20launch%20sequence%20which%20checked%20the%20entire%20health%20of%20the%20vehicle%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20our%20team%20could%20understand%20an%20anomaly%2C%20rectify%20it%2C%20and%20come%20back%20as%20fast.%20Congratulations%20to%20everybody.%20It%20is%20a%20big%20training%20for%20everybody%20here%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20Gaganyaan%20programme...happy%20that%20the%20launch%20could%20happen%20within%20the%20allocated%20launch%20window%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ISRO%20Chairman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20test%20is%20the%20predecessor%20to%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission%20which%20aims%20to%20send%20humans%20into%20space%20on%20a%20low%20Earth%20orbit%20of%20400%20kms%20for%20three%20days%20and%20bring%20them%20safely%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%20first%20test%2C%20ISRO%20will%20gather%20data%20on%20the%20efficacy%20of%20the%20crew%20escape%20system.%20It%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20another%20test%20flight%20carrying%20a%20robot%20to%20outer%20space%20before%20the%20final%20manned%20mission%20takes%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20ultimate%20manned%20'Gaganyaan'%20mission%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20test%20flight%20next%20year%2C%20which%20will%20carry%20Vyommitra%2C%20the%20female%20robot%20astronaut%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mission%20is%20aimed%20at%20developing%20a%20human-habitable%20space%20capsule%20that%20will%20carry%20a%20three-member%20crew%20into%20an%20orbit%20of%20400%20km%20for%20three%20days%2C%20before%20splashing%20down%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20programme%20will%20make%20India%20the%20fourth%20nation%20to%20launch%20a%20manned%20spaceflight%20mission%20after%20the%20US%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia's%20space%20programme%20has%20grown%20considerably%20in%20size%20and%20momentum%20since%20it%20first%20sent%20a%20probe%20to%20orbit%20the%20Moon%20in%202008%2C%20and%20it%20has%20steadily%20matched%20the%20achievements%20of%20established%20spacefaring%20powers%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20their%20cost.%20In%20August%2C%20India%20became%20just%20the%20fourth%20nation%20to%20land%20an%20unmanned%20craft%20on%20the%20Moon%20after%20Russia%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20plans%20a%20joint%20mission%20with%20Japan%20to%20send%20another%20probe%20to%20the%20Moon%20by%202025%20and%20an%20orbital%20mission%20to%20Venus%20within%20the%20next%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697872620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F7ln8e6eo_gaganyaan-test-flight-_625x300_21_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-says-launch-of-unmanned-test-flight-for-its-first-human-space-mission-gaganyaan-has-been-put-on-hold-for-now-4501701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20test%20for%20the%20Gaganyaan%20human%20space%20flight%20mission%20was%20successfully%20completed%20after%20ISRO%20fixed%20an%20anomaly%20that%20had%20delayed%20the%20lift%20off%20just%20seconds%20before%20the%20scheduled%20launch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-says-launch-of-unmanned-test-flight-for-its-first-human-space-mission-gaganyaan-has-been-put-on-hold-for-now-4501701%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-says-launch-of-unmanned-test-flight-for-its-first-human-space-mission-gaganyaan-has-been-put-on-hold-