%20war%20could%20trigger%20a%20wider%2C%20more%20devastating%20Middle%20East%20conflict%20if%20Iran%20gets%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20quite%20possible%20that%20Hezbollah%20which%20is%20much%20more%20militarily%20capable%20and%20supported%20by%20Iran%20could%20get%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20fighting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Israel's%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20-%20which%20is%20inevitable%20-%20will%20have%20massive%20global%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20ground%20war%20is%20going%20to%20happen.%20It%20is%20a%20bad%20idea%20for%20many%20reasons.%20It%20will%20kill%20enormous%20number%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians%2C%20it%20will%20be%20done%20in%20short%20order%20or%20without%20aid%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20to%20evacuate.%20It%20will%20lead%20to%20backlash%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20he%20expects%20the%20widening%20of%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20into%20a%20regional%20one%2C%20Mr%20Bremmer%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20World%20War%203%2C%20but%20the%20idea%20that%20is%20stays%20contained%20within%20Gaza%20is%20%26quot%3Bfar%20too%20imaginary%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20World%20War%203.%20The%20Russians%20and%20the%20Chinese%20will%20not%20get%20directly%20involved%20in%20this%20war.%20But%20the%20idea%20that%20is%20stays%20contained%20within%20Gaza%20is%20far%20too%20imaginary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20already%20seen%20drone%20strikes%20against%20US%20military%20bases%20and%20equipment%20in%20the%20region.%20We%20have%20seen%20some%20squirmish%20at%20the%20Northern%20border%20of%20Israel%20with%20Hezbollah%20strikes.%20Some%20small%20incursions%20could%20also%20get%20bigger.%20We%20have%20seen%20dozens%20of%20Palestinians%20get%20killed%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20Israeli%20settlers%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20involved%20in%20that%20violence%20but%20it%20could%20easily%20spread%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Eurasia%20Group%20founder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20economic%20impact%20of%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20war%2C%20Mr%20Bremmer%20said%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bnegligible%26quot%3B%20unless%20Iran%20gets%20involved.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Russian%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20had%20massive%20economic%20implications.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Israel%2C%20it's%20a%20tiny%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Iran%20gets%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20war%2C%20that%20will%20lead%20to%20wider%20implications%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BStrikes%20on%20Iran%20could%20probably%20lead%20to%20a%20major%20oil%20crisis%20that%20will%20drive%20the%20world%20into%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bremmer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20conflict%2C%20the%20second%20major%20foreign%20policy%20crisis%20for%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20is%20a%20huge%20distraction%20for%20the%20US.%20This%20is%20sort%20of%20pinning%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20leaders%20he%20does%20not%20privately%20like%20or%20trust%20-%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20and%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20after%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20launched%20an%20unprecedented%20raid%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20on%20October%207%2C%20killing%20at%20least%201%2C400%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%20shot%2C%20mutilated%20or%20burned%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Israeli%20bombers%20have%20levelled%20entire%20city%20blocks%20in%20Gaza%20in%20preparation%20for%20a%20ground%20invasion%20they%20say%20is%20coming%20soon.%20The%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20said%204%2C137%20Palestinians%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20have%20died%20in%20the%20onslaught.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697872080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F7ndvfk08_israelgaza-war-reuters_625x300_17_O