20Israel%20at%20this%20juncture%20is%20inhuman%20and%20politicking%20of%20the%20worst%20sort.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20prolonged%20torment%20had%20to%20generate%20a%20violent%20reaction%20sooner%20or%20later.%20It%20has%20come%20now%20to%20Gaza%2C%20and%20with%20the%20only%20outlet%20available.%20Terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20doubt%2C%20a%20nonviolent%20solution%20has%20to%20be%20found%20%E2%80%93%20but%20only%20a%20non-partisan%20statesman%20can%20strategise%20a%20treaty%20which%20preserves%20self%20respect%20for%20all%20the%20parties%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20time%20to%20talk%20or%20play%20politics.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20Israel%20has%20to%20recognise%20that%20Palestine%20is%20a%20State%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20Israel%20is.%20It%20is%20only%20then%20that%20ground%20can%20be%20laid%20for%20fruitful%20talks%20for%20a%20settlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99m%20not%20condoning%20terror%20%E2%80%93%20but%20years%20of%20torture%20and%20deprivation%20leave%20people%20with%20no%20recourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20not%20be%20swayed%20by%20videos%2C%20real%20or%20fake%2C%20but%20understand%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20light%20of%20recent%20history%2C%20which%20was%20made%20right%20in%20front%20of%20our%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmridula-garg%5C%22%3EMridula%20Garg%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20prominent%20Hindi%20writer%20and%20Sahitya%20Akademi%20award%20winner.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697871335000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21122414%2F20140805_beit_hanun8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Flet-us-not-forget-what-made-hamas-and-caused-the-recent-eruption%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Something%20had%20to%20erupt%20in%20Gaza%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20extreme%20and%20inhuman%20provocation%20which%20has%20gone%20on%20for%20decades%2C%20says%20leading%20Hindi%20writer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Flet-us-not-forget-what-made-hamas-and-caused-the-recent-eruption%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infant%20Rape-Murder%20Case%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Sets%20Aside%20Man's%20Conviction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20set%20aside%20the%20conviction%20of%20a%20man%20facing%20death%20penalty%20for%20alleged%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20three-month-old%20girl%20and%20remitted%20the%20matter%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bde%20novo%20(new)%20trial%26quot%3B%2C%20observing%20that%20the%20trial%20in%20the%20case%20was%20conducted%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bhurried%20manner%26quot%3B%20without%20giving%20him%20proper%20opportunity%20to%20defend%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20trial%20in%20the%20case%20lodged%20in%202018%20was%20completed%20within%20a%20span%20of%2015%20days%20from%20the%20date%20of%20filing%20of%20the%20charge%20sheet%2C%20the%20accused%20was%20convicted%20for%20several%20offences%20and%20sentenced%20to%20death%20by%20the%20trial%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20B%20R%20Gavai%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20of%20the%20considered%20view%20that%20the%20trial%20court%20conducted%20the%20trial%20in%20a%20hurried%20manner%20without%20giving%20proper%20opportunity%20to%20the%20accused%20to%20defend%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20settled%20that%20a%20hasty%20trial%20in%20which%20proper%20and%20sufficient%20opportunity%20was%20not%20provided%20to%20the%20accused%20to%20defend%20himself%20or%20herself%20would%20vitiate%20the%20trial%20as%20being%20%26quot%3Bmeaningless%20and%20stage-managed%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justices%20PS%20Narasimha%20and%20Prashant%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20said%20in%20its%20verdict%20delivered%20on%20October%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20the%20judgement%20of%20conviction%20and%20sentence%20passed%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20and%20affirmed%20by%20the%20high%20court%20is%20hereby%20set%20aside%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20remitted%20back%20to%20the%20trial%20court%20for%20de%20novo%20trial%20by%20affording%20proper%20opportunity%20to%20the%20appellant%20to%20defend%20himself%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20delivered%20its%20verdict%20on%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20appellant%2C%20Naveen%2C%20challenging%20the%20December%202018%20judgement%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20upholding%20his%20conviction%20for%20the%20offences%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20including%20that%20of%20murder%20and%20rape%2C%20and%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20had%20confirmed%20the%20death%20sentence%20awarded%20to%20him%20by%20a%20trial%20court%20in%20Indore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20noted%20in%20its%20verdict%20that%20the%20appellant%20was%20convicted%20and%20sentenced%20for%20committing%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20three-month-old%20girl%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20arguments%20before%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20counsel%20appearing%20for%20the%20appellant%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20entire%20trial%20was%20completed%20within%2015%20days%20--%20from%20April%2027%2C%202018%2C%20when%20the%20charge%20sheet%20was%20filed%2C%20to%20May%2012%2C%202018%2C%20when%20judgement%20was%20delivered%20by%20the%20trial%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20close%20reading%20and%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20order%20sheet%20recorded%20by%20the%20trial%20court%2C%20as%20stated%20above%20in%20brief%2C%20would%20manifest%20that%20the%20accused%20was%20not%20provided%20an%20opportunity%20to%20engage%20a%20counsel%20of%20his%20choice%20and%20instead%20his%20submission%20was%20recorded%20that%20he%20desires%20to%20be%20defended%20by%20a%20counsel%20appointed%20through%20legal%20aid%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20order%20sheets%20clearly%20indicated%20that%20the%20trial%20was%20conducted%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bhurried%20manner%26quot%3B%20without%20providing%20ample%20and%20proper%20opportunity%20to%20the%20defence%20counsel%2C%20who%20was%20engaged%20through%20legal%20aid%2C%20to%20prepare%20himself%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20principle%20of%20%26quot%3Bjudicial%20calm%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20context%20of%20fair%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20view%2C%20in%20the%20hallowed%20halls%20of%20justice%2C%20the%20essence%20of%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20trial%20lies%20in%20the%20steadfast%20embrace%20of%20judicial%20calm.%20It%20is%20incumbent%20upon%20a%20judge%20to%20exude%20an%20aura%20of%20tranquillity%2C%20offering%20a%20sanctuary%20of%20reason%20and%20measured%20deliberation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20halls%20of%20justice%2C%20the%20gavel%20strikes%20not%20in%20haste%2C%20but%20in%20a%20deliberate%20cadence%20ensuring%20every%20voice%2C%20every%20piece%20of%20evidence%2C%20is%20accorded%20its%20due%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20expanse%20of%20judicial%20calm%20serves%20not%20only%20as%20a%20pillar%20of%20constitutional%20integrity%2C%20but%20as%20the%20very%20bedrock%20upon%20which%20trust%20in%20a%20legal%20system%20is%20forged%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20noted%20it%20was%20impossible%20for%20the%20accused%20to%20produce%20during%20the%20trial%20two%20experts%2C%20authors%20of%20reports%20like%20DNA%20and%20FSL%2C%20in%20one%20day%20because%20they%20were%20government%20servants%20and%20could%20not%20have%20attended%20the%20court%20at%20his%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20trial%20court%20treate