cted%20much%2C%20political%20scientist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-iran-palestine-war-hezbollah-iran-no-world-war-3-but-eurasia-founder-to-ndtv-on-israel-gaza-crisis-4501955%5C%22%3EIan%20Bremmer%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20working%20with%20India%20because%20it%20is%20the%20largest%20population%20in%20the%20world%2C%20it%20is%20growing%20at%20over%206%25%20a%20year%2C%20and%20is%20increasingly%20developing%20some%20pretty%20extraordinary%20new%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20Iran%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20or%20Israel%2C%20you%20have%20lots%20of%20reasons%20to%20work%20with%20India.%20And%20that's%20not%20going%20to%20change%20anytime%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Eurasia%20Group%20president%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-israel-plans-to-establish-new-regime-in-gaza-after-destroying-hamas-4501654%5C%22%3EIsrael%20launched%20relentless%20aerial%20bombardment%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-and-israel-weigh-a-future-for-gaza-without-hamas-4501650%5C%22%3EGaza%20Strip%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%201%2C400%20citizens%20were%20killed%20in%20surprise%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207.%20Israel%20claims%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20the%20attack%20till%20Hamas%20is%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20is%20starkly%20divided%20on%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20emerging%20geopolitical%20faultlines%20further%20getting%20solidified.%20While%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%20have%20backed%20Israel%20to%20do%20everything%20in%20their%20power%20to%20tackle%20Hamas%2C%20China%20and%20Russia%20have%20spoken%20out%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20consistently%20called%20for%20restraint%20and%20a%20ceasefire%20but%20has%20also%20sharpened%20its%20criticism%20of%20Israel.%20Russia%20has%20expressed%20sympathy%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20while%20blaming%20the%20US%20and%20their%20%26quot%3Bfailed%20policy%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Bremmer%20said%20that%20while%20faultlines%20have%20been%20solidified%20and%20a%20ground%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-palestine-news-updates-hamas-frees-two-us-hostages-more-releases-likely-soon-4501626%5C%22%3Ewar%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20inevitable%2C%20this%20conflict%20may%20not%20lead%20to%20World%20War%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20ground%20war%20is%20going%20to%20happen.%20It%20is%20a%20bad%20idea%20for%20many%20reasons.%20It%20will%20kill%20enormous%20number%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians%2C%20it%20will%20be%20done%20in%20short%20order%20or%20without%20aid%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20to%20evacuate.%20It%20will%20lead%20to%20backlash%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bremmer%20tells%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20while%20India%20is%20not%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20to%20make%20strategic%20decisions%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20taking%20a%20similar%20stand%20to%20that%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20historically%20has%20recognised%20Palestine%2C%20but%20PM%20Modi%20immediately%20came%20out%20with%20sympathy%20for%20Netanyahu%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%20A%20very%20different%20perspective%20from%20what%20you%20see%20from%20countries%20in%20the%20global%20south%20and%20the%20middle%20east%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20India%20is%20moving%20ahead%20in%20a%20new%20direction%20under%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Bremmer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20continues%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20someone%20who%20wants%20to%20be%20aligned%20with%20the%20West%20and%20not%20the%20Chinese%2C%20not%20the%20Russians%20on%20geopolitical%20issues.%20These%20are%20incremental%20steps%2C%20not%20an%20alliance%2C%20but%20it's%20nonetheless%20a%20clear%20direction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Israeli%20author%20Yuval%20Noah%20Harari%20had%20also%20spoken%20about%20the%20immense%20leverage%20that%20India%20has%20in%20the%20global%20order.%20Speaking%20to%20NDTV's%20Sonia%20Singh%2C%20Mr%20Harari%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20(India)%20is%20a%20democracy.%20It%20is%20committed%2C%20unlike%20Russia%20or%20China.%20It%20is%20committed%20to%20democratic%20ideals.%20But%20it%20has%20good%20relations%20with%20many%20of%20these%20countries%20and%20also%20with%20Iran.%20So%20hopefully%20India%20will%20use%20whatever%20leverage%20it%20has%20on%20countries%20like%20Iran%20to%20de-escalate%2C%20first%20of%20all%2C%20to%20prevent%20further%20escalation%20of%20the%20conflict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaza%20has%20been%20under%20complete%20seige%20since%20Israel%20launched%20retaliatory%20strikes%20to%20the%20terror%20attack%20on%20October%207.%20Israel's%20military%20campaign%20has%20levelled%20entire%20city%20blocks%20in%20Gaza%2C%20killing%204%2C137%20Palestinians%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20troops%20are%20massed%20on%20the%20border%20with%20Gaza%20ahead%20of%20an%20expected%20ground%20invasion%20that%20officials%20have%20pledged%20will%20begin%20%26quot%3Bsoon%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697870580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fmm0sg1es_ian-bremmer-ndtv_625x300_21_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-ndtv-exclusive-will-india-be-impacted-by-israel-hamas-war-political-scientist-ian-bremmer-explains-4502011%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ongoing%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20could%20trigger%20wider%20conflict%20but%20India%20is%20not%20likely%20to%20be%20impacted%20much%2C%20political%20scientist%20Ian%20Bremmer%20says%