2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104601698%2Cimgsize-44290.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fira-khan-celebrates-love-and-best-decision-nupur-shikhare-with-unseen-engagement-pics%2Farticleshow%2F104601723.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104601723.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIra%20Khan%2C%20daughter%20of%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20is%20set%20to%20marry%20fitness%20trainer%20Nupur%20Shikhare%20on%20January%203%2C%202024.%20Ira%20recently%20shared%20intimate%20and%20unseen%20pictures%20from%20their%20engagement%20ceremony%2C%20showcasing%20heartfelt%20moments%20and%20family%20bonds.%20She%20expressed%20her%20love%20and%20appreciation%20for%20Nupur%2C%20emphasizing%20their%20special%20connection.%20The%20engagement%20gathering%20was%20attended%20by%20Bollywood%20luminaries%2C%20creating%20cherished%20pre-wedding%20memories.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fira-khan-celebrates-love-and-best-decision-nupur-shikhare-with-unseen-engagement-pics%2Farticleshow%2F104601723.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Appointments%20in%20Universities%3A%20Triumph%20of%20Political%20Largesse%20Over%20Academic%20Considerations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fdelhi-university.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%20Legislative%20Assembly%20recently%20passed%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Universities%20of%20Agriculture%2C%20Horticulture%20and%20Forestry%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023.%20The%20Bill%20amends%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Universities%20of%20Agriculture%2C%20Horticulture%20and%20Forestry%20Act%2C%201986%2C%20under%20which%20two%20of%20the%20seven%20state%20universities%20are%20established%20and%20governed.%20The%20amended%20Sections%202%2C%2023%2C%20and%2024%20of%20the%20Act%20confer%20the%20exclusive%20power%20upon%20the%20governor%20of%20the%20state%20(in%20the%20ex-officio%20capacity%20of%20chancellor)%20to%20appoint%20vice-chancellors%20of%20Sarwan%20Kumar%20Krishi%20Vishvavidyalay%2C%20Palampur%2C%C2%A0and%20Dr.%20Y.S.%20Parmar%20University%20of%20Horticulture%20and%20Forestry%2C%20Solan%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Caid%20and%20advice%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20of%20objects%20and%20reasons%20of%20the%20Bill%20claim%20to%20pursue%20objectives%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%202020%20and%20give%20effect%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Caspirations%20of%20the%20people%E2%80%9D.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20amendments%20are%20carried%20out%20to%20%E2%80%9Callow%20the%20Democratic%20Government%20to%20exercise%20its%20right%20to%20shape%20the%20institutions%20of%20higher%20learning%20by%20exclusively%20controlling%20the%20appointment%20of%20VCs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Amendment%20abolishes%20the%20original%20system%20of%20the%20selection%20of%20VCs%20through%20a%20neutral%20Selection%20Committee%20and%20gives%20exclusive%20power%20to%20the%20state%20government%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20top%20appointments%20in%20the%20universities.%20The%20government%20has%20similar%20proposals%20to%20amend%20other%20Acts%20of%20the%20state%20to%20bring%20democratic%20(political)%20influences%20by%20nominating%20MLAs%20in%20the%20governing%20bodies%20of%20its%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Funiversities-future-ruins-excellence%5C%22%3EIn%20Central%20Universities%2C%20the%20Future%20Will%20Now%20Be%20Built%20on%20the%20Ruins%20of%20Excellence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHimachal%20is%2C%20however%2C%20not%20the%20first%20state%20that%20has%20tried%20to%20diminish%20the%20autonomy%20of%20state%20universities.%20The%20first%20state%20was%20the%20Janata%20Party%20government%20of%20Gujarat%20which%20tried%20to%20control%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20universities%20by%20making%20the%20post%20of%20VC%20a%20political%20one.%20It%20amended%20the%20Gujarat%20University%20Act%2C%201949%20in%201978.%20Subsequently%2C%20there%20are%20many%20states%2C%20including%20Telangana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20have%20followed%20similar%20policies.%20Recently%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20amended%20its%20two%20statutes%20in%202022%20to%20establish%20political%20control%20over%20the%20appointments%20of%20VCs%20in%20its%2013%20state%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInfluence%20of%20party%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20two%20years%20before%20the%20Gujarat%20amendment%2C%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201976%20brought%20the%2042nd%20Amendment%20to%20the%20constitution%20and%20reconstituted%20the%20entire%20scheme%20of%20education%20under%20the%20Indian%20federal%20constitutional%20setup.%20In%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20post-colonial%20India%2C%20all%20educational%20institutions%2C%20except%20the%20existing%20three%20central%20universities%20such%20as%20Delhi%20University%2C%20Banaras%20Hindu%20University%2C%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%2C%20and%20a%20few%20central%20educational%20institutions%2C%20were%20schematised%20to%20be%20managed%20by%20the%20state%20governments.%20The%20government%20or%20parliament%20of%20India%20had%20only%20the%20power%20of%20coordination%20and%20maintenance%20of%20standards%20with%20respect%20to%20higher%20education.%20The%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%2C%20All%20India%20Council%20for%20Technical%20Education%20(AICTE)%2C%20Medical%20Council%20of%20India%20(MCI)%2C%20Bar%20Council%20of%20India%20(BCI)%2C%20and%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20(ICAR)%2C%20etc.%2C%20are%20the%20central%20agencies%20for%20coordinating%20and%20ensuring%20the%20minimum%20standard%20of%20education%20to%20be%20maintained%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2FJNU2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20the%20JNU%20campus.%20Source%3A%20JNU%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2FJNU2.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2FJNU2-300x198.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-21473%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22635%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20JNU%20campus.%20Source%3A%20JNU%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2042nd%20Amendment%20transferred%20the%20subject%20of%20%E2%80%98education%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20exclusive%20ambit%20of%20states%20(State%20List)%20to%20the%20Concurrent%20List%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20where%20both%20the%20Centre%20and%20states%20can%20make%20laws%20on%20the%20same%20subject%20matter.%20But%2C%20in%20case%20of%20conflict%2C%20the%20Central%20legislation%20has%20primacy%20by%20virtue%20of%20Article%20254%20(rule%20of%20repugnancy)%20of%20the%20constitution.%20This%20new%20constitutional%20scheme%20has%20failed%20to%20establish%20a%20minimum%20standard%20for%20the%20administration%20of%20educational%20institutions%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETeaching%20is%20never%20a%20neutral%20act.%20All%20education%20is%20political%20(Paulo%20Friere%2C%201968).%20Paulo%20was%20talking%20about%20the%20methods%20of%20pedagogy.%20But%20in%20the%20Indian%20context%2C%20the%20education%20system%20is%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20power%20politics%20of%20political%20parties.%20As%20far%20as%20the%20education%20system%20is%20concerned%2C%20neither%20democratic%20politics%20nor%20constitutional%20federalism%20has%20served%20well%20in%20India.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20practical%20logic%20of%20party%20politics%20and%20shifting%20schemes%20of%20federalism%20have%20worked%20against%20the%20cause%20of%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20right%20to%20school%20education%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right%20under%20Article%2021A%20of%20the%20constitution%20for%20every%20child%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%206-14%20years.%20Notably%2C%20Article%2026%20of%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%2C%201948%20declares%20the%20right%20to%20education%20a%20human%20right.%20Its%20language%20expresses%20the%20morality%20of%20aspiration%20to%20ensure%20elementary%20education%20is%20free%20and%20compulsory%20and%20higher%20or%20technical%20education%20accessible%20to%20all%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20merit.%20These%20normative%20enunciations%20mean%20little%20to%20the%20Indian%20policymakers%20who%20have%20increasingly%20used%20the%20system%20of%20school%20and%20higher%20education%20as%20a%20means%20of%20party%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20vice-chancellor%20of%20a%20university%20is%20the%20leader%20of%20that%20institution%20whose%20visions%20and%20actions%20lead%20the%20university%20in%20a%20certain%20direction.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20post%20of%20vice-chancellor%20should%20be%20held%20by%20an%20academician%20of%20profound%20intellect%20and%20highest%20integrity.%20The%20moment%20this%20post%20is%20made%20into%20political%20largesse%2C%20by%20any%20political%20party%20in%20power%2C%20its%20independence%20is%20compromised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20both%20in%20central%20universities%20and%20national%20institutions%20of%20importance%20too%2C%20political%20parties%20have%20been%20playing%20a%20decisive%20role.%20Teachers%20of%20colleges%20or%20degree%20colleges%20have%20been%20appointed%20to%20the%20post%20of%20vice-chancellor%20frequently.%20People%20such%20as%20careerists%20from%20private%20universities%20are%20rewarded%20with%20the%20post%20of%20vice-chancellor%20or%20registrar%20due%20to%20their%20connection%20with%20the%20political%20party%20in%20power.%20Parties%20do%20it%2C%20chiefly%2C%20to%20strengthen%20their%20cadre%20base%20by%20way%20of%20gifts%20of%20state%20largess.%20Immediately%2C%20the%20education%20system%20falls%20victim%20to%20the%20party-centric%20political%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fthe-virus-of-delegated-authoritarianism-or-why-we-mustnt-ignore-jnu-v-cs-evasions%5C%22%3EThe%20Virus%20of%20Delegated%20Authoritarianism%2C%20or%20Why%20We%20Mustn%E2%80%99t%20Ignore%20JNU%20V-C%E2%80%99s%20Evasions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPublic%20reason%20and%20electoral%20democracy%20are%20concepts%20that%20belong%20to%20the%20same%20essence.%20The%20government%20of%20the%20day%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20so-called%20custodian%20of%20public%20reason.%20However%2C%20neither%20public%20reason%20nor%20democracy%20can%20be%20conducive%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20knowledge%20and%20education.%20Thus%2C%20traditionally%2C%20universities%20have%20been%20regarded%20to%20be%20autonomous%20spaces%3B%20free%20from%20not%20only%20unrestricted%20governmental%20control%20but%20also%20from%20the%20coercive%20sentiments%20and%20opinions%20relating%20to%20morality%20and%20cultural%20norms%20emanating%20from%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20cadres%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20are%20the%20chief%20instruments%20for%20exercising%20social%2C%20political%2C%20and%20legal%20coercion%20in%20the%20education%20system.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20system%20of%20appointment%20of%20%E2%80%98guest%20teachers%E2%80%99%20without%20any%20merit-based%20examination%20has%20already%20done%20irreparable%20damage%20to%20government%20schools.%20Every%20government%20gives%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20appointment%20of%20guest%20teachers%20to%20its%20party%20workers.%20Later%20on%2C%20through%20legal%20battles%20in%20the%20courts%2C%20the%20permanency%20of%20the%20job%20is%20secured%20by%20the%20guest%20teachers%20and%20the%20question%20of%20merit%20disappears%20forever.%20A%20similar%20pattern%20has%20been%20adopted%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Bihar%2C%20among%20others%20under%20the%20Shiksha%20Mitra%20Scheme.%20The%20scheme%20is%20notorious%20as%20%3Cem%3EShiksha%20Shatru%3C%2Fem%3E%20(enemy%20of%20school%20education).%20Not%20unexpectedly%2C%20private%20schools%20with%20poor%20quality%20have%20been%20mushrooming%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20Almost%20every%20village%2C%20%3Cem%3EKasba%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20town%20has%20some%20sort%20of%20private%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20consideration%20for%20academic%20standards%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20respect%20to%20the%20system%20of%20university%2C%20it%20should%20be%20clearly%20understood%20that%20the%20universities%20must%20be%20governed%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Cacademic%20reason%E2%80%9D%20primarily.%20Academic%20reason%20comes%20with%20commitment%2C%20devotion%2C%20and%20lifelong%20dedication%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20knowledge%2C%20truth%2C%20and%20good%20academic%20accomplishments%20but%20not%20by%20political%20interference.%20If%20the%20teachers%20of%20universities%20are%20appointed%20due%20to%20political%20allegiance%20rather%20than%20academic%20merit%20then%20what%20can%20one%20expect%20from%20Indian%20universities%20with%20respect%20to%20academic%20excellence%3F%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20state%20of%20affairs%20is%20visible%20in%20all%20prominent%20universities%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20interferes%20in%20the%20governance%20of%20state%20universities%20through%20the%20agency%20of%20governors.%20In%20reaction%2C%20the%20states%20are%20resorting%20to%20amendments%20in%20their%20laws.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20it%20is%20the%20autonomy%20of%20universities%20and%20academic%20standards%20which%20suffer.%20The%20contemporary%20systems%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20vice-chancellor%20in%20Indian%20universities%20are%20not%20governed%20by%20academic%20reason%20rather%20it%20is%20determined%20by%20the%20political%20expediency%20of%20the%20party%20in%20power.%20Teaching%2C%20learning%2C%20and%20administration%20of%20the%20institution%20are%20affected%20by%20the%20policies%20and%20preferences%20of%20the%20vice-chancellor%20who%20needs%20to%20please%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20give-and-take%20manner%20%E2%80%93%20the%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20fate%20of%20leadership%20in%20higher%20educational%20institutions%20may%20be%20understood%20by%20asking%20a%20few%20conjectural%20questions.%20A%20student%20may%20simply%20ask%20herself%20how%20many%20research%20articles%20her%20vice-chancellor%2Fdirector%20has%20written%20which%20ought%20to%20be%20taught%20and%20read%20in%20her%20Master%E2%80%99s%20Course.%20Has%20her%20head%20of%20the%20institution%20produced%20academic%20books%20that%20can%20be%20prescribed%20as%20mandatory%20reference%20material%20in%20her%20post-graduation%20course%3F%20How%20many%20works%20of%20such%20head%2Fleader%20are%20part%20of%20reference%20courses%20in%20the%20top%201%2C000%20universities%20of%20the%20world%3F%20And%20so%20on.%20Most%20of%20the%20vice-chancellors%20on%20these%20parameters%20do%20not%20have%20to%20their%20credit%20significant%20academic%20contributions.%20But%20their%20political%20background%20and%20efficacious%20lobbying%20help%20them%20to%20reach%20the%20top%20posts%20in%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWay%20forward%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDemocracy%20has%20both%20emancipatory%20as%20well%20as%20repressive%20and%20regressive%20potential.%20Thus%2C%20there%20are%20politics%20of%20justice%2C%20fairness%2C%20liberation%2C%20and%20excellence.%20There%20are%20also%20politics%20of%20subjugation%2C%20domination%2C%20deprivation%2C%20and%20regression.%20The%20education%20system%20in%20India%20is%20suffering%20from%20the%20malaise%20of%20the%20latter%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20corrected%20urgently%20to%20revive%20the%20spirit%20of%20education%20as%20a%20process%20of%20contemplation%20and%20critical%20exploration.%20India%20needs%20Gandhian%20praxis%20of%20pragmatism%2C%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20humanism%2C%20and%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20sense%20of%20aestheticism%20in%20the%20leadership%20of%20higher%20education%20to%20visualise%20the%20renaissance%20of%20education%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20that%20a%20system%20of%20academic%20audit%20is%20devised%20and%20every%20candidate%20for%20the%20top%20positions%20of%20leadership%20in%20universities%20is%20assessed%20accordingly.%20The%20system%20of%20assessment%20may%20be%20operationalised%20by%20a%20neutral%20selection%20or%20screening%20committee%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20publicised%20academic%20audit%20reports%20amongst%20the%20professors%2C%20scholars%2C%20and%20students%20where%20the%20idea%20of%20academic%20reason%20can%20have%20a%20sufficient%20role%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr.%20Chanchal%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20Professor%20of%20Law%2C%20and%20Director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Comparative%20Public%20Law%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20National%20Law%20University%20(HPNLU)%2C%20Shimla.%20Dr.%20Mritunjay%20Kumar%2C%20Assistant%20Professor%20of%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Coordinator%2C%20Centre%20for%20Comparative%20Public%20Law%2C%20HPNLU%2C%20Shimla.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697869857000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fdelhi-university.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fappointments-in-universities-triumph-of-political-largesse-over-academic-considerations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Unless%20a%20system%20of%20independent%20academic%20audit%20is%20devised%20for%20leadership%20positions%20in%20universities%20without%20any%20influence%20of%20party%20politics%2C%20nothing%20can%20be%20done%20to%20arrest%20the%20downward%20slide%20of%20higher%20education.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fappointments-in-universities-triumph-of-political-largesse-over-academic-considerations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20China%20Envisions%20A%20New%20World%20Order%20Via%20BRI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReaffirming%20his%20nation's%20commitment%20to%20continue%20pouring%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20the%20economies%20of%20developing%20countries%20as%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%20-%20the%20%26quot%3Bproject%20of%20the%20century%26quot%3B%20-%20enters%20its%20second%20decade%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20underlined%20earlier%20this%20week%20at%20the%20BRI%20forum%20that%20%26quot%3BChina%20can%20only%20do%20well%20when%20the%20world%20is%20doing%20well...%20When%20China%20does%20well%2C%20the%20world%20will%20get%20even%20better.%26quot%3B%20More%20significantly%2C%20and%20perhaps%20expectedly%2C%20he%20took%20aim%20at%20the%20West%20when%20he%20suggested%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20stand%20against%20unilateral%20sanctions%2C%20economic%20coercion%2C%20decoupling%2C%20and%20supply%20chain%20disruption.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20only%2024%20world%20leaders%20in%20attendance%2C%20compared%20to%20the%2037%20who%20had%20attended%20the%20last%20BRI%20Forum%2C%20Xi%20was%20keen%20to%20showcase%20that%20China%20is%20open%20for%20business%20at%20a%20time%20when%20concerns%20are%20rising%20about%20the%20health%20of%20Chinese%20economy.%20He%20promised%20to%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensively%20remove%20restrictions%20on%20foreign%20investment%20access%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20opening%20up%20%26quot%3Bcross-border%20trade%20and%20investment%20in%20services%20and%20expand%20market%20access%20for%20digital%20products%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20China's%20first%20major%20international%20event%20since%20coming%20out%20of%20around%20three%20years%20of%20pandemic%20lockdown%20in%20January%202023%20and%20was%20a%20celebration%20of%20one%20of%20Xi's%20signature%20projects.%20Not%20surprisingly%2C%20he%20was%20gung-ho%20about%20the%20achievements%20of%20BRI%20as%20he%20underlined%20how%20his%20initiative%20has%20helped%20the%20developing%20world%20by%20making%20infrastructure%20and%20connectivity%20the%20centerpiece%20of%20emerging%20global%20economic%20discourse.%20He%20outlined%20how%20China%20has%20%26quot%3Bendeavored%20to%20build%20a%20global%20network%20of%20connectivity%20consisting%20of%20economic%20corridors%2C%20international%20transportation%20routes%20and%20information%20highway%20as%20well%20as%20railways%2C%20roads%2C%20airports%2C%20ports%2C%20pipelines%20and%20power%20grids%2C%26quot%3B%20thereby%20boosting%20%26quot%3Bthe%20flow%20of%20goods%2C%20capital%2C%20technologies%20and%20human%20resources%20among%20countries%20involved%20and%20injected%20fresh%20vitality%20into%20the%20millennia-old%20Silk%20Road%20in%20the%20new%20era.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20BRI%20has%20been%20an%20innovative%20idea%20to%20energize%20the%20next%20stage%20of%20economic%20globalisation%20and%2C%20for%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20world%20left%20outside%20the%20global%20economic%20order%2C%20this%20was%20a%20timely%20initiative%20which%2C%20by%20mobilising%20as%20much%20as%20%241%20trillion%20in%20finance%2C%20allowed%20for%20new%20economic%20possibilities%20to%20emerge.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20operationalization%20of%20the%20idea%20that%20left%20much%20to%20be%20desired%20as%20several%20nations%20got%20saddled%20with%20huge%20debt%20even%20as%20the%20financial%20and%20environmental%20sustainability%20of%20many%20projects%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20vulnerabilities%20of%20a%20centralised%2C%20top%20down%20project.%20With%20several%20infrastructure%20projects%20stuck%20and%20the%20Chinese%20economy%20slowing%20down%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20this%20forum%20was%20also%20Xi%20Jinping's%20attempt%20to%20demonstrate%20his%20nation's%20continued%20commitment%20to%20a%20project%20in%20which%20he%20is%20personally%20invested%20and%20which%20is%20as%20much%20about%20geopolitical%20positioning%20of%20China%20in%20the%20emerging%20global%20order%20as%20it%20is%20about%20geoeconomics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFacing%20a%20lot%20of%20flak%20for%20the%20performance%20of%20BRI%2C%20Xi%20tried%20to%20send%20out%20a%20message%20that%20he%20is%20willing%20to%20make%20some%20changes%20with%20a%20move%20to%20%26quot%3Bhigh-quality%26quot%3B%20development%2C%20focused%20primarily%20on%20the%20digital%20economy%20and%20sustainable%20%26quot%3Bgreen%20development%26quot%3B%20and%20underpinned%20by%20%26quot%3Bthe%20philosophy%20of%20open%2C%20green%20and%20clean%20cooperation%2C%20and%20the%20goal%20of%20pursuing%20high-standard%2C%20people-centered%20and%20sustainable%20cooperation.%26quot%3B%20Integrity%20is%20the%20new%20buzzword%20as%20Xi%20talked%20of%20establishing%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Integrity%20and%20Compliance%20Evaluation%20System%20for%20companies%20involved%20in%20Belt%20and%20Road%20cooperation%26quot%3B%20and%20working%20%26quot%3Bwith%20international%20organizations%20to%20carry%20out%20research%20and%20training%20on%20promoting%20integrity%20in%20Belt%20and%20Road%20cooperation.%26quot%3B%20This%20was%20part%20of%20his%20eight-point%20action%20plan%20that%20also%20includes%20supporting%20an%20open%20world%20economy%2C%20promoting%20green%20development%2C%20advancing%20scientific%20and%20technological%20innovation%2C%20supporting%20people-to-people%20exchanges%2C%20and%20strengthening%20institutional%20building%20for%20international%20Belt%20and%20Road%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20light%20of%20the%20challenges%20facing%20the%20BRI%20projects%20worldwide%20and%20others%20launching%20connectivity%20alternatives%20to%20BRI%2C%20it%20was%20imperative%20for%20Xi%20Jinping%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20making%20amends.%20How%20these%20changes%20get%20reflected%20on%20the%20ground%20will%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20BRI%20and%20China's%20credibility%20as%20a%20provider%20of%20global%20public%20goods.%20But%20for%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20this%20is%20also%20about%20offering%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20US-led%20global%20order%2C%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20a%20Taliban%20delegation%20led%20by%20its%20acting%20minister%20of%20industry%20and%20commerce%2C%20Nooruddin%20Aziz%2C%20brought%20this%20into%20sharp%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPutin%2C%20of%20course%2C%20was%20the%20star%20at%20the%20forum%2C%20getting%20a%20red%20carpet%20welcome%20from%20the%20hosts%20and%20applauding%20the%20%26quot%3Bsuccesses%26quot%3B%20of%20%26quot%3Bour%20Chinese%20friends%26quot%3B%20in%20return.%20Russia%20has%20not%20officially%20signed%20on%20to%20the%20BRI%20but%20Putin%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20attend%20the%20forum%20in%20person%20despite%20not%20having%20travelled%20abroad%20since%20launching%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20The%20Moscow-Beijing%20global%20alignment%20is%20unmistakable%20as%20they%20seek%20to%20challenge%20the%20West%2C%20also%20reflected%20in%20their%20explicit%20criticism%20of%20Israeli%20actions%20while%20refraining%20from%20condemning%20Hamas.%20Since%20the%20Ukraine%20crisis%2C%20where%20the%20West%20has%20tried%20to%20isolate%20Russia%2C%20China's%20embrace%20has%20become%20all-encompassing%20as%20it%20has%20emerged%20as%20Russia's%20most%20important%20trade%20partner%2C%20providing%20critical%20civilian%20and%20military%20goods%20that%20have%20sustained%20Russian%20economy%20and%20war%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20interesting%20presence%20was%20that%20of%20the%20Taliban%2C%20also%20meant%20to%20convey%20a%20message%20to%20the%20US%20that%20China%20will%20continue%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20its%20outreach%20to%20a%20pariah%20state%2C%20if%20only%20to%20scuttle%20Washington%20in%20achieving%20its%20objectives.%20Last%20month%2C%20China%20became%20the%20first%20country%20to%20send%20an%20ambassador%20to%20Afghanistan%20though%20Beijing%20is%20yet%20to%20give%20diplomatic%20recognition%20to%20the%20Taliban.%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20had%20also%20announced%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20the%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20would%20be%20extended%20to%20Afghanistan.%20Nothing%20much%20has%20come%20of%20it%20yet%20but%20China's%20support%20gives%20credibility%20to%20the%20Taliban's%20claims%20of%20being%20the%20only%20credible%20alternative%20in%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina's%20celebration%20of%20a%20decade%20of%20BRI%20was%20more%20an%20attempt%20to%20showcase%20its%20own%20rising%20profile%20as%20the%20provider%20of%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20US-led%20global%20order%20than%20to%20provide%20for%20the%20development%20needs%20of%20the%20Global%20South.%20But%20challenges%20for%20the%20BRI%20are%20mounting%20and%20Xi's%20words%20at%20the%20forum%20were%20an%20explicit%20acknowledgment%20that%20changes%20in%20Chinese%20approach%20would%20be%20necessary%20if%20the%20second%20decade%20of%20BRI%20is%20to%20see%20more%20accomplishments%20than%20the%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20He%20is%20Vice%20President%20-%20Studies%20and%20Foreign%20Policy%20at%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20Director%20(Honorary)%20of%20the%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Transnational%20Affairs%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697869440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F5vr72ck8_china-belt-and-road-initiative-_625x300_16_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-china-envisions-a-new-world-order-via-bri-4501968%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reaffirming%20his%20nation's%20commitment%20to%20continue%20pouring%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20the%20economies%20of%20developing%20countries%20as%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%20-%20the%20%26quot%3Bproject%20of%20the%20century%26quot%3B%20-%20enters%20its%20second%20decade%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-china-envisions-a-new-world-order-via-bri-4501968%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meeting%20Gandhi%20in%20Ben-Gurion%E2%80%99s%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21114244%2FUntitled-design-1-4.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20consul%20general%20in%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fkobbishoshani%2Fstatus%2F1713833832234045573%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DZJCJhEAnpz0jFlEdwtO2BQ%5C%22%3EKobbi%20Shoshani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20an%20unusual%20move%2C%20went%20after%20well-known%20Indian%20fact-checker%20and%20co-founder%20of%20Alt%20News%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fzoo_bear%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Egoogle%257Ctwcamp%255Eserp%257Ctwgr%255Eauthor%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Zubair%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20accusing%20him%20of%20%E2%80%9Cspreading%20fake%20news%20and%20hatred%20about%20Israel%E2%80%9D.%20This%20was%20days%20before%20he%20won%20the%20Index%20on%20Censorship%20journalism%20award%20for%202023%2C%20for%20busting%20misinformation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20put%20the%20lens%20closely%20on%20that%20post%20by%20the%20top%20Israeli%20diplomat%20on%20the%20micro-blogging%20site%20X%2C%20it%20appears%20as%20if%20intended%20for%20the%20Hindutva%20troll%20army%20to%20take%20a%20hint%20from%20it%2C%20and%20hunt%20for%20Zubair%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20to%20possibly%20bog%20him%20down%20and%20thereby%20divert%20attention%20from%20what%20he%20had%20been%20doing%20%E2%80%93%20fact-checking%20the%20claims%20and%20counter%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20Israeli%20side%20on%20the%20ongoing%20Israeli-Palestinian%20crisis.%20While%20the%20social%20media%20space%20has%20been%20a%20virtual%20battleground%20with%20both%20pro-and%20anti-Israeli%20posts%20after%20the%20horrendous%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20that%20the%20diplomat%20went%20especially%20after%20Zubair%20seemed%20to%20support%20that%20possibility.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClearly%2C%20after%20the%20initial%20developments%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20showdown%20where%20Hamas%20mercilessly%20attacked%20unarmed%20innocent%20Jews%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20losing%20the%20sympathy%20wave%20in%20the%20social%20media%20space%2C%20worldwide%2C%20to%20the%20Palestinians.%20The%20cold-hearted%20bombing%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20now%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20the%20images%20springing%20out%20of%20the%20Israeli%20army%E2%80%99s%20pounding%20of%20the%20strip%20has%20left%20their%20government%20to%20face%20a%20barrage%20of%20uncomfortable%20questions%20from%20the%20international%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20a%20free%20and%20ready%20to%20go%20troll%20army%20from%20India%20to%20bat%20for%20the%20Israeli%20government%20has%20to%20be%20a%20gift.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20expected%2C%20after%20Shoshnani%E2%80%99s%20post%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fgarg_trupti%2Fstatus%2F1713861345026973977%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Elost%20no%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20troll%20Zubair%2C%20a%20marked%20guy%20for%20the%20right%20wing%20in%20India%20anyway%20for%20his%20continuous%20debunking%20of%20several%20of%20their%20communal%20claims.%20A%20fact-checker%20with%20a%20wrong%20name%2C%20of%20course.%20Off%20and%20on%2C%20FIRs%2C%20therefore%2C%20get%20filed%20against%20Zubair%2C%20prodding%20police%20in%20some%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20ruled%20state%20or%20the%20other%20to%20take%20them%20further.%20One%20such%20complaint%20had%20put%20him%20behind%20bars%20for%20some%20weeks%20not%20so%20long%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20by%20the%20time%20the%20Israeli%20diplomat%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20stop%20Zubair%E2%80%99s%20work%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20troll%20army%20and%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20had%20already%20set%20the%20tone%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20mouthing%20unwavering%20support%20for%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20straightjacketing%20Palestinians%20as%20%E2%80%98terrorists%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhindutva-israel-tweets-palestine-conflict%5C%22%3EUnpacking%20the%20Hindutva%20Embrace%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20stand%20is%20typically%20hinged%20on%20the%20anti-Muslim%20ideology%20of%20the%20larger%20Sangh%20Parivar%2C%20and%20also%20its%20one%20nation%2C%20one%20language%2C%20one%20religion%20dream%20which%20brings%20them%20closer%20to%20trying%20to%20be%20a%20Hindutva%20Zion%2C%20a%20partner%20state%20of%20Israel%2C%20to%20paraphrase%20Faisal%20Devji%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hup.harvard.edu%2Fcatalog.php%3Fisbn%3D9780674072671%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMuslim%20Zion%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20title%20of%20his%20book%20on%20how%20Pakistan%20imagined%20itself.%20So%20also%20the%20Israeli%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20imparting%20arms-training%20to%20all%20its%20young%20and%20able%2C%20which%20fits%20perfectly%20in%20support%20shown%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20K.B.%20Hedgewar%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20for%20the%20militarisation%20of%20the%20Hindu%20society%2C%20to%20eventually%20fight%20the%20Muslims.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20no%20rocket%20science%20that%20the%20reigning%20star%20of%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20has%20been%20inching%20closer%20to%20the%20Israeli%20far-right%20wing%20government%20and%20particularly%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20its%20controversial%20prime%20minister.%20The%20idea%20about%20Israel%2C%20a%20Jewish%20homeland%2C%20is%20a%20model%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20desperately%20wants%20to%20bring%20home%20to%20India%20in%20a%20Hindutva%20variant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlast%20from%20the%20past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20likes%20of%20Shoshnani%20must%20need%20reminding%20though%20is%20the%20pro-Nazi%20sentiment%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20contingent%20in%20the%201930s.%20Particularly%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20leader%20V.K.%20Savarkar%2C%20considered%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20flip%20here%20a%20few%20pages%20of%20history%20to%20help%20Shoshnani%20and%20his%20ilk%20do%20that%20reminding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Jerusalem%2C%20some%20years%20ago%2C%20walking%20through%20the%20largest%20Holocaust%20remembrance%20centre%2C%20Yad%20Vashem%2C%20my%20Hindu%20heart%20sank%20in%20shame%20when%20at%20one%20place%2C%20an%20audio%20visual%20exhibit%20flashed%20the%20Swastika%20to%20highlight%20that%20Hitler%20copied%20the%20symbol%20from%20the%20religion.%20That%20a%20sacred%20symbol%20of%20my%20religion%20was%20worn%20on%20the%20arms%20that%20aimed%20for%20the%20neck%20of%20thousands%20of%20innocent%20Jews%20including%20children%20did%20make%20me%20mumble%20under%20my%20breath%2C%20it%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20in%20my%20name.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21112644%2FDSC_2831_0.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21112644%2FDSC_2831_0.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21112644%2FDSC_2831_0-300x206.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681129%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EYad%20Vashem%2C%20The%20World%20Holocaust%20Remembrance%20Center.%20Photo%3A%20Yossi%20Ben%20David%2F%20Yad%20Vashem%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.yadvashem.org%2F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParallel%20to%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20Germany%2C%20in%20the%20India%20of%20the%201930s%2C%20top%20honchos%20of%20Hindutva%20were%2C%20however%2C%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Nazi%20leader%20and%20his%20annihilation%20of%20the%20Jews.%C2%A0%20The%20likes%20of%20Savarkar%20and%20M.S.%20Golwalkar%20were%20at%20odds%20with%20Congress%20leaders%20of%20the%20day%2C%20like%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20for%20not%20supporting%20the%20Nazis%20and%20the%20Fascism%20of%20Italy.%20Marzia%20Casolari%20in%20her%202023%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Shadow%20of%20Swastika%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Relationship%20Between%20Indian%20Radical%20Nationalism%2C%20Italian%20Fascism%20and%20Nazism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20writes%20that%20a%20month%20after%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgreat%20anti-Jewish%20pogrom%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98the%20Night%20of%20Broken%20Glass%E2%80%99%20took%20place%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpro-Hindu%20Mahasabha%20journals%20published%20articles%20in%20favour%20of%20German%20anti-Semitism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20author%20further%20writes%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThis%20stance%20brought%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20into%20conflict%20with%20the%20Congress%20which%2C%20on%2012%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20December%20(1938)%2C%20made%20a%20statement%20containing%20clear%20references%20to%20recent%20European%20events.%20Within%20the%20Congress%2C%20only%20(Subhash%20Chandra)%20Bose%20opposed%20the%20party%20stance.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20in%20April%201939%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20support%20the%20party%20motion%20that%20Jews%20might%20find%20refuge%20in%20India.%20Savarkar%20and%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20had%20a%20similar%20opinion.%E2%80%9D%20(page%2090)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Malegaon%20in%20the%20autumn%20of%20that%20year%2C%20Savarkar%20felt%20that%20following%20the%20German%20example%20could%20solve%20Hindutva%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20problem%E2%80%99.%20This%20was%20just%20one%20example%20of%20several%20instances%20cited%20by%20the%20noted%20author%20where%20Savarkar%20justified%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20pogrom%20on%20the%20Jews.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20the%20book%20quotes%20Savarkar%20saying%20publicly%2C%20%E2%80%9CSurely%20Hitler%20knows%20better%20than%20Pandit%20Nehru%20does%20what%20suits%20Germany%20best.%20The%20very%20fact%20that%20Germany%20or%20Italy%20(under%20Mussolini)%20has%20so%20wonderfully%20recovered%20and%20grown%20so%20powerful%20as%20never%20before%20at%20the%20touch%20of%20Nazi%20or%20Fascist%20magical%20wand%20is%20enough%20to%20prove%20that%20those%20political%20%E2%80%98isms%E2%80%99%20were%20the%20most%20congenial%20tonics%20their%20health%20demanded.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECasolari%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CGolwalkar%20went%20further%20than%20Savarkar%20and%20even%20considered%20the%20possibility%20of%20denying%20the%20Muslims%20citizens%E2%80%99%20rights.%20It%20is%20well-known%20that%20Golwalkar%E2%80%99s%20idea%20of%20nation%20was%20inspired%20by%20Johann%20Kaspar%20Bluntschli%2C%20%E2%80%98an%20exponent%20of%20German%20ethnic%20nationalism%E2%80%99%20and%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Theory%20of%20the%20State%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBack%20to%20the%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20recent%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20the%20Congress%20called%20for%20shunning%20violence%2C%20and%20also%20reiterated%20India%E2%80%99s%20longstanding%20stand%20in%20support%20of%20a%20Palestinian%20state.%20That%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%20accused%20the%20Congress%20thereafter%20of%20supporting%20%E2%80%98terrorists%E2%80%99%20(read%20Muslims)%20came%20across%20as%20a%20fitting%20parallel%20to%20what%20Savarkar%20and%20his%20ilk%20had%20stated%20to%20the%20anti-Nazi%20stand%20of%20the%20Congress%20of%20the%201930s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20began%20to%20escalate%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20did%20end%20up%20falling%20back%20on%C2%A0%20India%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20line%20on%20Palestine%20but%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20campaign%20against%20Congress%20for%20that%20statement%20has%20continued%2C%20merely%20because%20it%20has%20an%20anti-Muslim%20edge%20to%20it%2C%20a%20potential%20weapon%20in%20a%20difficult%20election%20season.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20many%20in%20Israel%2C%20the%20recent%20Hamas%20attack%20is%20also%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20frequent%20attacks%20carried%20out%20on%20Jewish%20civilians%20by%20Arab%20militants%20infiltrating%20from%20neighbouring%20Syria%2C%20Jordan%20and%20Egypt%20in%20the%201950s%20and%20the%201960s%2C%20leading%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20to%20conduct%20raids%2C%20better%20known%20as%20Reprisal%20Operations.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201955%2C%20David%20Ben-Gurion%2C%20considered%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20founding%20father%2C%20ordered%20one%20such%20raid%20against%20the%20Egyptians%20near%20Gaza%20after%20the%20murder%20of%20an%20Israeli%20civilian%20inside%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20his%20retirement%20from%20politics%2C%20though%2C%20Ben-Gurion%20famously%20went%20on%20to%20settle%20down%20at%20a%20modest%20house%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Negev%20desert%2C%20not%20very%20far%20from%20Gaza.%20Apart%20from%20a%20photo%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20what%20hung%20at%20his%20home%20was%20one%20other%20frame.%20It%20was%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20from%20India%2C%20a%20black%20and%20white%20visage%20of%20the%20ambassador%20of%20non-violence%20hanging%20from%20a%20wall%20of%20his%20small%20study.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20Savarkar%2C%20Hegdewar%20or%20Golwalkar.%20No%2C%20not%20even%20Nehru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20spotting%20that%20photo%20of%20Gandhi%20all%20those%20years%20ago%2C%20all%20the%20shame%20that%20I%20had%20felt%20on%20finding%20the%20Swastika%20at%20Yad%20Vesham%20vanished%20into%20the%20hot%20desert%20air%20of%20Negev.%20It%20was%20seamlessly%20replaced%20by%20the%20pride%20that%20only%20an%20Indian%20could%20feel.%20That%20a%20man%20whose%20lifetime%20had%20seen%20so%20much%20violence%20on%20his%20community%20had%20come%20home%20to%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697869423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21114244%2FUntitled-design-1-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fgandhi-ben-gurion-israel-india-hindutva-mohammed-zubair-kobbi-shoshani%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Israeli%20diplomat%20going%20after%20an%20award-winning%20fact%20checker%20seemed%20to%20have%20given%20a%20green%20light%20to%20blood%20thirsty%20posts%20by%20Hindutva%20supporters.%20It%20triggered%20memories%20of%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20Holy%20Land%20some%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22