%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21111234%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20include%20%E2%80%9Cnon-heterosexual%20unions%E2%80%9D%20within%20the%20realm%20of%20marriage%20is%20heartbreaking%2C%20if%20not%20unsurprising.%20Especially%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20%3Cem%3ENavtej%20Singh%20Johar%20vs%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2018)%2C%20which%20decriminalised%20homosexuality%20and%20promised%20the%20queer%20community%20a%20rainbow%20of%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20top%20court%20said%20all%20the%20right%20things%2C%20it%20simply%20fell%20short%20of%20doing%20enough.%20Despite%20the%20plea%20for%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9Cman%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwoman%E2%80%9D%20(as%20used%20in%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act)%20to%20be%20read%20in%20a%20gender%20neutral%20manner%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20felt%20encumbered%20by%20institutional%20limitations.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20judgment%20authored%20by%20Justice%20S.%20Ravindra%20Bhat%20(on%20behalf%20of%20Justice%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20himself)%20disagreed%20with%20aspects%20of%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ENavtej%20Johar%3C%2Fem%3E%20judgment%20and%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20almost%20intractable%20difficulties%20in%20creating%2C%20through%20judicial%20diktat%2C%20a%20civil%20right%20to%20marry%20or%20a%20civil%20union%2C%20no%20less%2C%20of%20the%20kind%20that%20is%20sought%20by%20the%20petitioners%20in%20these%20proceedings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bhat%20also%20expressed%20an%20inability%20to%20allow%20same-sex%20couples%20the%20right%20to%20adopt%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELegal%20experts%20have%2C%20however%2C%20expressed%20disappointed%20with%20the%20narrow%2C%20restrictive%20and%20conservative%20approach%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20focus%20on%20the%20letters%20of%20the%20law%20than%20on%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20lawyer%20lamented%20in%20a%20private%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20Justice%20Bhat%20hung%20his%20robes%20on%20October%2020%20it%20may%20be%20pertinent%20to%20remember%20that%20this%20judgment%20alone%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20cast%20a%20pall%20over%20his%20otherwise%20sparkling%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20like%20crying%20that%20he%20is%20retiring%2C%20he%20was%20really%20fair%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20lawyer%20who%20practices%20on%20the%20criminal%20side%20told%20me%20on%20a%20phone%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBoth%20as%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20and%20as%20a%20person%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20advocate%20added%20in%20a%20separate%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgainst%20manual%20scavenging%2C%20for%20speedy%20disposal%20of%20cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20judge%20of%20the%20top%20court%20Justice%20Bhat%20displayed%20a%20reform-oriented%20and%20empathetic%20approach.%20Right%20up%20to%20his%20last%20day%20in%20court%2C%20when%20he%20issued%20a%20slew%20of%20directions%2C%20with%20a%20firm%20reminder%20that%20%E2%80%9CUnion%20and%20States%20are%20duty%20bound%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20practice%20of%20manual%20scavenging%20is%20completely%20eradicated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Bhat%20and%20Aravind%20Kumar%20ordered%20that%20the%20compensation%20in%20cases%20of%20sewer%20deaths%20must%20be%20increased%20to%20Rs%2030%20lakhs%2C%20in%20cases%20of%20permanent%20disablement%20due%20to%20sewer%20operations%20to%20Rs%2020%20lakhs%2C%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakhs%20for%20other%20forms%20of%20disablement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20government%20data%20alone%20shows%20that%20339%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20to%20manual%20scavenging%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20Many%20others%20have%20been%20crippled%20by%20it.%20Their%20families%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20of%20us%20owe%20to%20this%20large%20segment%20of%20population%20who%20have%20remained%20unseen%2C%20unheard%20and%20muted%2C%20in%20bondage%20systematically%20trapped%20in%20inhuman%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20matter%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Bhat%20and%20Kumar%20also%20lamented%20the%20pendency%20of%20cases%20in%20the%20courts%20of%20the%20country%20and%20passed%20eleven%20directions%20for%20their%20speedy%20disposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20might%20add%2C%20there%20is%20already%20a%20problem%20of%20arbitrary%20arrests%20and%20limited%20adherence%20by%20the%20police%20to%20judicial%20guidelines%20(such%20as%20those%20passed%20in%20the%20cases%20of%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-arnesh-kumar-guidelines-arrest-section-498a-high-court-director-general-of-police-notifications-234044%5C%22%3EArnesh%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F7148380%2F%5C%22%3ESatendra%20Kumar%20Antil%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E).%20Data%20reveals%20that%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Indian%20jails%20are%20packed%20beyond%20capacity.%20And%20then%20the%20%E2%80%9Csnail%20pace%E2%80%9D%20(if%20one%20might%20borrow%20a%20phrase%20from%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20vocabulary)%20at%20which%20trials%20are%20carried%20out%20and%20bail%20orders%20are%20passed%20further%20amplifies%20the%20disease%2C%20depravation%20and%20despair%20that%20mark%20the%20life%20of%20an%20average%20Indian%20inmate.%20Thus%2C%20such%20directions%20hold%20immense%20timely%20relevance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeeping%20the%20survivor%20in%20mind%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20bench%20recently%20observed%20that%20the%20state%20is%20obligated%20(under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20Act%20or%20POCSO)%20to%20provide%20%E2%80%98support%20persons%E2%80%99%20to%20child%20survivors%20of%20sexual%20offences%20and%20that%20it%20should%20not%20be%20left%20to%20the%20discretion%20of%20the%20survivor%E2%80%99s%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202021%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Bhat%20and%20A.M.%20Khanwilkar%20had%20set%20aside%20a%20Bombay%20high%20court%20order%20that%20had%20granted%20bail%20to%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20accused%20on%20condition%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-tie-rakhi-bail-condition-asking-man-accused-of-sexual-assault-to-get-rakhi-tied-by-victim-171352%5C%22%3Ehe%20get%20a%20%E2%80%98rakhi%E2%80%99%20tied%20by%20the%20complainant%3C%2Fa%3E%20(and%20give%20her%20Rs%2011%2C000%20as%20per%20ritual%2C%20and%20take%20her%20blessings).%20Noting%20that%20such%20orders%20can%20potentially%20re-traumatise%20a%20survivor%2C%20the%20top%20court%20mandated%20a%20gender-sensitisation%20module%20for%20all%20judges%2C%20among%20other%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20simply%20Justice%20Bhat%E2%80%99s%20reform-oriented%20approach%20that%20deserves%20mention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20dissent%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fews-quota-a-stupefying-inversion-of-the-idea-of-equality%5C%22%3EEconomically%20Weaker%20Section%20(EWS)%20quota%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20compared%20with%20one%20of%20the%20great%20dissents%20of%20Indian%20judicial%20history%20(including%20that%20of%20Justice%20H.R.%20Khanna%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EADM%20Jabalpur%3C%2Fem%3E%20case.)%20The%20EWS%20quota%2C%20as%20upheld%20by%20the%20majority%20view%2C%20does%20not%20recognise%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20or%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes.%20Justice%20Bhat%20held%20that%20this%20exclusionary%20clause%20strikes%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeath%20knell%20to%20the%20equality%20and%20fraternity%20principle%20which%20permeates%20the%20equality%20code%20and%20non-discrimination%20principle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bhat%20displayed%20a%20degree%20of%20independence%20that%20many%20others%20might%20struggle%20with%2C%20especially%20when%20confronted%20by%20an%20overbearing%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20talk%20delivered%20online%20amid%20the%20pandemic%2C%20he%20asked%20the%20citizens%20to%20use%20their%20liberties%20to%20constantly%20question%20the%20authorities%20in%20power%20and%20to%20not%20be%20complacent%20about%20any%20encroachment%20of%20their%20rights.%20And%20he%2C%20himself%2C%20walked%20the%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemanding%20answers%20of%20the%20Executive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Justice%20Bhat%20was%20part%20of%20a%20bench%20(with%20Justices%20Chandrachud%20and%20L.%20Nageswarao%20Rao)%20that%20demanded%20answers%20from%20the%20government%20on%20its%20COVID-related%20policies.%20Observing%20(in%20a%20prior%20hearing)%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20dual%20pricing%20policy%20for%20the%20COVID%20vaccine%20was%20compelling%20the%20different%20state%20governments%20to%20compete%20with%20each%20other%20(while%20the%20pandemic%20raged%20and%20so%20many%20lives%20were%20lost%2C%20if%20one%20might%20add)%2C%C2%A0%20the%20bench%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20Constitution%20does%20not%20envisage%20courts%20to%20be%20silent%20spectators%20when%20constitutional%20rights%20of%20citizens%20are%20infringed%20by%20executive%20policies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCourts%20have%20often%20reiterated%20the%20expertise%20of%20the%20executive%20in%20managing%20a%20public%20health%20crisis%2C%20but%20have%20also%20warned%20against%20arbitrary%20and%20irrational%20policies%20being%20excused%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwide%20latitude%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20executive%20that%20is%20necessitated%20to%20battle%20a%20pandemic%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20further%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20court%2C%20as%20per%20its%20own%20admission%2C%20had%20only%20assumed%20%E2%80%9Ca%20dialogic%20jurisdiction%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20few%20days%20later%20(June%207)%2C%20the%20government%20itself%20announced%20the%20centralisation%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20drive%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20all%20vaccines%20will%20be%20given%20to%20the%20states%20for%20free.%20So%20even%20if%20it%20seems%20as%20if%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98own%E2%80%99%20decision%2C%20one%20might%20wonder%20if%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20take%20had%20something%20to%20do%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20killing%20of%20gangster%20Atiq%20Ahmed%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fhow-can-someone-just-come-and-shoot-someone-is-complicit-sc-on-atiq-ahmads-killing%5C%22%3EJustices%20Bhat%20and%20Kumar%20reportedly%20pulled%20up%20the%20UP%20police%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20explain%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehensive%20affidavit%E2%80%9D%20what%20went%20so%20wrong%20that%20the%20duo%20were%20killed%20while%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20on%20being%20informed%20later%20that%20Ahmed%E2%80%99s%20surviving%20sons%20(minors)%20wanted%20to%20reside%20with%20their%20family%20instead%20of%20a%20childcare%20institution%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20the%20same%20bench%C2%A0%20directed%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20to%20decide%20the%20matter%20afresh.%20Finally%2C%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20boys%20were%20released%20to%20the%20custody%20of%20their%20aunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20when%20the%20SC%20came%20to%20his%20court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPertinently%2C%20Justice%20Bhat%20was%20not%20one%20to%20be%20overawed%20by%20status%20or%20status%20quo%20%E2%80%93%20even%2010%20years%20prior%20to%20his%20elevation%20to%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202009%2C%20as%20a%20Delhi%20high%20court%20judge%2C%20Justice%20Ravindra%20Bhat%20dismissed%20an%20appeal%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20itself.%20Noting%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20power%20%E2%80%93%20judicial%20power%20being%20no%20exception%20%E2%80%93%20is%20held%20accountable%20in%20a%20modern%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20single-handedly%20opened%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20to%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act.%20This%20decision%20was%20upheld%20by%20the%20apex%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeyond%20the%20judge%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20not%20arguing%20that%20the%20good%20cancels%20out%20the%2C%20well%2C%20not-so-good.%20So%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20hits%20of%20Justice%20Bhat%E2%80%99s%20career%20is%20in%20no%20way%20discounting%20the%20misses%20that%20may%20have%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%20Justice%20Bhat%E2%80%99s%20judicial%20career%20spans%20nearly%20two%20decades%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20that%20cannot%20be%20fairly%20encapsulated%20in%20this%20piece.%20But%20who%20you%20are%20as%20a%20human%20being%20will%20always%20impact%20what%20you%20do%20as%20a%20judge.%20And%20so%2C%20Justice%20Bhat%20as%20a%20person%20also%20deserves%20a%20mention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20way%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20while%20those%20who%20could%20were%20hiding%20in%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20apartments%2C%20and%20migrant%20workers%2C%20rendered%20helpless%20and%20jobless%20by%20the%20suddenness%20of%20the%20lockdown%2C%20were%20desperately%20trying%20to%20flee%20the%20city%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20was%20reportedly%20seen%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Delhi%20distributing%20packets%20of%20food.%20Needless%20to%20add%2C%20that%20judge%20was%20S.%20Ravindra%20Bhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20form%20%3C%2Fem%3ELiveLaw%2C%20Leaflet%2C%20The%20Quint%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Economic%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMekhala%20Saran%20is%20studying%20Global%20Media%20and%20Digital%20Communications%20at%20SOAS%2C%20University%20of%20London.%20She%20has%20an%20LLB%20and%20an%20English%20honours%20degree%20and%20was%20formerly%20principal%20legal%20correspondent%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Quint.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697867027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21111234%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-ravindra-bhat-marriage-equality-legacy-supreme-court%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20good%20does%20not%20cancel%20out%20the%20not-so-good.%20But%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20hits%20of%20Justice%20Bhat%E2%80%99s%20career%20is%20in%20no%20way%20discounting%20the%20misses%20that%20may%20have%20been.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-ravindra-bhat-marriage-equality-legacy-supreme-court%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20World%20War%203%2C%20But%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%3A%20Eurasia%20Founder%20To%20NDTV%20On%20Israel-Gaza%20Crisis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697866440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fmalctsvg_manvi_640x480_21_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fshows%2Fserious-business-with-manvi-sinha-dhillon%2Fno-world-war-3-but-eurasia-founder-to-ndtv-on-israel-gaza-crisis-733406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fshows%2Fserious-business-with-manvi-sinha-dhillon%2Fno-world-war-3-but-eurasia-founder-to-ndtv-on-israel-gaza-crisis-733406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bhagavanth%20Kesari%20box%20office%20collection%20day%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697866236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104600373%2Cimgsize-1477672.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2