using%20an%20old%20printer%20or%20fax%20machine%2C%20which%20were%20common%20in%20the%20past%2C%20can%20be%20confusing%20for%20them.%20This%20lack%20of%20knowledge%20can%20make%20them%20feel%20like%20they're%20not%20good%20enough.%20The%20workplace%20should%20help%20bridge%20this%20generation%20gap%20in%20tech%20to%20make%20everyone%20feel%20supported%20and%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2Ffeb%2F27%2Fgen-z-tech-shame-office-technology-printers%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20tech%20company%20HP%20coined%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3Btech%20shame%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20define%20how%20overwhelmed%20young%20people%20felt%20using%20basic%20office%20tools.%20According%20to%20the%20study%2C%20one%20in%20five%20young%20office%20workers%20reported%20%26quot%3Bfeeling%20judged%20for%20having%20tech%20issues%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20made%20them%20less%20likely%20to%20ask%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20another%20survey%2C%20the%20employment%20firm%20LaSalle%20Agency%20found%20that%20almost%20half%20of%20the%20class%20of%202022%20felt%20%26quot%3Bunderprepared%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20technical%20skills%20relevant%20for%20entering%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20Tech%20Shame%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETech%20shaming%20is%20when%20people%20make%20others%20feel%20embarrassed%20or%20inadequate%20because%20they%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20use%20technology%20well.%20This%20can%20happen%20at%20home%2C%20work%2C%20or%20school%20and%20can%20come%20in%20various%20forms.%20Tech%20shaming%20can%20be%20harmful%20to%20a%20person's%20self-esteem%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20world%20where%20being%20tech-savvy%20is%20considered%20essential%20for%20success.%20It%20can%20also%20make%20people%20feel%20isolated%20and%20excluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETech%20shame%20can%20impact%20people%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20particularly%20challenging%20for%20Gen%20Z%20employees.%20They%20often%20face%20added%20pressure%20because%20their%20colleagues%20assume%20they%20can%20effortlessly%20navigate%20all%20technology%20due%20to%20their%20upbringing.%20However%2C%20this%20isn't%20always%20true%2C%20as%20older%20technology%20can%20still%20pose%20difficulties%20for%20younger%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2Ffeb%2F27%2Fgen-z-tech-shame-office-technology-printers%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gen%20Z%20workers%20tend%20to%20be%20well%20equipped%20to%20edit%20photos%20and%20videos%20all%20from%20their%20phones%20or%20use%20website%20builders%20like%20Squarespace%20and%20Wix.%20They%20grew%20up%20using%20apps%20to%20get%20work%20done%20and%20are%20used%20to%20the%20ease%20that%20comes%20with%20Apple%20operating%20systems.%20Their%20formative%20tech%20years%20were%20spent%20using%20software%20that%20exists%20to%20be%20user-friendly.%20But%20desktop%20computing%20is%20decidedly%20less%20intuitive.%20Things%20like%20files%2C%20folders%2C%20scanning%2C%20printing%2C%20and%20using%20external%20hardware%20are%20hallmarks%20of%20office%20life.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FSysadminhumor%2Fcomments%2Fzyh8mc%2Fi_was_told_that_gen_z_are_supposed_to_be_tech%2F%5C%22%3EI%20was%20told%20that%20Gen%20Z%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20tech%20savvy%E2%80%A6%20After%20far%20too%20many%20calls%2C%20I%20finally%20had%20to%20spell%20it%20out%20for%20them.%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2Fmowikn%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2Fmowikn%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FSysadminhumor%2F%5C%22%3ESysadminhumor%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EAre%20they%20familiar%20with%20the%20process%20of%20turning%20on%20a%20bulky%20computer%20monitor%2C%20considering%20many%20of%20them%20merely%20shut%20their%20personal%20laptops%20when%20they're%20finished%3F%20According%20to%20an%20IT%20professional%20on%20Reddit%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20often%20no.%20This%20IT%20worker%20has%20even%20gone%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20placing%20a%20sign%20over%20the%20power%20button%20on%20office%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697857920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-11%2Fcsdbn5s_multifunctionlaserprinteramazon_625x300_24_November_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwhat-exactly-is-tech-shame-and-why-does-it-impact-generation-z-4501684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tech%20shame%20can%20affect%20anyone%2C%20but%20Gen%20Z%20workers%20are%20often%20targeted%20because%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20tech-savvy.%20However%2C%20even%20Gen%20Z%20workers%20can%20struggle%20with%20older%20technology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwhat-exactly-is-tech-shame-and-why-does-it-impact-generation-z-4501684%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwhat-exactly-is-tech-shame-and-why-does-it-impact-generation-z-4501684%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwhat-exactly-is-tech-shame-and-why-does-it-impact-generation-z-4501684%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20Administration%20Proposes%20Changes%20In%20H-1B%20Visas%20To%20Improve%20Efficiency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20is%20proposing%20changes%20in%20the%20H-1B%20foreign%20workers%20programme%20to%20improve%20efficiency%20by%20streamlining%20eligibility%2C%20providing%20more%20flexibility%20to%20F-1%20students%2C%20entrepreneurs%20and%20those%20working%20for%20non-profit%20bodies%20and%20ensuring%20better%20condition%20for%20other%20non-immigrant%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%2C%20which%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20published%20by%20the%20US%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services%20(USCIS)%20on%20October%2023%20in%20the%20Federal%20Register%20have%20been%20proposed%20without%20changing%20the%20Congress-mandated%2060%2C000%20limit%20on%20the%20number%20of%20such%20visas%20the%20US%20issues%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaking%20the%20proposed%20rules%20public%20for%20stakeholders%20to%20give%20their%20comments%20and%20feedback%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20(DHS)%20said%20the%20proposed%20changes%20in%20the%20rules%20are%20aimed%20at%20streamlining%20eligibility%20requirements%2C%20improving%20programme%20efficiency%2C%20providing%20greater%20benefits%20and%20flexibilities%20to%20employers%20and%20workers%2C%20and%20strengthening%20integrity%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20H-1B%20programme%20helps%20US%20employers%20hire%20the%20employees%20they%20need%20to%20meet%20their%20business%20needs%20and%20remain%20competitive%20in%20the%20global%20marketplace%2C%20while%20adhering%20to%20all%20US%20worker%20protection%20norms%20under%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Secretary%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20Alejandro%20N%20Mayorkas%20said%20the%20Biden-Harris%20administration's%20priority%20is%20to%20attract%20global%20talent%2C%20reduce%20undue%20burdens%20on%20employers%2C%20and%20prevent%20fraud%20and%20abuse%20in%20the%20immigration%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EObserving%20that%20the%20H-1B%20non-immigrant%20visa%20program%20allows%20US%20employers%20to%20temporarily%20employ%20foreign%20workers%20in%20speciality%20occupations%2C%20defined%20by%20statute%20as%20occupations%20that%20require%20highly%20specialised%20knowledge%20and%20a%20bachelor's%20or%20higher%20degree%20in%20the%20specific%20speciality%20or%20its%20equivalent%2C%20the%20DHS%20said%20the%20proposed%20rule%20would%20change%20how%20USCIS%20conducts%20the%20H-1B%20registration%20selection%20process%20to%20reduce%20the%20possibility%20of%20misuse%20and%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20current%20process%2C%20the%20more%20registrations%20that%20are%20submitted%20on%20behalf%20of%20an%20individual%2C%20the%20higher%20the%20chances%20of%20that%20person%20being%20selected%20in%20a%20lottery.%20Under%20the%20new%20proposal%2C%20each%20individual%20who%20has%20a%20registration%20submitted%20on%20their%20behalf%20would%20be%20entered%20into%20the%20selection%20process%20once%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20number%20of%20registrations%20submitted%20on%20their%20behalf%2C%20the%20DHS%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20improve%20the%20chances%20that%20a%20legitimate%20registration%20would%20be%20selected%20by%20significantly%20reducing%20or%20eliminating%20the%20advantage%20of%20submitting%20multiple%20registrations%20for%20the%20same%20beneficiary%20solely%20to%20increase%20the%20chances%20of%20selection.%20Furthermore%2C%20it%20could%20also%20give%20beneficiaries%20more%20choice%20between%20legitimate%20job%20offers%20because%20each%20registrant%20who%20submitted%20a%20registration%20for%20a%20selected%20beneficiary%20would%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20file%20an%20H-1B%20petition%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20beneficiary%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20proposed%20rule%2C%20the%20criteria%20for%20speciality%20occupation%20positions%20would%20be%20revised%20to%20reduce%20confusion%20between%20the%20public%20and%20adjudicators%20and%20to%20clarify%20that%20a%20position%20may%20allow%20a%20range%20of%20degrees%2C%20although%20there%20must%20be%20a%20direct%20relationship%20between%20the%20required%20degree%20field(s)%20and%20the%20duties%20of%20the%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20rule%20codifies%20that%20adjudicators%20generally%20should%20defer%20to%20a%20prior%20determination%20when%20no%20underlying%20facts%20have%20changed%20at%20the%20time%20of%20a%20new%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20proposed%20rule%2C%20certain%20exemptions%20to%20the%20H-1B%20cap%20would%20be%20expanded%20for%20certain%20nonprofit%20entities%20or%20governmental%20research%20organizations%20as%20well%20as%20beneficiaries%20who%20are%20not%20directly%20employed%20by%20a%20qualifying%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20DHS%20would%20also%20extend%20certain%20flexibility%20for%20students%20on%20an%20F-1%20visa%20when%20students%20are%20seeking%20to%20change%20their%20status%20to%20H-1B.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20department%20would%20establish%20new%20H-1B%20eligibility%20requirements%20for%20rising%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStrengthening%20integrity%20measures%20in%20addition%20to%20changing%20the%20selection%20process%2C%20misuse%20and%20fraud%20in%20the%20H-1B%20registration%20process%20would%20be%20reduced%20by%20prohibiting%20related%20entities%20from%20submitting%20multiple%20registrations%20for%20the%20same%20beneficiary.%20The%20rule%20would%20also%20codify%20USCIS'%20authority%20to%20conduct%20site%20visits%20and%20clarify%20that%20refusal%20to%20comply%20with%20site%20visits%20may%20result%20in%20denial%20or%20revocation%20of%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20DHS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20American%20Ajay%20Bhutoria%2C%20a%20leading%20advocate%20for%20immigration%20reform%20welcomed%20the%20proposed%20'Modernizing%20H1B%20Requirements%2C%20Providing%20Flexibility%20in%20the%20F-1%20Program%2C%20and%20Program%20Improvements%20Affecting%20Other%20Nonimmigrant%20Workers'%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20proposed%20changes%20mark%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20streamlining%20our%20immigration%20system%20and%20making%20it%20more%20accessible%20for%20highly%20skilled%20professionals%20and%20students%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20Bhutria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20proposed%20reform%20plan%20reflects%20a%20thoughtful%20approach%20to%20addressing%20some%20of%20the%20long-standing%20issues%20in%20the%20H-1B%20visa%20program%2C%20including%20providing%20more%20flexibility%20to%20F-1%20students%20and%20improving%20conditions%20for%20other%20nonimmigrant%20workers.%20We%20appreciate%20the%20DHS's%20commitment%20to%20fostering%20an%20environment%20that%20is%20conducive%20to%20attracting%20global%20talent%20and%20maintaining%20the%20competitiveness%20of%20American%20industries%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhutoria%20said.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697857920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-04%2Fus-visa-us-immigration-istock_650x400_41524626692.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiden-administration-proposes-changes-in-h-1b-visa-system-to-improve-efficiency-4501602%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Biden%20administration%20is%20proposing%20changes%20in%20the%20H-1B%20foreign%20workers%20programme%20to%20improve%20efficiency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiden-administration-proposes-changes-in-h-1b-visa-system-to-improve-efficiency-4501602%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiden-administration-proposes-changes-in-h-1b-visa-system-to-improve-efficiency-4501602%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiden-administration-proposes-changes-in-h-1b-visa-system-to-improve-efficiency-4501602%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Guadeloupe%20to%20declare%20red%20alert%20as%20Hurricane%20Tammy%20nears%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697857681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104597588%2Cimgsize-112910.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world