ms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104597252.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBrazil's%20President%20Luiz%20Inacio%20Lula%20da%20Silva%20will%20partially%20veto%20a%20bill%20that%20restricts%20Indigenous%20groups'%20claims%20to%20ancestral%20lands%2C%20overriding%20Congress's%20recent%20approval%20of%20the%20legislation.%20The%20president's%20veto%20will%20reject%20a%20core%20stipulation%20of%20the%20bill%20that%20only%20recognized%20Indigenous%20peoples'%20right%20to%20claim%20territories%20they%20occupied%20or%20disputed%20legally%20in%20October%201988.%20The%20land%20rights%20legislation%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20counteract%20Lula's%20efforts%20to%20protect%20the%20environment%20and%20Indigenous%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fbrazil-president-vetoes-bill-limiting-indigenous-land-claims%2Farticleshow%2F104597252.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fbrazil-president-vetoes-bill-limiting-indigenous-land-claims%2Famp_articleshow%2F104597252.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fbrazil-president-vetoes-bill-limiting-indigenous-land-claims%2Famp_articleshow%2F104597252.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elation%20and%20Disappointment%3A%20The%20Story%20of%20Bengal's%20Durga%20Puja%20Economy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20192600%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-11-at-10.26.01-PM-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Durga%20Puja%20kicks%20off%20in%20earnest%20today%2C%20it%20is%20time%20to%20recognise%20that%20along%20with%20being%20a%20cultural%20extravaganza%2C%20it%20is%20an%20economic%20powerhouse%20in%20its%20own%20right.%20The%20festival%20brings%20together%20diverse%20communities%20and%2C%20in%20the%20process%2C%20fosters%20a%20financial%20ecosystem%20that%20involves%20transactions%20of%20significant%20amount%20across%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20weeks%20preceding%20each%20Puja%2C%20the%20traditional%20shopping%20destinations%20such%20as%20Hatibagan%2C%20Gariahat%2C%20and%20New%20Market%20in%20Kolkata%20extend%20their%20operating%20hours%20well%20into%20the%20night.%20Last%20week%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20had%20to%20shut%20a%20vital%20thoroughfare%20to%20vehicular%20traffic%20to%20contain%20the%20pre-Puja%20shopping%20rush.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20Dharmatala%2C%20Farhan%20Sheikh%2C%20a%20retailer%20of%20readymade%20garments%20said%20that%20uptick%20in%20business%20is%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20timing%20of%20people%20receiving%20their%20salary%20bonuses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20time%20when%20many%20government%20and%20non-government%20employees%2C%20as%20well%20as%20labourers%2C%20do%20their%20festive%20shopping.%20Our%20sales%20reached%20their%20peak%20during%20the%20last%20one%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAjay%20Gupta%20has%20been%20selling%20readymade%20clothes%20on%20the%20footpath%20of%20Gariahat%20in%20south%20Kolkata%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20people%20from%20both%20religions%2C%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%2C%20used%20to%20kickstart%20their%20Puja%20shopping%20after%20August%2015.%20The%20entire%20market%20revolved%20around%20the%20festival%20throughout%20the%20year.%20However%2C%20after%202014%2C%20the%20market%20experienced%20a%20series%20of%20setbacks%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20chit-fund%20scams%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fthis-year-the-durga-puja-returned-to-its-core-group-those-who-cant-celebrate-it%5C%22%3Eimpact%20of%20COVID%20and%20subsequent%20lockdowns%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fdurga-puja-history-unesco-cultural-heritage%5C%22%3EKolkata%E2%80%99s%20Durga%20Puja%20Is%20Social%2C%20Cultural%20and%20Never%20Adequately%20Religious%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20chit%20fund%20scam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20Ponzi%20schemes%20in%20Indian%20history%2C%20continues%20to%20have%20a%20devastating%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20millions%20of%20people.%20An%20estimated%202%20million%20investors%2C%20mostly%20from%20poor%20and%20lower%20middle-class%20backgrounds%2C%20lost%20over%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crores%20in%20it.%20Many%20investors%20lost%20their%20life%20savings%20and%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20and%20its%20investment%20climate%20took%20a%20beating.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGupta%20feels%20that%20the%20scams%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20lockdowns%20might%20explain%20why%20the%20shopping%20picks%20up%20much%20later%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20odds%20with%20the%20sellers%20on%20the%20footpath%2C%20the%20upmarket%20malls%20are%20upbeat.%20%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20last%20year%2C%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20Puja%20market%20is%20thriving.%20We%20have%20seen%20an%20increase%20in%20footfall%20and%20sales.%20Our%20primary%20estimate%20suggests%20that%20the%20business%20in%20our%20malls%20has%20grown%20by%2030%25%20since%20last%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ramesh%20Pandey%2C%20director%20at%20Ambuja%20Reality%2C%20who%20manages%20two%20malls%20in%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERetail%20is%20widely%20understood%20to%20be%20the%20primary%20driving%20force%20behind%20financial%20activity%20during%20the%20Puja%20season%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20chunk%20of%20the%20total%20business.%20For%20small-scale%20retailers%20though%2C%20the%20July%20fire%20at%20Malangala%20Hat%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20garment%20markets%20in%20eastern%20India%2C%20dealt%20a%20severe%20blow.%20While%20the%20market%20has%20since%20reopened%2C%20a%20segment%20of%20retailers%20shifted%20towards%20direct%20business%20with%20Delhi%20and%20Surat%2C%20worsening%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20wholesalers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20193324%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-11-at-10.26.03-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20193324%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-11-at-10.26.03-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20193324%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-11-at-10.26.03-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20193324%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-11-at-10.26.03-PM-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681090%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShoppers%20ahead%20of%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20in%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Kolkata.%20Photo%3A%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20while%20Kolkata%20may%20have%20seen%20retail%20activity%2C%20the%20picture%20has%20been%20grim%20in%20handicrafts%20hubs%20across%20the%20state.%20At%20Shantipur%20and%20Fulia%20in%20Nadia%20district%2C%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20handloom%20industry%20in%20the%20state%2C%20declining%20product%20demand%20and%20insufficient%20government%20support%20plague%20artisans.%20Both%20regions%20have%20thousand-year-old%20heritages%20and%20both%20grapple%20with%20reduced%20product%20demand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESomen%20Pal%2C%20a%20Shantipur%20businessman%20connected%20to%20the%20industry%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20area%2C%2057%20handloom%20units%20have%20closed%20down%20since%20the%20lockdown%20in%202020.%20The%20traditional%20weaving%20community%20now%20confronts%20the%20threat%20of%20extinction%2C%20as%20weavers%20disassemble%20their%20looms%20en%20masse%20and%20seek%20migrant%20labour%20opportunities.%20The%20younger%20generation%20shows%20minimal%20interest%20in%20weaving%2C%20as%20they%20have%20discovered%20more%20financially%20rewarding%20prospects%20in%20other%20fields%2C%20where%20their%20hard%20work%20leads%20to%20significantly%20higher%20earnings%20compared%20to%20the%20modest%20returns%20from%20weaving.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEconomist%20Abhiroop%20Sarkar%20notes%20that%20the%20lockdown%20has%20two%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COne%20group%20faced%20a%20loss%20of%20income%2C%20while%20another%20group%2C%20driven%20by%20unmet%20demand%2C%20ventured%20into%20the%20market.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20market%20is%20on%20the%20path%20to%20becoming%20relatively%20prosperous%2C%20although%20not%20entirely%20restored%20to%20its%20previous%20economic%20conditions.%20Nonetheless%2C%20this%20shift%20has%20had%20an%20impact%20on%20those%20who%20lost%20their%20jobs%20or%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarkar%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fdurga-puja-washed-out-for-kolkatas-idol-makers%5C%22%3EDurga%20Puja%20Washed%20Out%20for%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20Idol%20Makers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20a%20British%20Council%20study%20estimated%20the%20puja%20economy%20at%20approximately%20Rs%2032%2C000%20crore%2C%20contributing%20to%202.6%25%20of%20the%20state%20domestic%20product.%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20estimated%20the%20figure%20will%20reach%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20state%20starved%20of%20jobs%2C%20this%20%E2%80%9CDurga%20Puja%20economy%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20lifeline%20for%20thousands%20of%20families%2C%20serving%20as%20their%20primary%20source%20of%20income.%20From%20crafting%20intricate%20idols%20to%20illuminating%20the%20city%20and%20creating%20stunning%20designs%2C%20families%20across%20generations%20are%20heavily%20involved%20in%20the%20preparations.%20The%20Pujas%E2%80%99%20essence%20thrives%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20notable%20shift%20in%20the%20landscape%20of%20business%20operations%2C%20particularly%20with%20a%20marked%20increase%20in%20locally-owned%20businesses%2C%20predominantly%20led%20by%20women%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20influence%20of%20social%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20one%20year%20ago%2C%20Trinanka%20Poddar%2C%20fresh%20out%20of%20college%2C%20launched%20her%20handbag%20venture%20from%20her%20residence%20in%20Habra%20in%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20with%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20Leveraging%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20she%20initially%20focused%20on%20a%20local%20customer%20base%20but%20gradually%20expanded%20her%20reach.%20Just%20ahead%20of%20the%20Puja%20season%2C%20Trinanka%20ventured%20into%20offline%20retail%20with%20the%20opening%20of%20her%20first%20physical%20store.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Amrita%20Biswas%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Nadia%E2%80%99s%20Badkulla%2C%20has%20been%20running%20a%20clothing%20business%20for%20the%20past%20six%20years%20from%20her%20home.%20This%20time%2C%20she%20has%20invested%20nearly%20Rs%208%20lakhs%20to%20open%20her%20own%20store.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20small%20towns%2C%20not%20everyone%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20in%20hand.%20However%2C%20during%20the%20Puja%20season%2C%20it%E