to%20achieve%20the%20target%20of%20257%20here%20on%20Thursday%2C%20when%20Nasum%20Ahmed%20sent%20a%20delivery%20down%20the%20leg%20side%2C%20which%20surprisingly%20was%20also%20not%20adjudged%20a%20wide%20by%20the%20on-field%20umpire%20Richard%20Kettleborough.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbangladesh-captain-breaks-silence-on-virat-kohli-wide-ball-controversy-in-world-cup-match-vs-india-4498740%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbangladesh-captain-breaks-silence-on-virat-kohli-wide-ball-controversy-in-world-cup-match-vs-india-4498740%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fbangladesh-captain-breaks-silence-on-virat-kohli-wide-ball-controversy-in-world-cup-match-vs-india-4498740%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Seeks%20Total%20Ban%20On%20Crackers%20Across%20NCR%20Region%20In%20Meet%20With%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20meeting%20of%20states%20with%20the%20Centre%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20urged%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20to%20impose%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20firecracker%20burning%20and%20the%20movement%20of%20diesel%20buses%20across%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20told%20reporters%20here%20that%20Union%20Environment%20Minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20environment%20ministers%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20During%20this%20meeting%2C%20Delhi%20suggested%20several%20measures%20to%20curb%20pollution%20in%20the%20entire%20NCR%20region%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Rai%20had%20requested%20the%20Centre%20to%20convene%20a%20meeting%20of%20all%20NCR%20states%20to%20collaboratively%20develop%20an%20action%20plan%20to%20combat%20pollution%20during%20the%20winter%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Mr%20Yadav%2C%20Mr%20Rai%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20has%20taken%20numerous%20steps%20to%20curb%20air%20pollution%20during%20the%20winter%20season%20but%20these%20steps%20won't%20be%20effective%20unless%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20address%20the%20sources%20of%20pollution%20in%20the%20NCR%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20independent%20environmental%20think%20tank%20Centre%20for%20Science%20and%20Environment%20(CSE)%2C%2031%20per%20cent%20of%20Delhi's%20pollution%20originates%20from%20sources%20within%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20while%2069%20per%20cent%20stems%20from%20sources%20in%20NCR%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Rai%20stressed%20that%20the%20states%20in%20the%20NCR%20should%20enforce%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20firecrackers%20and%20stubble%20burning%20across%20the%20region%20and%20only%20permit%20CNG%20and%20electric%20vehicles%20to%20ply.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20industrial%20units%20in%20NCR%20states%20still%20use%20polluting%20fuels.%20They%20should%20be%20swiftly%20converted%20to%20piped%20natural%20gas.%20The%20highly%20polluting%20brick%20kilns%20operating%20in%20NCR%20states%20should%20be%20required%20to%20adopt%20zig-zag%20technology%20to%20mitigate%20pollution%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20electricity%20should%20be%20made%20available%20to%20all%20housing%20societies%20in%20NCR%20states%20to%20reduce%20reliance%20on%20diesel%20generators.%20The%20concerned%20state%20governments%20should%20also%20redirect%20non-destined%20vehicles%20from%20their%20point%20of%20origin%20on%20the%20Eastern%20and%20Western%20Peripheral%20Expressways%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20organised%20a%20run%20on%20Friday%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20effects%20of%20air%20pollution%20and%20to%20seek%20public%20support%20in%20improving%20the%20city's%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Rai%20said%20officials%20from%20various%20Delhi%20government%20departments%20participated%20in%20the%20'Run%20Against%20Pollution'%20event%20and%20pledged%20to%20use%20public%20transport%2C%20turn%20off%20vehicle%20engines%20when%20the%20traffic%20signal%20turns%20red%20and%20maintain%20clean%20surroundings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20plans%20to%20relaunch%20the%20'Red%20Light%20On%20Gaadi%20Off'%20campaign%20to%20combat%20vehicular%20pollution%20in%20the%20city.%20Another%20public%20awareness%20campaign%2C%20'Patakhe%20Nahi%20Diye%20Jalao%2C'%20will%20be%20reintroduced%20to%20discourage%20the%20burning%20of%20firecrackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20accordance%20with%20the%20practice%20of%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20Delhi%20had%20last%20month%20announced%20a%20comprehensive%20ban%20on%20the%20manufacturing%2C%20storage%2C%20sale%20and%20use%20of%20firecrackers%20within%20the%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20government%20also%20introduced%20a%2015-point%20action%20plan%20to%20mitigate%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20capital%20during%20the%20winter%20season%2C%20focusing%20on%20addressing%20dust%20pollution%2C%20vehicular%20emissions%2C%20and%20open%20burning%20of%20garbage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpecific%20action%20plans%20for%20each%20of%20the%2013%20air%20pollution%20hotspots%20in%20Delhi%20have%20been%20developed%20based%20on%20real-time%20air%20quality%20data%20collected%20from%2040%20monitoring%20stations%20in%20the%20capital.%20There%20are%20already%20ongoing%20campaigns%20to%20combat%20dust%20pollution%20and%20industrial%20emissions.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697856420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-11%2Fh6h6a2bg