wire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20144110%2Fajin-k-s-bOoEVNhRX_k-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98A%20leader%20is%20best%20when%20people%20barely%20know%20he%20exists%2C%20when%20his%20work%20is%20done%2C%20his%20aim%20fulfilled%2C%20they%20will%20say%3A%20we%20did%20it%20ourselves.%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Lao%20Tzu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20a%20woman%20became%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20in%20Maharashtra%20was%20in%20the%20year%202010.%20As%20expected%2C%20there%20was%20great%20rejoicement%20among%20the%20public%2C%20especially%20women%20since%20another%20male%20bastion%20had%20been%20scaled.%20My%20first%20month%20at%20the%20job%20was%20therefore%20spent%20responding%20to%20enthusiastic%20felicitations%20from%20Punekars%20and%20giving%20them%20audience.%20I%20was%20relieved%20to%20have%20returned%20to%20work%20after%20a%20nearly%20year-long%20leave%20and%20did%20not%20mind%20the%20balance%20of%20life%20tilting%20more%20towards%20my%20chosen%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20eighth-largest%20metropolis%20in%20India%2C%20Pune%20is%20the%20cultural%20capital%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20also%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Queen%20of%20the%20Deccan%E2%80%99.%20It%20has%20a%20growing%20industrial%20hinterland%2C%20replete%20with%20information%20technology%2C%20engineering%20and%20automotive%20companies.%20The%20city%20is%20famous%20for%20cultural%20activities%2C%20classical%20music%20recitals%2C%20a%20vibrant%20theatre%20and%20literary%20scene.%20Besides%20being%20recognized%20as%20a%20seat%20of%20learning%20%E2%80%93%20some%20call%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98Oxford%20of%20the%20East%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Pune%20has%20made%20a%20definitive%20mark%20on%20the%20world%20of%20sports%20too.%20During%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20it%20gained%20further%20international%20recognition%20as%20the%20local%20Serum%20Institute%20of%20India%20produced%20and%20exported%20the%20much%20sought-after%20AstraZeneca%20%E2%80%98Covishield%E2%80%99%20vaccine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20the%20initial%20formalities%20of%20taking%20over%20as%20Commissioner%2C%20I%20started%20visiting%20all%20the%20police%20stations%20in%20Pune.%20Having%20lived%20there%20and%20worked%20at%20the%20local%20CID%20headquarters%2C%20I%20was%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20crime%20situation%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20important%20for%20me%20to%20be%20properly%20visible%20to%20the%20Pune%20police%20team.%20I%20believe%20that%20a%20leader%20has%20to%20be%20present%20and%20approachable%20to%20those%20she%20claims%20to%20lead.%20During%20my%20police%20station%20visits%2C%20we%20would%20hold%20regular%20meetings%20with%20the%20staff%20as%20well%20as%20local%20citizens%20in%20order%20to%20listen%20to%20their%20views%20on%20policing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20368px)%2085vw%2C%20368px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20144149%2FMadam-Commissioner-front-cover.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22368%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20144149%2FMadam-Commissioner-front-cover.jpg%20781w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20144149%2FMadam-Commissioner-front-cover-195x300.jpg%20195w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20144149%2FMadam-Commissioner-front-cover-666x1024.jpg%20666w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681022%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22565%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMeeran%20Chadha%20Borwankar%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EMadam%20Commissioner%3A%20The%20Extraordinary%20Life%20of%20an%20Indian%20Police%20Chief%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EPan%20Macmillan%20India%20(October%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20I%20felt%20disappointed%20by%20the%20quality%20of%20police%20investigation%20I%20observed%20during%20these%20visits.%20A%20few%20times%20I%20even%20left%20the%20police%20stations%20in%20anguish.%20While%20CBI%20and%20Mumbai%20crime%20branch%20officers%20had%20time%20to%20pursue%20cases%20assiduously%20and%20without%20interruptions%2C%20police%20officers%20in%20Pune%20were%20always%20running%20around%20in%20circles%20attending%20to%20multifarious%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20too%20many%20VIP%20visits%2C%20festival%20celebrations%2C%20agitations%2C%20protests%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth.%20Lethargy%20and%20corruption%20too%20had%20seeped%20in.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20appreciated%20the%20cordial%20citizen%E2%80%93police%20relations%20in%20the%20city.%20As%20with%20most%20organizations%2C%20about%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20staff%20were%20highly%20motivated%20and%20efficient%2C%20another%2020%20per%20cent%20were%20shirkers%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%20lot%20preferred%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20fence.%20Our%20team%20concentrated%20on%20bringing%20these%20fence-sitters%20over%20to%20the%20mainstream%20motivated%20workforce.%20But%20I%20must%20admit%20that%20we%20could%20probably%20rope%20in%20only%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20fence-sitters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20these%20circumstances%2C%20I%20finalized%20the%20three%20projects%20that%20I%20would%20undertake%20during%20my%20tenure.%20The%20first%20community%20police%20project%20was%20named%20%E2%80%98Pune%20Police%20Vidyarathi%20Abhiyan%E2%80%99.%20As%20part%20of%20it%2C%20we%20offered%20unpaid%20internships%20to%20college%20students%20at%20all%20police%20stations.%20The%20basic%20aim%20was%20to%20familiarize%20students%20with%20police%20operations.%20While%20working%20on%20my%20doctorate%2C%20I%20had%20surveyed%20about%20a%20hundred%20college%20students%20and%20they%20had%20shown%20keen%20interest%20in%20learning%20how%20the%20police%20functioned.%20The%20additional%20commissoner%20Sanjay%20Lathkar%20and%20his%20team%20prepared%20a%20detailed%20syllabus%20that%20the%20student%20interns%20would%20have%20to%20complete.%20The%20internships%20were%20advertised%20on%20the%20city%20police%20website%20and%20publicized%20widely.%20Many%20local%20colleges%20including%20the%20management%20department%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pune%20participated%20by%20sending%20their%20students%20to%20nearby%20police%20stations.%20The%20youngsters%20always%20responded%20enthusiastically.%20An%20intern%20in%20fact%20apprehended%20a%20chain%20snatcher%20in%20an%20area%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20Hadapsar%20police%20station.%20The%20university%E2%80%99s%20female%20students%20insisted%20on%20accompanying%20the%20Chaturshringi%20police%20officers%20during%20night%20rounds.%20These%20student%E2%80%93police%20collaborations%20yielded%20many%20interesting%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20a%20year%20of%20these%20internships%20and%20upon%20consultation%20with%20Dr%20C.%20M.%20Chitale%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20management%20department%20at%20the%20university%2C%20we%20reviewed%20the%20usefulness%20of%20the%20programme.%20Questionnaires%20were%20drafted%20and%20presented%20to%20the%20interns.%20Students%20of%20New%20Law%20College%2C%20Shri%20Siddhivinayak%20College%20for%20Women%20and%20Maharshi%20Karve%20Stree%20Shikshan%20Samstha%20participated%20in%20the%20survey.%20Almost%2094%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20students%20said%20that%20mutual%20relations%20between%20the%20police%20and%20the%20common%20man%20improve%20through%20such%20initiatives%3B%2095.6%20per%20cent%20stated%20that%20they%20no%20longer%20felt%20afraid%20of%20the%20police%20after%20their%20internship%3B%2094.7%20per%20cent%20said%20they%20would%20recommend%20such%20internship%20programmes%20to%20their%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20called%20the%20second%20community%20police%20initiative%20%E2%80%98Chowki%20Sabalikaran%E2%80%99%2C%20through%20which%20we%20intended%20to%20improve%20the%20efficacy%20of%20police%20chowkies.%20Pune%20is%20probably%20the%20only%20city%20in%20Maharashtra%20where%20citizens%20approach%20their%20chowkis%20to%20lodge%20FIRs.%20Each%20police%20station%20supervises%20the%20work%20of%20two%20or%20three%20such%20chowkis.%20Since%20their%20jurisdictions%20are%20small%2C%20the%20citizens%20and%20chowki%20police%20staff%20know%20one%20another%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20part%20of%20this%20exercise%2C%20the%20IndSearch%20Institute%20of%20Management%20Studies%20%26amp%3B%20Research%20was%20entrusted%20the%20task%20of%20training%20the%20chowki%20personnel%20in%20conducting%20meetings%20with%20citizens.%20The%20institute%E2%80%99s%20faculty%20trained%20the%20police%20staff%20on%20how%20to%20draw%20agenda%20items%20in%20advance%2C%20take%20down%20meeting%20minutes%20and%20prepare%20reports%20of%20action%20taken.%20Professor%20Sham%20Wagh%20of%20the%20institute%20steered%20the%20project.%20After%20training%20sessions%20were%20conducted%20for%20all%20police%20chowkies%20in%20Pune%2C%20joint%20meetings%20were%20held%20to%20assess%20the%20implementation%20and%20impact%20of%20suggested%20improvements.%20The%20institute%20collected%20feedback%20from%20citizens%20and%20police%20officers%20on%20the%20usefulness%20of%20meetings%20and%20participation%20levels.%20They%20expressed%20their%20overall%20satisfaction%20with%20regards%20to%20the%20conduct%20and%20recording%20of%20the%20meetings%20post%20training%20sessions.%20Even%20though%20there%20were%20times%20when%20specified%20agenda%20items%20were%20not%20pursued%2C%20the%20faculty%20noted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98participation%20of%20citizens%20is%20more%20important%20and%20an%20encouraging%20factor%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20third%20project%20was%20the%20creation%20of%20%E2%80%98Study%20Circles%E2%80%99%20in%20each%20police%20station%20by%20inviting%20local%20experts%20to%20discuss%20diverse%20topics.%20Many%20inspectors%20took%20keen%20interest%20in%20these%20sessions%20and%20reported%20that%20eminent%20Punekars%20were%20more%20than%20willing%20to%20share%20their%20knowledge%20with%20police%20officers.%20In%20my%20profession%2C%20people%20tend%20to%20get%20sucked%20into%20routine%20police%20work%20and%20thereby%20start%20stagnating.%20Study%20circles%20can%20help%20broaden%20our%20perspective%20and%20enrich%20us%20as%20individuals.%20Our%20endeavour%20therefore%20received%20a%20very%20positive%20response%20and%20has%20since%20been%20adopted%20by%20many%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20revived%20the%20%E2%80%98Mahila%20Dakshata%20Samitees%E2%80%99%20at%20all%20police%20stations%20in%20Pune.%20This%20stems%20from%20my%20belief%20that%20the%20police%20alone%20are%20insufficient%20to%20handle%20the%20ubiquitous%20issue%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20that%20collaboration%20with%20civil%20society%2C%20academicians%20and%20NGOs%20can%20improve%20our%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahila%20Dakshata%20Samitees%20in%20Maharashtra%20were%20constituted%20in%20the%20early%201980s%2C%20with%20local%20women%20being%20nominated%20to%20lead%20these%20groups%20and%20cooperate%20with%20police%20stations%20to%20help%20women%20victims.%20There%20were%20hardly%20any%20females%20in%20the%20police%20force%20in%20those%20days.%20Later%20on%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20introduced%20a%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20all%20government%20departments%2C%20leading%20to%20more%20women%20joining%20the%20police.%20While%20reactivating%20these%20committees%20we%20weeded%20out%20those%20who%20were%20not%20interested%20in%20the%20work%20these%20groups%20did%20%E2%80%93%20many%20had%20been%20appointed%20simply%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20their%20political%20allegiance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20two-day%20state-level%20conference%20was%20held%20to%20mark%20and%20celebrate%20twenty-five%20years%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Mahila%20Dakshata%20Samitees%E2%80%99.%20Women%20from%20far-flung%20corners%20of%20the%20state%20came%20to%20attend%20it%2C%20even%20though%20they%20had%20to%20fund%20the%20trips%20on%20their%20own%20as%20the%20Pune%20police%20could%20only%20make%20arrangements%20for%20their%20stay.%20Their%20sessions%20were%20highly%20interactive%20and%20their%20awareness%20about%20the%20latest%20legal%20amendments%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20was%20completely%20focused%20on%20ensuring%20the%20conference%E2%80%99s%20success%20until%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20a%20young%20woman%20took%20me%20by%20surprise.%20%E2%80%98Madam%20Commissioner%2C%E2%80%99%20she%20began%2C%20%E2%80%98is%20it%20a%20crime%20to%20have%20coffee%20in%20Pune%20late%20in%20the%20evening%3F%E2%80%99%20Feeling%20a%20bit%20baffled%2C%20I%20asked%20her%20to%20elaborate.%20Instead%2C%20she%20asked%20to%20see%20me.%20So%2C%20I%20invited%20her%20to%20visit%20my%20office%20between%204%20and%205%20p.m.%2C%20during%20the%20one%20hour%20I%20used%20to%20reserve%20for%20citizen%20walk-ins.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20came%20along%20with%20a%20friend%20and%20began%20recounting%20her%20story.%20A%20few%20days%20back%2C%20the%20two%20of%20them%20were%20having%20coffee%20at%20a%20cafe%20near%20the%20airport%20when%20a%20group%20of%20boys%20at%20the%20adjoining%20table%20started%20teasing%20them.%20Initially%20they%20ignored%20it%20but%20when%20their%20obnoxious%20behaviour%20became%20unbearable%2C%20they%20dialled%20police%20control%20room%2C%20seeking%20help.%20The%20police%20operator%20responded%20promptly%20but%20asked%20them%20why%20they%20were%20out%20so%20late%20in%20the%20evening.%20Could%20they%20not%20have%20had%20coffee%20at%20home%3F%20He%20was%20arrogant%20and%20rude.%20The%20young%20girls%20were%20livid%20and%20decided%20to%20approach%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPune%E2%80%99s%20police%20control%20room%20was%20on%20the%20same%20floor%20of%20the%20building%20as%20my%20office%20chamber.%20We%20had%20recently%20installed%20new%20technology%20that%20allowed%20us%20to%20record%20all%20our%20phone%20conversations%20with%20citizens.%20Since%20the%20girls%20had%20provided%20the%20exact%20date%20and%20time%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20I%20asked%20the%20control%20room%20officers%20to%20locate%20the%20conversation.%20When%20the%20recorded%20conversation%20was%20played%20to%20me%2C%20it%20became%20immediately%20clear%20that%20the%20police%20constable%20who%20had%20taken%20the%20call%20was%20indeed%20very%20rude.%20He%20was%20arguing%20with%20the%20girls%20instead%20of%20directing%20a%20nearby%20police%20vehicle%20to%20go%20to%20their%20aid.%20Without%20wasting%20any%20time%2C%20I%20transferred%20him%20out%20and%20initiated%20disciplinary%20action.%20Had%20these%20young%20women%20not%20taken%20the%20initiative%20to%20bring%20the%20control%20room%20operator%E2%80%99s%20unjustified%20conduct%20to%20my%20notice%2C%20he%20would%20have%20continued%20in%20the%20same%20vein.%20Two-way%20communication%20between%20citizens%20and%20police%20is%20only%20of%20mutual%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20was%20introducing%20various%20measures%20to%20strengthen%20citizen%E2%80%93police%20relations%2C%20this%20incident%20exposed%20the%20underbelly%20of%20the%20police%20as%20an%20organization.%20I%20realized%20that%20we%20still%20had%20miles%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Chr%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20excerpt%20from%20Meeran%20Chadha%20Borwankar%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3EMadam%20Commission%3Cem%3E%20was%20republished%20with%20permission%20from%20Pan%20Macmillan%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697855423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20144110%2Fajin-k-s-bOoEVNhRX_k-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fcitizen-police-relations-meeran-chadha-borwankar-excerpt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20exceprt%20from%20Meeran%20Chadha%20Borwankar's%20book%20'Madam%20Commissioner'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fcitizen-police-relations-meeran-chadha-borwankar-excerpt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Argentina%20election%3A%20Javier%20Milei%2C%20TikTok%20economist%2C%20leads%20polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697855315000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F153B8%2Fproduction%2F_131486968_gettyimages-1701087602.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67170266%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Can%20a%20former%20TV%20personality%20who's%20vowed%20to%20blow%20up%20Argentina's%20central%20bank%20win%20Sunday's%20elections%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A62%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67170266%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67170266.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67170266.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Pak%20PM%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20To%20Return%20Home%20Today%20After%20Four%20Years%20Of%20Self-Exile%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree-time%20Pakistani%20prime%20minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20will%20return%20home%20on%20Saturday%20after%20four%20years%20of%20self-imposed%20exile%2C%20primed%20to%20make%20a%20political%20comeback%20ahead%20of%20elections.%C2%A0The%20South%20Asian%20nation%20is%20facing%20overlapping%20security%2C%20economic%20and%20political%20crises%20ahead%20of%20polls%20already%20pushed%20back%20to%20January%202024%2C%20with%20Sharif's%20primary%20opponent%2C%20the%20fiercely%20popular%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20languishing%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20time%20for%20hope%20and%20celebration.%20His%20return%20bodes%20well%20for%20Pakistan's%20economy%20and%20its%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Khawaja%20Muhammad%20Asif%2C%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20Sharif's%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharif%20has%20spent%20the%20past%20several%20days%20in%20Dubai%2C%20and%20will%20fly%20from%20there%20to%20the%20capital%20Islamabad%2C%20then%20on%20to%20Lahore%2C%20where%20his%20supporters%20will%20gather%20for%20a%20welcome%20home%20rally%2C%20his%20party%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20return%20has%20been%20touted%20for%20months%20by%20the%20PML-N%2C%20whose%20leaders%20hope%20Sharif's%20political%20clout%20and%20%26quot%3Bman%20of%20the%20soil%26quot%3B%20swagger%20will%20revive%20its%20flagging%20popularity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20former%20leader%20has%20a%20conviction%20for%20graft%20and%20an%20unfinished%20prison%20sentence%20hanging%20over%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20Islamabad%20High%20Court%20granted%20protective%20bail%20to%20Sharif%20until%20Tuesday%2C%20removing%20the%20threat%20of%20immediate%20arrest%20when%20he%20lands%20back%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fheres-a-look-at-nawaz-sharifs-journey-ahead-of-his-arrival-in-pakistan-4500712%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESharif%20has%20been%20prime%20minister%20three%20times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20was%20ousted%20in%202017%20and%20given%20a%20lifetime%20disqualification%20from%20politics%20after%20being%20convicted%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20served%20less%20than%20a%20year%20of%20a%20seven-year%20sentence%20before%20getting%20permission%20to%20seek%20medical%20care%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20ignoring%20subsequent%20court%20orders%20to%20return%20during%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan's%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20fortunes%20changed%20when%20his%20brother%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20came%20to%20power%20last%20year%20and%20his%20government%20oversaw%20changes%20to%20the%20law%2C%20including%20limiting%20the%20disqualification%20of%20lawmakers%20from%20contesting%20elections%20to%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharif's%20return%20has%20likely%20been%20smoothed%20by%20a%20deal%20between%20the%20military%20establishment%20and%20his%20party%20to%20prevent%20significant%20legal%20hurdles%2C%20said%20analyst%20Zahid%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20some%20sort%20of%20arrangement%20with%20the%20military%20establishment%3B%20without%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20have%20decided%20to%20come%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOften%20draped%20in%20a%20red%20Gucci%20scarf%2C%20Sharif%20has%20seen%20his%20political%20fortunes%20rise%20and%20fall%20on%20his%20relationship%20with%20Pakistan's%20powerful%20military%20establishment%20--%20the%20country's%20true%20kingmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPoliticians%20in%20Pakistan%20are%20often%20tangled%20in%20legal%20proceedings%20that%20rights%20monitors%20say%20are%20orchestrated%20by%20the%20powerful%20military%2C%20which%20has%20ruled%20the%20country%20directly%20for%20more%20than%20half%20of%20its%20history%20and%20continues%20to%20enjoy%20immense%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFans%20call%20him%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Lion%20of%20Punjab%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20eastern%20and%20most%20populous%20province%20where%20his%20support%20is%20strongest%2C%20and%20he%20is%20known%20to%20parade%20big%20cats%20at%20extravagant%20political%20events%20drumming%20up%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20faces%20the%20tough%20task%20of%20winning%20over%20an%20electorate%20weary%20of%20dynastic%20politics%20and%20a%20young%20population%20that%20has%20been%20captured%20by%20Khan's%20social-media-savvy%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSharif's%20key%20challenge%20is%20first%20to%20establish%20himself%20and%20his%20party%20as%20viable%20options%20to%20replace%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20already%20popular%2C%20and%20secondly%20to%20turn%20around%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20political%20analyst%20Ayesha%20Siddiqa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697854980