%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20over%2050%20questions%20in%20parliament%20%E2%80%9Cpertaining%20directly%20to%20his%20business%20interests%E2%80%9D%20which%20targeted%20not%20just%20Modi%20but%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbusiness%20activities%20of%20M%2Fs%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20(2)%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20much-publicized%20Hindenburg%20Report%20contained%20direct%20references%20from%20the%20complaints%20filed%20by%20Smt.%20Moira%20against%20M%2Fs%20Adani%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdani%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2FNewsroom%2FMedia-Release%2FMedia-Statement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equick%20to%20issue%20a%20triumphant%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Dehadrai%E2%80%99s%20complaint%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Ccorroborated%E2%80%9D%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20charge%20that%20there%20was%20a%20wider%20%E2%80%9Carrangement%20to%20besmirch%20the%20reputation%20and%20interests%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20our%20chairman%20Mr.%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%9D.%20Significantly%2C%20the%20Adani%20statement%20alleged%20that%20recent%20news%20reports%20on%20the%20group%20by%20the%20%3Ci%3EFinancial%20Times%20%3C%2Fi%3Ewere%20also%20part%20of%20this%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnsolicited%20affidavit%20from%20Hiranandani%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Hiranandani%2C%20who%20describes%20himself%20as%20a%20close%20friend%20of%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20since%202017%2C%20issued%20an%20%E2%80%98affidavit%E2%80%99%20in%20which%20he%20endorsed%20two%20of%20the%20allegations%20Dehadrai%20had%20made.%20First%2C%20that%20he%20had%20used%20her%20login%20credentials%20to%20post%20questions%20on%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20portal%20and%20helped%20her%20draft%20questions%20about%20the%20Adani%20group.%20Second%2C%20that%20he%20had%20given%20her%20unspecified%20gifts%2C%20helped%20renovate%20her%20official%20MP%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20Delhi%20and%20provided%20%E2%80%9Csecretarial%20and%20logistical%20assistance%E2%80%9D%20for%20some%20of%20her%20travels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hiranandani%20did%20not%20corroborate%20the%20two%20most%20damaging%20charges%20Dehadrai%20and%20Dubey%20had%20levelled%20at%20Moitra.%20There%20is%20no%20cash%20payout%20%E2%80%98smoking%20gun%E2%80%99%20that%20government%20handlers%20evidently%20hoped%20he%20would%20deliver.%20Nor%20does%20he%20say%20the%20gifts%20he%20gave%20were%20in%20exchange%20for%20anything%20Moitra%20had%20done%20as%20an%20MP%2C%20least%20of%20all%20for%20asking%20questions%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20absence%20of%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20is%20further%20borne%20out%20by%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20claim%20in%20the%20affidavit%20that%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20targeting%20of%20Adani%20was%20driven%20not%20by%20his%20business%20interests%20or%20purported%20gifts%20but%20by%20what%20he%20described%20as%20her%20own%20political%20ambition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98impeccable%20reputation%E2%80%99%2C%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98rise%20of%20Adani%20created%20jeaousy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Moitra%20wanted%20to%20make%20her%20mark%20as%20an%20MP%20after%20getting%20elected%20in%202019%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20advised%20by%20her%20friends%20and%20advisors%20that%20the%20shortest%20possible%20route%20to%20fame%20is%20by%20personally%20attacking%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20theme%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20critics%20are%20possessed%20by%20the%20desire%20to%20%E2%80%98abuse%E2%80%99%20him%20%E2%80%93%20sounds%20familiar%20to%20those%20who%20have%20heard%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speeches%20%5Bsee%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fcompetition-among-congress-leaders-to-abuse-me-pm-modi-on-ravan-remark-1167376.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_