nt%20interactions%20with%E2%80%9D%20the%20business%20journalist%20Sucheta%20Dalal%20%E2%80%93%20known%20for%20her%20integrity%20and%20no-nonsense%20reporting%20on%20a%20range%20of%20big%20corporates%2C%20including%20Adani%20%E2%80%93%20and%20%E2%80%9Cjournalists%20from%20the%20%3Ci%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ci%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20the%20BBC%20and%20also%20with%20several%20Indian%20publications.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20foreign%20media%20outlets%20named%20have%20all%20earned%20the%20ill-will%20of%20the%20government%20for%20their%20coverage%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F7aadb3d7-4a03-44ba-a01e-8ddd8bce29ed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F06%2F21%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fbiden-modi-visit.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemocratic%20backsliding%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fwith-bbc-tax-raid-the-modi-cult-makes-india-the-smother-of-democracy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20own%20controversial%20role%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20riots%20of%202002%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHiranandani%20also%20identified%C2%A0%20the%20lawyers%20Shardul%20Shroff%20and%20Pallavi%20Shroff%20as%20individuals%20who%20were%20%E2%80%9Cfeeding%20%5BMoitra%5D%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20unverified%20information%20relating%20to%20Sh.%20Gautam%20Adani%20and%20his%20companies%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cassisting%20her%20in%20this%20targeted%20attack%E2%80%9D%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20someone%20with%20whom%20she%20had%20%E2%80%9Cinteractions%20with%E2%80%A6%20on%20matters%20relating%20to%20Adani%20companies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Gun%20put%20to%20head%E2%80%99%2C%20Moitra%20says%20about%20%E2%80%98dear%20friend%E2%80%99%20Hiranandani%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELate%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMahuaMoitra%2Fstatus%2F1715080166870004009%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%20issued%20a%20two-page%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98affidavit%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20which%20she%20called%20a%20%E2%80%9Cplea%20bargain%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20was%20not%20notarised%20and%20had%20not%20been%20officially%20released%20to%20the%20media%20by%20its%20signatory%20but%20was%20instead%20hurriedly%20%E2%80%98leaked%E2%80%99%C2%A0%20in%20order%20to%20fuel%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmedia%20circus%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20also%20said%20that%20Shardul%20Shroff%2C%20whom%20Hiranandani%20had%20dragged%20in%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20the%20brother%20of%20Cyril%20Shroff%20who%20has%20had%20a%20bitter%20separation%20of%20business%20from%20him.%20Cyril%20Shroff%20is%20Gautam%20Adani%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3Es%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3Esamdhi%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20on%20the%20SEBI%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3Es%20committee%20%5Bprobing%20the%20Hindenburg%20allegations%5D%20in%20total%20conflict%20of%20interest.%E2%80%9D%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fdarshan-hiranandani-affidavit-mahua-moitra-adani-amarchand-8992078%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShroffs%2C%20incidentally%2C%20have%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewarned%20Hiranandani%20that%20they%20may%20sue%20him%20for%20defamation%20for%20making%20%E2%80%9Creckless%2C%20malicious%E2%80%9D%20allegations%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHiranandani%2C%20who%20signed%20the%20%E2%80%98affidavit%E2%80%99%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Thursday%2C%20flew%20back%20to%20Dubai%20the%20same%20day.%20On%20Friday%2C%20he%20issued%20a%20notarised%20version%20of%20the%20same%20document%2C%20without%20explaining%20why%20he%20had%20rushed%20to%20issue%20a%20non-notarised%20affidavit%20the%20previous%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20a%20businessman%20like%20Hiranandani%20would%20only%20have%20signed%20a%20letter%20in%20this%20way%20if%20a%20%E2%80%98gun%20was%20put%20to%20his%20head%E2%80%99%2C%20Moitra%20described%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20letter%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20joke%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20clearly%20been%20drafted%20by%20some%20half-wit%20in%20the%20PMO%20who%20doubles%20up%20as%20a%20creative%20writer%20in%20the%20BJP%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3Es%20IT%20cell.%20It%20sings%20paeans%20to%20Modi%20and%20Gautam%20Adani%20while%20linking%20in%20every%20opponent%20of%20theirs%20to%20me%20and%20my%20alleged%20corruption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20Hiranandani%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdear%20friend%E2%80%9D%2C%20Moitra%20said%20that%20the%20PMO%20gave%20his%20father%20and%20him%20%E2%80%9C20%20minutes%20to%20sign%20this%20letter%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20threatened%20with%20a%20total%20shutdown%20of%20all%20their%20businesses.%20His%20father%20is%20in%20real%20estate%20which%20depends%20on%20government%20licenses.%20And%20he%20is%20in%20energy%2C%20data%20centres%20and%20semiconductor%20chip%20manufacturing%20which%20too%20depends%20on%20government%20licenses.%20He%20has%20over%2030%2C000%20crore%20investments%20in%20UP%20alone.%20They%20were%20told%20they%20will%20be%20finished%2C%20the%20CBI%20would%20raid%20them%20and%20all%20government%20business%20would%20stop%20and%20all%20PSU%20bank%20financing%20would%20be%20stopped%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20draft%20of%20this%20letter%20was%20sent%20by%20the%20PMO%20and%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20sign%20it.%20And%20it%20was%20leaked%20to%20the%20press%20immediately.%20This%20is%20in%20return%20for%20the%20government%20not%20doing%20a%20CBI%20investigation%20or%20not%20aggressively%20attacking%20their%20businesses.%20Though%20tragic%2C%20it%20is%20totally%20understandable%20that%20Darshan%20(who%20is%20a%20dear%20friend)%20would%20need%20to%20think%20of%20what%20is%20at%20stake%20for%20him%20here%20%E2%80%93%20namely%20the%20continuation%20of%20his%20family%20businesses%20built%20up%20over%20decades%20and%20the%20fate%20of%20thousands%20of%20employees%20%E2%80%93%20and%20buckle%20under%20pressure%20and%20sign%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20usual%20modus%20operandi%20of%20this%20BJP%20government%20or%20rather%20Gautam%20Adani%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3Es%20government%20run%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Moitra%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20552px)%2085vw%2C%20552px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21042050%2FJANUARY-24-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22552%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21042050%2FJANUARY-24-1.png%20480w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21042050%2FJANUARY-24-1-120x300.png%20120w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21042050%2FJANUARY-24-1-410x1024.png%20410w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681115%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221380%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAdani%2C%20Modi%2C%20Moitra%3A%20A%20Timeline%20%5BGraphic%3A%20The%20Wire%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20Hiranandani%20coerced%20by%20the%20PMO%20as%20Moitra%20alleges%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20circumstances%20under%20which%20the%20businessman%E2%80%99s%20affidavit%20appeared%20on%20Thursday%20were%20highly%20unusual.%20Affidavits%20are%20normally%20notarised%20and%20released%20publicly%20but%20the%20version%20which%20was%20put%20into%20circulation%20that%20night%20was%20not.%20Finally%20on%20Friday%20a%20notarised%20version%20of%20the%20same%20affidavit%20was%20released.%C2%A0%20So%20what%20was%20the%20tearing%20hurry%20on%20Thursday%3F%C2%A0%20Was%20Hiranandani%20asked%20by%20the%20government%20to%20issue%20a%20statement%20broadly%20corroborating%20Dehadrai%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20against%20Moitra%3F%20The%20question%20needs%20to%20be%20posed%20because%20he%20had%20neither%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20ethics%20committee%20of%20parliament%20or%20by%20any%20official%20investigating%20agency.%20The%20language%20of%20the%20affidavit%20seems%20to%20speak%20in%20two%20registers.%20One%20is%20personal%20and%20almost%20informal.%20The%20other%20is%20formal%20and%20%3Cem%3Esarkari%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20with%20lots%20of%20%E2%80%98Shris%E2%80%99%20and%20gushing%20remarks%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20classic%20hallmarks%20of%20official%20drafting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Hiranandani%20group%20has%20extensive%20and%20growing%20business%20interests%20in%20states%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP%20which%20renders%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20official%20threats%20and%20pressure.%20The%20past%20few%20years%20have%20seen%20many%20examples%20of%20the%20threat%20or%20even%20use%20of%20investigative%20agencies%20to%20ensure%20opposition%20politicians%20fall%20in%20line%20and%20soften%20up%20businessmen%20into%20accepting%20deals%20and%20arrangements%20that%20they%20might%20otherwise%20not%20be%20willing%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20happens%20next%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParliament%E2%80%99s%20ethics%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar%2C%20has%20called%20Dehadrai%20and%20Dubey%20for%20a%20hearing%20on%20October%2026.%20The%2015-member%20committee%20(comprising%20seven%20BJP%20MPs%20and%20one%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Shinde)%20MP%2C%20four%20Congress%20MP%2C%20and%20one%20each%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20BSP%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist))%20can%20recommend%20action%20be%20taken%20against%20Moitra%20but%20she%20would%20also%20have%20to%20be%20given%20a%20hearing.%20The%20ethics%20committee%20does%20not%20recommend%20expulsion%20and%20has%20never%20done%20it%2C%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%20PDT%20Achary%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20normally%20recommends%20suspension%2C%20at%20most%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWill%20Hiranandani%20be%20asked%20to%20give%20evidence%20to%20the%20ethics%20committee%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20affidavit%20is%20to%20become%20the%20grounds%20for%20any%20punitive%20action%20against%20Moitra%2C%20the%20businessman%20will%20have%20to%20be%20subjected%20to%20cross-questioning.%20Dehadrai%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20businessman%20paid%20cash%20as%20a%20bribe%20to%20Moitra%20but%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20otherwise%20sweeping%20affidavit%20makes%20no%20such%20claim.%20If%20he%20appears%20before%20the%20committee%2C%20he%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20asked%20whether%20Dehadrai%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20he%20gave%20money%20to%20Moitra%20is%20true.%20Answering%20no%20would%20discredit%20Dehadrai%20and%20weaken%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20case.%20And%20if%20circumstances%20prevail%20upon%20him%20to%20say%20yes%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20so%20dramatically%20improve%20upon%20his%20affidavit%20would%20discredit%20him%20as%20a%20witness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWould%20the%20government%20handlers%20who%20extracted%20the%20affidavit%20from%20Hiranandani%20want%20a%20situation%20where%20he%20might%20end%20up%20deviating%20from%20a%20carefully%20framed%20narrative%3F%20Perhaps%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECan%20the%20government%20move%20to%20have%20Moitra%20expelled%20from%20parliament%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20to%20recommend%20expulsion%20rests%20with%20the%20privileges%20committee%20or%20any%20special%20committee%20appointed%20by%20the%20house.%20Further%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20speaker%20has%20no%20power%20to%20punish%20a%20member.%20This%20power%20vests%20in%20the%20house.%20Only%20the%20house%20can%20expel%20a%20member%20on%20a%20proper%20motion%20which%20will%20be%20voted%20by%20all%20MPs%2C%20among%20whom%20the%20BJP%20has%20a%20majority%2C%20says%20Achary.%20But%20this%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done%2C%20even%20given%20the%20precedent%20which%20exists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202005%2C%20several%20MPs%20were%20expelled%20after%20they%20were%20caught%20in%20a%20sting%20operation%20accepting%20cash%20in%20exchange%20for%20agreeing%20to%20table%20questions%20in%20parliament.%20The%20accusation%20against%20Moitra%20seems%20designed%20to%20invoke%20the%202005%20expulsions%20as%20a%20precedent.%20However%2C%20unlike%20the%20%E2%80%98cash%20for%20questions%E2%80%99%20sting%2C%20there%20is%20so%20far%20no%20evidence%20to%20back%20up%20the%20claim%20that%20she%20received%20a%20%E2%80%98bribe%E2%80%99%20from%20Hiranandani%20or%20anyone%20else%20for%20any%20question%20that%20she%20has%20asked.%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20own%20affidavit%20does%20not%20support%20such%20a%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20about%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20her%20parliamentary%20login%20credentials%20to%20draft%20and%20post%20questions%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHiranandani%20has%20said%20he%20used%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20login%20to%20draft%20and%20post%20questions%20and%20this%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20the%20ethics%20committee%20is%20likely%20to%20raise%20with%20Moitra%2C%20assuming%20there%20is%20a%20rulebook%20of%20parliament%20which%20stipulates%20that%20MPs%20are%20barred%20from%20sharing%20their%20login%20details%20with%20anybody%20other%20than%20their%20staff%20or%20interns.%20But%20for%20this%20to%20become%20a%20more%20serious%20charge%2C%20the%20committee%20would%20have%20to%20establish%20that%20the%20questions%20Hiranandani%20uploaded%2C%20if%20any%2C%20brought%20him%20actual%20benefit%20in%20business%20terms%20and%20that%20he%20rewarded%20Moitra%20in%20some%20tangible%20way%20for%20that.%20So%20far%2C%20such%20a%20nexus%20has%20not%20been%20established.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWould%20an%20MP%20who%20saw%20two%20persons%20associated%20with%20her%20party%20%E2%80%93%20Prashant%20Kishor%20and%20Abhishek%20Banerjeee%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fprashant-kishor-mamata-banerjee-nephew-pegasus-spyware%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehit%20with%20Pegasus%20spyware%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20who%20knew%20her%20own%20outspokenness%20on%20Adani%20made%20her%20a%20target%2C%20use%20a%20businessman%20in%20Dubai%20to%20log%20in%20and%20upload%20questions%20for%20her%20if%20those%20questions%20represented%20an%20act%20of%20corruption%3F%20Similarly%2C%20would%20a%20businessman%20seeking%20to%20%E2%80%98plant%E2%80%99%20a%20question%20to%20further%20his%20business%20interests%20be%20comfortable%20leaving%20his%20own%20digital%20fingerprints%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20crime%3F%20These%20are%20questions%20the%20ethics%20committee%20members%20are%20likely%20to%20ponder%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20questions%20submitted%20through%20the%20parliament%20members%E2%80%99%20portal%20generate%20an%20OTP%20which%20goes%20to%20the%20MP%E2%80%99s%20registered%20mobile%20phone%20each%20time%20something%20has%20to%20be%20uploaded%20means%20Hiranandani%20did%20not%20have%20unsupervised%20access%20and%20did%20not%20%E2%80%9Chack%E2%80%9D%20any%20official%20computer%20network%20as%20some%20have%20suggested.%20Moitra%20would%20have%20had%20to%20authorise%20the%20submission%20of%20each%20question%2C%20thus%20retaining%20control.%20So%20was%20she%20simply%20using%20her%20businessman%20friend%20as%20a%20glorified%20secretary%20to%20upload%20questions%20she%20had%20approved%3F%20%E2%80%9COnce%20she%20asked%20you%20for%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hiranandani%20says%20in%20his%20affidavit%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20always%20a%20drop%20everything%20and%20do%20it%20now%20for%20me%20approach.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAn%20MP%20can%20get%20information%20from%20any%20source%20and%20frame%20questions%20on%20that%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20PDT%20Achary%20told%20The%20Wire.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20or%20she%20may%20procure%20information%20from%20even%20illegal%20sources.%20No%20one%20can%20ask%20the%20MP%20to%20disclose%20their%20source.%20So%20Moitra%20can%20procure%20information%20from%20%5BHiranandani%5D%20and%20frame%20questions%20or%20draft%20Bills%20or%20whatever.%20No%20one%20can%20question%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%E2%80%9CBut%20sharing%20the%20password%20is%20not%20allowed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20do%20we%20know%20about%20the%20gifts%20Hiranandani%20says%20he%20gave%20Moitra%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20affidavit%2C%20Hiranandani%20has%20not%20described%20the%20nature%20and%20value%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98gifts%E2%80%99%20he%20said%20he%20gave%20her%2C%20an%20omission%20that%20is%20hard%20to%20understand%20unless%20the%20inventory%20was%20seen%20as%20underwhelming%20by%20those%20who%20urged%20him%20to%20put%20pen%20to%20paper.%20Under%20cross-examination%2C%20however%2C%20those%20details%20would%20emerge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20both%20Hiranandani%20and%20Moitra%20say%20they%20have%20been%20close%20friends%20for%20several%20years%2C%20the%20committee%20will%20have%20to%20ask%20him%20what%20gifts%20he%20gave%20and%20when%2C%20in%20order%20to%20assess%20their%20significance%20and%20any%20potential%20conflict%20of%20interest.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20affidavit%20does%20not%20link%20his%20gifts%20and%20favours%20to%20the%20asking%20of%20parliament%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%E2%80%99s%20statement%20notes%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3EHiranandani%E2%80%99s%20says%20he%20gave%20in%20to%20her%20%E2%80%9Cdemands%E2%80%9D%20because%20he%20was%20fearful%20of%20displeasing%20her.%20%E2%80%9CDarshan%20and%20his%20father%20run%20one%20of%20India%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3Es%20largest%20business%20groups%20and%20their%20recent%20projects%20in%20UP%20and%20Gujarat%20have%20been%20inaugurated%20by%20the%20CM%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20Darshan%20accompanied%20the%20PM%20abroad%20as%20part%20of%20his%20business%20delegation%20very%20recently.%20Why%20would%20such%20a%20wealthy%20successful%20businessman%20who%20enjoys%20direct%20access%20to%20every%20Minister%20and%20the%20PMO%20be%20coerced%20by%20a%20first%20time%20Opposition%20MP%20into%20giving%20her%20gifts%20and%20giving%20into%20her%20demands%3F%20It%20is%20totally%20illogical%20and%20only%20cements%20the%20truth%20that%20this%20letter%20was%20drafted%20by%20the%20PMO%20and%20not%20Darshan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cb%3EAdani%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Mahua%20Moitra%3A%20A%20Timeline%20of%20how%20the%20war%20has%20unfolded%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJanuary%2024%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Hindenburg%20report%20on%20the%20Adani%20Group%20alleges%20insider%20trading%20via%20offshore%20funds%20to%20artificially%20boost%20company%20share%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFebruary%202023%20onwards%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EMahua%20Moitra%20demands%20probe%20into%20the%20allegations%20made%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20targets%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20for%20shielding%20the%20business%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAugust%2031%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20The%20%3Ci%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20%3Ci%3EGuardian%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20OCCRP%20publish%20stories%20linking%20some%20of%20the%20offshore%20funds%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20to%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%209%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Having%20received%20a%20questionnaire%20about%20a%20new%20story%20the%20%3Ci%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%20was%20working%20on%2C%20the%20Adani%20group%20issues%20a%20statement%20condemning%20what%20it%20said%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmalicious%20attempt%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20newspaper%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctarnish%20its%20global%20reputation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%2010%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Moitra%20hits%20out%20at%20Adani%20group%20for%20attacking%20the%20FT%20over%20its%20forthcoming%20story%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%2011%2C%202023%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThe%20%3Ci%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%20publishes%20a%20detailed%20and%20highly%20damaging%20story%20on%20the%20alleged%20over-invoicing%20of%20coal%20imports%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20The%20story%20referenced%20an%20earlier%20investigation%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20but%20documented%20how%20the%20over-invoicing%20is%20still%20continuing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%2013%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Moitra%20says%20the%20Adani%20group%20is%20lying%20when%20it%20claimed%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20FT%20story%2C%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20%E2%80%9Calready%20settled%E2%80%9D%20the%20issue%20of%20overvaluation%20of%20coal%20imports%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%2014%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20alleges%20Mahua%20Moitra%20was%20bribed%20by%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament%20targeting%20the%20Adani%20group%20but%20provides%20no%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%2015%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20demands%20a%20CBI%20case%20and%20a%20parliamentary%20ethics%20probe%20against%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20but%20again%20offered%20no%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%2016%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20The%20Adani%20group%20issues%20a%20media%20statement%20linking%20Dehadrai%20and%20Dubey%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20against%20Moitra%20to%20the%20%3Ci%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20OCCRP%E2%80%99s%20critical%20coverage%20of%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOctober%2016%2C%202023%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Moitra%20posts%20three%20questions%20on%20X%20directed%20at%20the%20Ada