ontent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20drought%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Maharashtra%20during%202013-2016%2C%20the%20worst%20to%20hit%20in%2040%20years%2C%20that%20a%20fundamental%20shift%20took%20place%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20Nutan%20Upendra%20Desai%20aka%20Nutanben%2C%20now%2051.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202016%2C%20when%20she%20found%20herself%20in%20remote%20Ambajogai%20in%20Beed%20district%20to%20oversee%20her%20team%E2%80%99s%20water%20rejuvenation%20work%2C%20she%20witnessed%20what%20she%20thought%20existed%20only%20in%20films.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20parched%20and%20cracked%20earth%2C%20the%20emaciated%20and%20undernourished%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20and%20the%20cattle%20dying%20from%20the%20lack%20of%20water%2C%20all%20changed%20her%20perspective.%20As%20if%20these%20conditions%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20she%20discovered%20that%20the%20people%20there%20were%20succumbing%20to%20water-borne%20diseases%20due%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20they%20were%20consuming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20shocked%20and%20concerned%20her%20more%20was%20that%20the%20people%20living%20there%20were%20consuming%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329441%2Fchennai-startup-bookwater-tracks-water-cans-quality-with-qr-codes-helps-access-safe-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20drinking%20water%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20ordinarily%20one%20would%20even%20be%20hesitant%20to%20touch.%20The%20dirty%2C%20fungus-filled%20green%20water%20with%20black%20molecules%20floating%20around%20was%20more%20than%20just%20a%20sore%20sight.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20basic%20human%20right%2C%20something%20millions%20of%20us%20take%20for%20granted%2C%20was%20being%20denied%20to%20these%20people%2C%20and%20she%20for%20one%2C%20could%20not%20live%20with%20the%20unfairness%20of%20it.%20The%20people%20were%20surviving%20on%20a%20rationed%20quantity%20of%20200%20litres%20of%20this%20filthy%20water%20for%207-8%20days%20per%20family%20and%20were%20absurdly%20grateful%20for%20it.%20It%20was%20beyond%20comprehension%20for%20someone%20who%20had%20never%20witnessed%20or%20suffered%20such%20scarcity%20in%20her%20life%20and%20she%20knew%20she%20had%20no%20option%20but%20to%20vest%20herself%20more%20fully%20into%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20completed%20her%20work%20in%2048%20villages%20in%20Beed%2C%20Nutanben%20made%20her%20way%20to%20Jalna%20in%20July-August%202016%2C%20where%20she%20began%20working%20with%20her%20NGO%20%E2%80%98Samast%20Mahajan%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20she%20is%20a%20trustee%20based%20out%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20on%20desilting%20water%20bodies%20and%20rejuvenating%20water%20sources%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20local%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20675px)%20100vw%2C%20675px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20locals%20in%20Jalna%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665.jpg%20675w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-150x112.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22506%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20locals%20in%20Jalna%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJalna%E2%80%99s%20transformation%3A%20From%20250%20tankers%20a%20day%20to%20nil%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20NGO%2C%20headquartered%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20provided%20the%20rental%20costs%20of%20the%20expensive%20machines%20required%20for%20the%20job%20through%20its%20partnership%20with%20the%20A.T.E.%20Chandra%20foundation%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20while%20the%20locals%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20team%20worked%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20translated%20into%20results%20on%20the%20ground.%20Although%20her%20NGO%20had%20been%20set%20up%20many%20years%20ago%20with%20the%20purpose%20of%20focussing%20on%20animal%20care%2C%20it%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20primarily%20focussed%20on%20saving%20and%20improving%20human%20lives%20in%20a%20country%20prone%20to%20natural%20and%20manmade%20calamities%20where%20government%20intervention%20is%20often%20inadequate%20or%20even%20absent.%20Human%20beings%2C%20at%20some%20level%2C%20took%20precedence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nutanben%20and%20her%20team%20began%20working%20in%20around%20330-odd%20villages%20and%20%3Cem%3Etalukas%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20comprise%20the%20Jalna%20district%2C%20the%20situation%20was%20not%20much%20better%20than%20it%20was%20in%20Beed.%20Water%20was%20very%20scarce%2C%20most%20of%20the%20water%20bodies%20in%20the%20region%20were%20silted%20up%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288219%2Fafter-visiting-drought-prone-villages-23-yo-plants-3-lakh-trees-in-three-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebone%20dry%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20tankers%20were%20the%20only%20way%20of%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20started%20working%2C%20each%20%3Cem%3Etehsil%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%208%20in%20Jalna%20district%20%E2%80%94%20survived%20on%20250%20tankers%20per%20day.%20Farmers%20were%20barely%20producing%20anything%20since%20there%20was%20no%20water%20for%20farming%3B%20meeting%20the%20basic%20consumption%20needs%20was%20a%20struggle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20when%20the%20team%20arrived%20in%20the%20district%2C%20villagers%20and%20locals%20were%20highly%20sceptical%20on%20whether%20such%20work%20could%20be%20done%20with%20community%20participation%20and%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20an%20NGO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20primarily%20seen%20as%20work%20only%20the%20government%20could%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Narayan%20Devkate%2C%2055%2C%20a%20farmer%20in%20Pimparkhed%2C%20who%20tends%20to%20his%2050-acre%20land%20parcel%20with%20his%20two%20brothers.%20Of%20the%20117-odd%20villages%20in%20his%20vicinity%2C%2078%20had%20no%20water%20at%20all%20when%20the%20effort%20began%2C%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPainstakingly%20and%20with%20gentle%20but%20persistent%20persuasion%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280255%2Ftamil-nadu-village-pond-revival-malarvizhli-akka-inspiring-water-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20work%20began%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ranged%20from%20desilting%20and%20rejuvenating%20small%20ponds%2C%20recharging%20borewells%2C%20%3Cem%3Enaali%20kholikaran%20%3C%2Fem%3E(veins%20of%20the%20river%20that%20have%20got%20filled%20with%20silt%20and%20turned%20dry)%20and%20compartment%20bunding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20a%20total%20of%20427%20km%20of%20nullahs%20have%20been%20opened%2C%2019%20ponds%20have%20been%20brought%20back%20to%20life%20and%20a%20total%20of%2079%2C7443%20cubic%20metres%20of%20silt%20has%20been%20removed%20and%20carted%20in%20the%20last%206-7%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20work%20has%20started%20on%20cleaning%20and%20rejuvenating%20the%2020%20km%20Kundalika%20and%20Seena%20river%2C%20of%20which%20around%205%20km%20has%20been%20done%20so%20far%20and%20a%20total%20of%20900%2C000%20lakh%20cubic%20metre%20of%20silt%20and%20a%20total%20of%20405%2C000%20cubic%20metre%20of%20garbage%20has%20been%20pulled%20out%20and%20carted!%20To%20see%20the%20river%20flowing%2C%20even%20if%20only%20in%20part%2C%20gave%20Nutanben%20and%20her%20team%20a%20spark%20of%20joy%20that%20only%20a%20few%20other%20things%20could%20manage!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20is%20perhaps%20only%20joy%20and%20satisfaction%20for%20the%20NGO%20team%20working%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20far%20better%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20the%20farmers%20and%20the%20community%20living%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaxman%20Sawade%20was%20growing%20around%20five%20quintals%20of%20cotton%20every%20year%20on%20his%20seven%20acre%20farm%20and%20barely%20managing%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20In%202013%2C%20he%20took%20the%20initiative%20of%20applying%20300%20trollies%20of%20silt%20on%20three%20acres%20of%20his%20land.%20Not%20only%20has%20his%20cotton%20output%20gone%20up%2C%20he%20is%20also%20growing%20grapes%20on%20his%20land%20since.%20Overall%2C%20his%20income%20has%20jumped%20to%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20a%20year%2C%20helping%20him%20build%20a%20better%20home%2C%20buy%202.5%20additional%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20a%20tractor%20and%20a%20motorbike.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20notion%20that%20almost%20nothing%20brings%20more%20prosperity%20and%20hope%20than%20water%20security%20has%20been%20amply%20reinforced%20by%20Jalna.%20Devkate%20says%20that%20three%20new%20factories%20have%20come%20up%20in%20the%20area%2C%20including%20a%20water%20intensive%20sugarcane%20factory%2C%20leading%20to%20new%20employment%20opportunities%20in%20the%20district.%20In%20a%20region%20that%20has%20been%20bereft%20of%20almost%20any%20work%20opportunities%2C%20this%2C%20he%20argues%2C%20is%20what%20has%20helped%20bring%20in%20more%20and%20more%20takers%20for%20the%20ongoing%20efforts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20806px)%20100vw%2C%20806px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A