g%5C%22%3E6.%20Meghnad%20Saha%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20444px)%20100vw%2C%20444px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fimage-85_11zon-1697717069.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22444%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meghnad%20Saha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fimage-85_11zon-1697717069.jpg%20444w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fimage-85_11zon-1697717069-208x300.jpg%20208w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fimage-85_11zon-1697717069-150x216.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332589%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMeghnad%20Saha%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaha%20was%20nominated%20for%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20in%201930%2C%201937%2C%201939%2C%201940%2C%201951%20and%201955.%20His%20Saha-Langmuir%20equation%2C%20which%20helps%20astronomers%20determine%20how%20much%20the%20various%20elements%20of%20a%20star%20have%20been%20ionised%2C%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20integral%20development%20in%20Physics.%20However%2C%20a%20shortcoming%20was%20that%20the%20equation%20was%20limited%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F199157%2Fmeghnad-saha-nobel-prize-unsung-indian-scientist-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eastrophysics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20Saha%20attempted%20to%20publish%20in%20the%20famous%20%3Cem%3EAstrophysical%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%20his%20theory%20of%20selective%20radiation%20pressure%20that%20would%20better%20explain%20the%20equation%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20due%20to%20financial%20constraints.%20It%20is%20often%20said%20that%20this%20missed%20opportunity%20may%20have%20been%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20missed%20Nobel%20Prize.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697812765000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fimage-90_11zon-1697716769.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332582%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20the%20stories%20of%20six%20Indian%20scientists%20who%20made%20important%20contributions%20to%20the%20field%20of%20science%20and%20were%20nominated%20for%20the%20Nobel%20Prize.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332582%2Findian-scientists-nominated-for-nobel-prize-homi-jehangir-bhabha-meghnad-saha%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20RSS%20Plan%20to%20Eradicate%20Caste%20Is%20Outdated%20and%20Skirts%20the%20Real%20Issues%20of%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20161440%2FF06GwWTWcAEgnoO.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20taking%20a%20stand%20on%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20has%20declared%20that%20it%20would%20work%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20caste.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Esarsangchalak%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20talked%20about%20God%20not%20creating%20caste%20but%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmohan-bhagwat-rss-pandit-caste-system%5C%22%3Epandits%20having%20created%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20need%20for%20reservations%20remaining%20as%20long%20as%20caste%20discrimination%20remains.%20These%20are%20stray%20statements%20that%20the%20RSS%20leaders%20give%20to%20satisfy%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20and%20Dalits%2C%20as%20their%20votes%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDattatreya%20Hosabale%2C%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20declared%20that%20the%20organisation%20should%20work%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20caste.%20On%20October%2011%2C%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20its%20workers%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fanyone-can-enter-a-temple-anywhere-work-to-eradicate-caste-bias-hosabale-123101300116_1.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cany%20person%20has%20the%20right%20to%20enter%20a%20temple%20anywhere%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20also%20urged%20RSS%20cadres%20to%20work%20for%20%E2%80%9Celiminating%20caste-based%20discrimination%20which%20brings%20disrepute%20to%20Hinduism%E2%80%9D.%20He%20was%20reported%20to%20have%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAny%20person%20can%20enter%20any%20temple%2C%20and%20everyone%20has%20the%20right%20to%20fetch%20water%20from%20any%20source%20of%20water.%20We%20must%20not%20tolerate%20such%20discrimination%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%20or%20untouchability%2C%20because%20it%20brings%20disrepute%20to%20the%20entire%20Hindu%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20media%20reported%20his%20statement%20on%20the%20next%20day%20as%20if%20it%20was%20the%20first%20programme%20to%20eradicate%20caste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDattatreya%E2%80%99s%20plan%20is%20quite%20outdated.%20His%20plan%20is%20built%20on%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20programme%2C%20which%20did%20not%20have%20any%20value%20for%20caste%20eradication%2C%20then%20or%20now.%20Temple%20entry%20for%20Shudras%2C%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20is%20now%20more%20or%20less%20accepted.%20The%20restrictions%20placed%20on%20Dalits%20for%20fetching%20water%20are%20also%20fewer%20now%2C%20though%20sporadic%20incidents%20still%20happen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20plan%20may%20reduce%20caste-based%20discrimination%20in%20a%20few%20areas%20but%20will%20not%20result%20in%20the%20eradication%20or%20abolition%20of%20caste.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20kind%20of%20typical%20old%20Gandhian%20programme%20does%20not%20suit%20the%20present%20times%20and%20demands%20of%20Shudras%2C%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20Adivasis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20are%20asking%20for%20now%20is%20a%20caste%20census.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnine-reasons-why-the-bihar-caste-census-could-shake-up-national-politics%5C%22%3EBihar%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20already%20done%20it%20and%20released%20the%20results.%20The%20RSS%20seems%20to%20have%20advised%20the%20BJP-run%20Union%20government%20and%20also%20state%20governments%20run%20by%20the%20party%20not%20to%20do%20so.%20If%20the%20numbers%20of%20Shudras%20and%20Dwijas%20(Brahmin%2C%20Bania%2C%20Kayastha%2C%20Khatri%20and%20Ksatriyas)%20are%20revealed%2C%20the%20resource%20and%20power-sharing%20will%20have%20to%20be%20done%20on%20that%20basis%20%E2%80%93%20which%20will%20have%20huge%20implications%20for%20the%20Dwija%20control%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20power%20%E2%80%93%20spiritual%20and%20social%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%20historically%20has%20been%20concerned%20about%20maintaining%20Dwija%20control%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20wealth%2C%20power%20and%20also%20the%20Hindu%20spiritual%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20Modi%20government%20buckled%20down%20against%20the%20caste%20count%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20claimed%20OBC%20status%2C%20the%20caste%20discourse%20among%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20has%20been%20scaled%20up.%20The%20critical%20question%20among%20them%20is%20how%20come%20a%20Brahmin%20%E2%80%93%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20is%20calling%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20while%20an%20OBC%20%E2%80%93%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20is%20against%20it.%20The%20RSS%20strategy%20of%20having%20an%20OBC%20PM%20to%20mobilise%20OBC%20voters%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20deep%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhy-the-bjp-is-afraid-of-a-caste-census%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20BJP%20Is%20Afraid%20of%20a%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%2C%20which%20never%20accepted%20caste%20as%20a%20category%20of%20electoral%20agenda%2C%20projected%20Modi%20as%20the%20first%20OBC%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20in%202013.%20The%20mainstream%20media%2C%20which%20was%20also%20averse%20to%20a%20discourse%20on%20caste%2C%20carried%20this%20propaganda%20to%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20India.%20Now%20the%20same%20RSS%20and%20media%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20whereas%20they%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fews-quota-a-stupefying-inversion-of-the-idea-of-equality%5C%22%3E10%25%20EWS%20reservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20upper%20castes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-the-issues-to-consider%5C%22%3Ewomen%E2%80%99s%20reservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20without%20an%20OBC%20quota%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20parliament%20and%20in%20assemblies.%20The%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20see%20through%20this%20game%20plan%20of%20the%20RSS%2FBJP%20and%20the%20big%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20at%20all%20the%20RSS%20is%20for%20the%20abolition%20of%20caste%2C%20they%20should%20have%20declared%20an%20agenda%20for%20priesthood%20training%20to%20all%20castes%20by%20abolishing%20the%20Brahmin%20control%20over%20spiritual%20institutions%20like%20temples%2C%20mutts%2C%20gurukuls%20and%20so%20on.%20Another%20equally%20important%20spiritual%20reform%20they%20could%20address%20is%20whether%20Sanskrit%20should%20still%20continue%20as%20the%20language%20of%20prayer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20leave%20that%20aside.%20Why%20do%20they%20not%20take%20the%20initiative%20to%20admit%20boys%20and%20girls%20of%20all%20castes%20for%20priesthood%20training%3F%20Why%20do%20they%20not%20talk%20about%20opening%20up%20schools%20and%20colleges%20for%20Hindu%20theological%20training%2C%20which%20would%20be%20open%20for%20competition%20cutting%20across%20the%20castes%20that%20consider%20themselves%20Hindu%2C%20to%20run%20the%20temples%20and%20other%20spiritual%20institutions%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Gandhian%20agenda%20in%20the%20early%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20did%20not%20go%20that%20far.%20It%20was%20confined%20to%20temple%20entry%20and%20water%20rights%20to%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20and%20Dalits.%20The%20Hindu%20spiritual%20agencies%20agreed%20to%20allow%20Shudra%2FOBCs%20into%20temples%20but%20not%20Dalits%20at%20that%20time.%20However%2C%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20some%20laws%20secured%20temple%20entry%20and%20water%20rights%20to%20Dalits%20to%20a%20large%20extent.%20Why%20is%20the%20RSS%20talking%20about%20these%20old%20issues%20but%20avoiding%20the%20question%20of%20caste%20census%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20big%20media%20houses%20play%20up%20small%20inconsequential%20statements%20by%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20or%20Dattatreya%20Hosabale%20on%20the%20same%20level%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20the%20RSS%20has%20expanded%20the%20base%20that%20sustains%20the%20Dwija%20control%20of%20all%20systems%20of%20India.%20Now%20they%20think%20that%20the%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cshown%20their%20place%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20and%20that%20Shudra%2C%20OBC%2C%20Dalit%20and%20Adivasi%20assertion%20has%20to%20be%20tackled%20with%20tact%20but%20without%20giving%20them%20any%20substantial%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31181250%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-6.12.02-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31181250%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-6.12.02-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31181250%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-6.12.02-PM-300x151.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31181250%2FScreenshot-2023-08-31-at-6.12.02-PM-1024x515.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670898%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22603%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20via%20X%2F%40RahulGandhi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20RSS%20does%20not%20talk%20about%20the%20present%20school%20and%20college%20education%20system%20where%20private%2C%20English%20medium%20schools%20are%20under%20the%20control%20of%20education%20business%20houses.%20The%20government%20school%20and%20college%20education%20in%20regional%20languages%20is%20of%20poor%20quality%20and%20has%20poor%20infrastructure.%20However%2C%20they%20directed%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20stress%20the%20importance%20of%20education%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98mother%20tongue%E2%80%99%20(meaning%20regional%20language)%20in%20the%20government%20sector%20only.%20The%20RSS%20remains%20silent%20about%20providing%20the%20same%20medium%20and%20an%20equal%20standard%20school%20and%20college%20education%20to%20all%20%E2%80%93%20this%20will%20contribute%20to%20the%20eradication%20of%20caste.%20The%20RSS%20leadership%20knows%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENor%20does%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20RSS%20get%20into%20real%20issues%20that%20will%20weaken%20segregation%20based%20on%20caste%20in%20the%20agrarian%20sector.%20Caste%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20the%20graded%20indignity%20of%20labour%20and%20production-related%20science.%20The%20graded%20inequality%20that%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20talked%20about%20was%20institutionalised%20in%20the%20process%20of%20establishing%20graded%20indignity%20of%20labour%20and%20productive%20science.%20For%20example%2C%20leather-related%20scientific%20and%20technological%20work%20is%20treated%20as%20more%20undignified%20than%20tilling%20the%20land%20or%20making%20pots.%20Washing%20clothes%20and%20cutting%20hair%20were%20treated%20as%20more%20undignified%20than%20iron%20and%20gold%20smithy.%20Finally%2C%20temple%20priesthood%20and%20teaching%20in%20gurukuls%20were%20treated%20as%20more%20dignified%20than%20tilling%20the%20land%20and%20harvesting.%20Thus%2C%20the%20temple%20pujari%20and%20gurukul%20teacher%2C%20who%20were%2Fare%20only%20Brahmins%2C%20treated%20all%20other%20tasks%20as%20beneath%20their%20body%20and%20soul.%20The%20RSS%2C%20in%20its%20100%20years%20of%20existence%2C%20never%20tried%20to%20take%20up%20a%20campaign%20against%20these%20indignities%20and%20anti-science%20belief%20systems%20that%20got%20entrenched%20into%20caste%20society%E2%80%99s%20belief%20systems.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20RSS%20is%20serious%20about%20abolishing%20caste%2C%20it%20should%20push%20for%3Cspan%3E%20courses%20about%20the%20dignity%20of%20labour%20and%20respect%20for%20science%20and%20technological%20knowledge%20that%20exists%20in%20tanning%2C%20cutting%20hair%2C%20washing%20clothes%2C%20making%20pots%20and%20tilling%20the%20land%20to%20be%20i%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Entroduced%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20no%20political%20leader%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20Brahmin%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0took%20a%20decisive%20stand%20on%20the%20basic%20task%20of%20counting%20castes%20and%20redistributing%20resources%20to%20the%20oppressed.%20Not%20even%20his%20own%20ancestors.%20Among%20upper%20caste%20leaders%2C%20after%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20a%20Bania%2C%20it%20is%20only%20Rahul%20who%20has%20taken%20a%20definite%20stand%20on%20caste.%20One%20has%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20if%20this%20genuine%20commitment%20remains%20in%20the%20future%2C%20but%20his%20stand%20must%20be%20appreciated.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20Push%20for%20Caste%20Census%20Is%20a%20Step%20Towards%20Ideological%20Unity%20in%20Opposition%20Ranks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RSS%2C%20if%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20eradicating%20caste%2C%20should%20start%20a%20campaign%20about%20the%20dignity%20of%20labour%2C%20production%20and%20science%20and%20make%20it%20acceptable%20in%20the%20Hindu%20spiritual%20system.%20The%20course%20content%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%20must%20have%20teach%20human%20equality%20and%20equal%20respect%20for%20every%20work%20and%20different%20food%20cultures.%20The%20RSS%20must%20ask%20for%20the%20same%20medium%20and%20equal%20quality%20of%20school%20and%20college%20education%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20the%20institute%20is%20government-run%20or%20private.%20Training%20for%20pujaris%20must%20be%20opened%20for%20all%20castes%20that%20claim%20to%20be%20Hindu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%2C%20which%20mostly%20comprises%20people%20from%20the%20Brahmin%20caste%2C%20has%20the%20will%20for%20such%20a%20reform.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EKancha%20Ilaiah%20Shepherd%20is%20a%20political%20theorist%2C%20social%20activist%20and%20author.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697812240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthe-rss-plan-to-eradicate-caste-is-outdated-and-skirts-the-real-issues-of-today%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20it%20is%20serious%2C%20it%20must%20work%20towards%20allowing%20all%20castes%20to%20become%20temple%20priests%20and%20change%20the%20education%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT%20%26amp%3B%20NIT%20Grads%E2%80%99%20Innovative%20Smart%20Ring%20Supports%20Contactless%20Payments%20While%20Tracking%20Health%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMuse%20Wearables%2C%20a%20technology%20startup%20born%20out%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274587%2Fiit-madras-startup-tvasta-builds-3d-printed-houses-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIT%20Madras%3C%2Fa%3E%20Incubation%20Cell%2C%20has%20developed%20a%20smart%20ring%20weighing%20just%20five%20grams%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20capable%20of%20performing%20advanced%20health%20tracking%2C%20contactless%20payments%20(NFC%20payments)%2C%20and%20cuffless%20blood%20pressure%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalled%20Ring%20One%2C%20the%20founders%20of%20Muse%20Wearables%20claim%20that%20it%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cworld%E2%80%99s%20first%20smart%20ring%20to%20offer%20NFC%20payments%20and%20health%20tracking%20in%20the%20smallest%20and%20most%20comfortable%20form%20factor%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20KLN%20Sai%20Prasanth%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Conzumex%20Industries%20%E2%80%94%20which%20operates%20the%20Muse%20Wearables%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20there%20are%20health-focused%20rings%20like%20Oura%20in%20the%20USA%20or%20Ultrahuman%2C%20boAt%2C%20etc%20in%20India%2C%20none%20currently%20offer%20the%20combined%20functionality%20of%20NFC%20payments%20and%20health%20tracking%20in%20a%20single%20compact%20ring.%20Also%2C%20most%20rings%20don%E2%80%99t%20offer%20clinical-grade%20accuracy%20for%20monitoring%20most%20vitals%20and%20none%20of%20them%20offer%20cuffless%20BP%20management%20on%20a%20ring%20form%20factor.%20This%20combination%20is%20typically%20found%20in%20smartwatches%20like%20Apple%20Watch%2C%20Galaxy%20Watch%20or%20Garmin%20where%20space%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20constraint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20sets%20Ring%20One%20apart%20is%20this%20combination%20of%20NFC%20Payments%20and%20advanced%20health%20tracking%20in%20a%20form%20factor%20that%E2%80%99s%20just%203.2%20mm%20thick%20and%207.6%20mm%20wide%20and%20weighs%20less%20than%20five%20grams%2C%20making%20it%20the%20smallest%20and%20most%20comfortable%20wearable%20to%20offer%20this%20convenience%20and%20functionality%20to%20users.%20Moreover%20Ring%20One%20is%20the%20first%20smart%20ring%20in%20the%20world%20to%20offer%20cuffless%20BP%20management%20and%20continuous%20monitoring%20of%20many%20vitals%20with%20clinical%20grade%20accuracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDesigned%20and%20manufactured%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Ring%20One%20has%20already%20entered%20mass%20production.%20And%20to%20facilitate%20that%2C%20Muse%20has%20teamed%20up%20with%20various%20contract%20manufacturers.%20Late%20last%20month%2C%20Muse%20launched%20the%20Ring%20One%20globally.%20In%20India%2C%20however%2C%20the%20product%20is%20set%20for%20launch%20later%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Francis%2C%20CTO%20at%20Muse%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9CRing%20One%20can%20measure%20six%20di%EF%AC%80erent%20vitals%20%E2%80%94%20heart%20rate%2C%20blood%20oxygen%2C%20temperature%2C%20respiratory%20rate%2C%20heart%20rate%20variability%2C%20and%20blood%20pressure.%20Trained%20with%20five%20million%20data%20points%20from%20over%204%2C000%20people%2C%20Ring%20One%20o%EF%AC%80ers%20clinical%20grade%20accuracy%20for%20health%20information.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRing%20One%20is%20also%20the%20%EF%AC%81rst%20smart%20ring%20in%20the%20world%20to%20o%EF%AC%80er%20cu%EF%AC%80%20less%20blood%20pressure%20measurement.%20It%20detects%20sleep%20and%20naps%2C%20analyses%20various%20sleep%20stages%20and%20gives%20personalised%20insights%20to%20help%20improve%20sleep.%20Ring%20One%20can%20also%20track%20your%20workouts%20and%20give%20you%20advanced%20metrics%20to%20optimise%20your%20%EF%AC%81tness%20gains.%20It%20can%20measure%20the%20impact%20of%20your%20relaxation%20sessions%20and%20helps%20you%20with%20tailored%20insights%20to%20reduce%20your%20stress%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20recent%20press%20release%20issued%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331198%2Fupcycling-scrap-leather-to-make-luxury-accessories-delhi-fashion-startup-econock%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CRing%20One%20%5Balso%5D%20offers%20the%20convenience%20of%20%E2%80%98tap%20to%20pay%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20a%20simple%20wave%20of%20the%20palm%2C%20Ring%20One%20can%20complete%20transactions%20with%20ease.%20Muse%20has%20partnered%20with%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20payment%20networks%2C%20including%20Mastercard%2C%20VISA%20and%20Rupay%2C%20to%20make%20payments%20with%20the%20Ring%20accessible%20to%20everyone%20across%20the%20world.%20The%20payments%20will%20be%20live%20in%20India%2C%20USA%2C%20Canada%2C%20Europe%2C%20Australia%2C%20Singapore%20and%20UAE%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20press%20release%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202015%20by%20graduates%20from%20IIT%20Madras%20and%20NIT%20Warangal%2C%20Muse%20Wearables%20already%20makes%20payment-enabled%20hybrid%20smartwatches%2C%20health%20trackers%2C%20and%20Gtag%2C%20its%20glucose%20sensor.%20Based%20out%20of%20Bengaluru%20with%20registered%20offices%20in%20Chennai%2C%20USA%2C%20and%20Singapore%2C%20Muse%20currently%20caters%20to%2030%20countries%20by%20selling%20products%20through%20online%20platforms%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IIT-M%20Startup%20develops%20Smart%20Ring%20One%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FRing-One-Muse-Wearables-Feature-Image--1697806161-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332711%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ring%20One%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Smart%20Ring%20developed%20by%20Indian%20tech%20start-up%20Muse%20Wearables%20is%20equipped%20with%20advanced%20health%20tracking%20%26amp%3B%20NFC%20payments.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20all%20in%20a%20finger%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202018%2C%20we%20launched%20our%20hybrid%20watch%20on%20Kickstarter%20and%20received%20a%20great%20response.%20But%20as%20we%20were%20ready%20to%20scale%20up%20manufacturing%20of%20this%20hybrid%20watch%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298376%2Fmolbio-diagnostics-truenat-covid-testing-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehappened.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20had%20to%20temporarily%20stop%20operations%20and%20realised%20the%20need%20to%20pivot%20quickly%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Prasanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%20in%20March%202020%20brought%20silent%20hypoxia%20(low%20blood%20oxygen%20levels%20in%20the%20body)%2C%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20COVID-related%20deaths%2C%20into%20sharp%20focus.%20In%20the%20three-month%20lockdown%20which%20followed%2C%20Prasanth%20and%20his%20team%20were%20immersed%20in%20extensive%20research%20and%20development%20to%20develop%20a%20technology%20that%20could%20accurately%20capture%20low%20blood%20oxygen%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20mission%20was%20to%20engineer%20and%20design%20a%20precise%20sensor%20powered%20by%20leading-edge%20algorithms%20that%20could%20deliver%20nothing%20short%20of%20accurate%20results.%20In%20a%20whirlwind%2090%20days%20from%20design%20to%20production%2C%20we%20launched%20a%20comprehensive%20wrist-based%20health%20tracker%20in%20September%202020%20even%20before%20industry%20leaders%20like%20Apple%20introduced%20wrist%20SpO2%20monitoring%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20there.%20At%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20second%20wave%2C%20we%20deployed%20our%20trackers%20on%20patients%20and%20were%20able%20to%20save%20some%20lives%20by%20generating%20alerts%20to%20provide%20timely%20oxygen%20support.%20We%20learnt%20that%20wearable%20technology%20can%20transform%20lives.%20We%20married%20the%20findings%20from%20our%20past%20two%20products%20and%20came%20up%20with%20the%20path-breaking%20Ring%20One%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Prasanth%20recalls%20a%20personal%20anecdote%20when%20he%20delivered%20Muse%E2%80%99s%20very%20first%20hybrid%20watch%20to%20a%20customer.%20The%20customer%20mentioned%20to%20him%20that%20she%20would%20be%20very%20interested%20to%20see%20such%20features%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmuch%20more%20sleek%20and%20comfortable%20form%20factor%20like%20a%20ring%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20the%20very%20first%20time%20I%20came%20across%20the%20idea%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrathyusha%20K%2C%20co-founder%20and%20COO%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CObserving%20hundreds%20of%20users%20during%20the%20pandemic%20has%20imparted%20us%20with%20priceless%20insights%2C%20most%20notably%20that%20the%20wrist%20might%20not%20be%20the%20most%20optimal%20position%20to%20get%20accurate%20data.%20Also%2C%20many%20people%20were%20unable%20to%20wear%20the%20wrist%20tracker%20during%20sleep.%20We%20found%20that%20the%20%EF%AC%81nger%20is%20a%20more%20accurate%20location%20to%20get%20precise%20data.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Prasanth%2C%20the%20finger%20is%20considered%20a%20more%20accurate%20location%20to%20obtain%20precise%20health%20data.%20Explaining%20his%20reasons%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20because%20the%20finger%20experiences%20less%20interference%20from%20bones%2C%20tendons%20and%20muscles%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20higher%20density%20of%20capillary%20action%2C%20which%20improves%20signal%20quality%20for%20health%20measurements.%20Also%2C%20the%20arteries%20carrying%20blood%20are%20situated%20closer%20to%20the%20finger%20and%20are%20surrounded%20by%20thinner%2C%20more%20uniform%20tissue%20compared%20to%20the%20wrist.%20This%20proximity%20to%20major%20blood%20vessels%20contributes%20to%20more%20accurate%20data.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20rings%20offer%20a%20uniform%20fit%20across%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20people%2C%20unlike%20smartwatches%2C%20which%20can%20vary%20in%20tightness%20and%20positioning%20on%20the%20wrist.%20This%20variation%20can%20affect%20the%20accuracy%20of%20readings.%20This%20is%20why%20doctors%20measure%20heart%20rate%20or%20blood%20oxygen%20from%20the%20finger%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20reasons%20are%20supported%20by%20various%20studies%2C%20such%20as%20one%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7309104%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPubMed%20Central%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20found%20finger-based%20monitoring%20to%20offer%20improved%20signal%20quality.%20Another%20study%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F1424-8220%2F19%2F8%2F1874%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMDPI%20%3C%2Fa%3E(a%20publisher%20of%20open-access%20scientific%20journals)%20highlighted%20the%20advantages%20of%20finger-based%20measurements%20for%20various%20health%20parameters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smart%20Ring%20for%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357.jpg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357-300x141.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357-500x235.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357-768x361.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FHeropicfinal11-1697806357-150x71.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332713%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22706%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ring%20One%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Smart%20Ring%20developed%20by%20Indian%20tech%20start-up%20Muse%20Wearables%20can%20measure%20six%20di%EF%AC%80erent%20vitals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20it%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20advanced%20health%20tracking%2C%20Prasanth%20notes%20that%20Ring%20One%20employs%20LEDs%20that%20project%20light%20into%20your%20arteries%20and%20photo-detectors%20that%20capture%20the%20reflected%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20photo-detectors%20come%20with%20lenses%20with%20optimised%20curvature%20to%20enhance%20the%20light%20collected%20and%20ensure%20great%20signal%20quality.%20The%20properties%20of%20the%20reflected%20light%20change%20based%20on%20your%20blood%20flow.%20These%20changes%20are%20captured%20in%20the%20signal%20received%20by%20the%20photo-detectors.%20Ring%20One%20uses%20a%20total%20of%20six%20LEDs%20(green%2C%20red%20and%20IR)%20and%20two%20photo-detectors%20to%20give%20you%20accurate%20readings%20all%20through%20the%20day.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Ring%20One%20also%20captures%20your%20movement%20in%20six%20different%20axes%20using%20the%203D%20accelerometer%20and%20gyroscope.%20This%20ensures%20that%20you%20get%20accurate%20health%20vital%20measurements%20even%20when%20you%20are%20working%20out%20or%20are%20on%20the%20move%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%20Ring%20One%20observes%20your%20blood%20flow%20patterns%20using%20an%20optical%20sensor%20to%20track%20all%20your%20vitals%20like%20respiratory%20rate%2C%20SPO2%20and%20BP%2C%20amongst%20others.%20It%20also%20uses%20a%20temperature%20sensor%20to%20measure%20your%20temperature%20changes%20all%20through%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20contactless%20payments%2C%20the%20user%20can%20enter%20their%20card%20details%20on%20the%20Muse%20app.%20These%20details%20are%20encrypted%20and%20sent%20securely%20to%20their%20ring%E2%80%99s%20NFC%20chip.%20They%20can%20then%20tap%20the%20Ring%20across%20any%20PoS%20(point%20of%20sale)%20terminal%20to%20make%20a%20payment%20similar%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctap%20to%20pay%E2%80%9D%20payment%20done%20with%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20users%20can%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20the%20Ring%20One%20with%20minimal%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F265807%2Feducation-campaign-help-students-villages-study-smartphones-during-lockdown%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmartphone%20%3C%2Fa%3Eintervention%2C%20Muse%20has%20designed%20two%20key%20interfaces%20%E2%80%94%20Turn%20Wheel%20and%20Magic%20Glyph.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Turn%20Wheel%2C%20users%20can%20switch%20between%20different%20modes.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20simple%20turn%20to%20the%20left%20can%20start%20a%20workout%20mode%20and%20monitor%20their%20health%20while%20exercising%20without%20needing%20their%20phone.%20Likewise%2C%20users%20can%20enable%20payments%20with%20a%20quick%20turn%20to%20the%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20having%20a%20convenient%20and%20intuitive%20controller%20on%20your%20ring.%20It%20also%20helps%20add%20additional%20layers%20of%20security%20to%20your%20payments.%20You%20can%20use%20the%20turn%20wheel%20interface%20to%20lock%20the%20payments%20and%20enable%20them%20only%20when%20you%20want%20to%20ensure%20no%20phishing%20can%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prasanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Magic%20Glyph%20interface%20is%20all%20about%20showing%20users%20the%20most%20important%20information%20at%20a%20glance.%20It%20lets%20them%20check%20things%20like%20the%20charging%20levels%20of%20the%20ring%20and%20case.%20Also%2C%20if%20a%20user%20ever%20misplaces%20their%20ring%20or%20case%2C%20they%20can%20use%20the%20Magic%20Glyph%20interface%20to%20locate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMade%20with%20Titanium%20grade%202%20and%20Ceramic%20(Zirconia)%2C%20this%20smart%20ring%20is%20lightweight%20yet%20robust.%20Going%20further%2C%20the%20inner%20layer%20of%20the%20ring%20is%20made%