%80%98means%20good%E2%80%99%20and%20is%20godly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20171219%2FF8N0WYHWsAAL58Q.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20171219%2FF8N0WYHWsAAL58Q.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20171219%2FF8N0WYHWsAAL58Q-300x182.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20171219%2FF8N0WYHWsAAL58Q-1024x622.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681076%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22729%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20the%20holy%20Parvati%20Kund%20of%20Pithoragarh%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20Photo%3A%20X%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20akin%20to%20the%20garb%20he%20chose%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20first%20COVID-19%20lockdown.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20growing%20locks%20and%20flowing%20beard%20made%20him%20look%20sagely%20and%20saved%20him%20for%20being%20pinioned%20for%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20shortfalls%20and%20lack%20of%20foresight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20visit%20to%20Uttarakhand%2C%20he%20performed%20and%20enacted%20multiple%20roles%2C%20even%20when%20addressing%20a%20public%20meeting.%20The%20ostensible%20occasion%20was%20the%20inauguration%20and%20foundation-laying%20ceremony%20of%20multiple%20projects%20in%20Pithoragarh%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20most%20publicised%20picture(s)%20were%20those%20in%20a%20creamy%20shade%20of%20white%20underscoring%20the%20%E2%80%98purity%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20person%20donning%20the%20costume.%20Modi%20went%20to%20the%20Shiva%20temple%20located%20at%20a%20dizzying%20height%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Parvati%20Kund%20wearing%20this%20costume.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20exotic%20locales%20have%20their%20own%20appeal.%20But%20in%20this%20case%2C%20as%20indicated%20in%20Bachchan%E2%80%99s%20post%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20spot%20where%20numerous%20devout%20Hindus%20aspire%20to%20go%20and%20pay%20obeisance%20to%20Lord%20Shiva.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20such%20settings%20enable%20Modi%20to%20display%20himself%20as%20a%20leader%20who%20is%20also%20a%20saviour%20of%20people.%20With%20this%20act%20particularly%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20conveyed%20to%20people%20that%20to%20seek%20boons%20and%20blessings%20for%20them%20he%20even%20%E2%80%98undertakes%20the%20hardship%E2%80%99%20of%20trekking%20up%20to%20such%20remote%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20posts%20buttresses%20this%20point%3A%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20this%20place%20of%20spirituality%20and%20culture%20situated%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20nature%2C%20I%20wished%20a%20happy%20life%20for%20all%20the%20family%20members%20of%20our%20country.%E2%80%9D%20The%20message%20was%20unambiguous%20%E2%80%93%20he%20has%20travelled%20this%20far%2C%20not%20to%20partake%20in%20the%20visual%20wonderment%20that%20the%20images%20arouse%2C%20or%20tick%20another%20destination%20from%20his%20%E2%80%98to-visit%E2%80%99%20list%2C%20but%20to%20seek%20well-being%20of%20%E2%80%98his%20people%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20posts%20depicted%20the%20premier%20in%20the%20designer%20costume%20(obviously)%20worn%20over%20layers%20of%20woolens%20with%20a%20headgear%20in%20place.%20A%20search%20revealed%20that%20the%20outfit%20Modi%20wore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Farchive%2Ffeatures%2Frang-tribals-from-pithoragarh-nepal-come-together-287798%5C%22%3Eis%20actually%20donned%20by%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20particular%20tribal%20community%20of%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20inside%20the%20cave%20in%20the%20Kedarnath%20temple%20complex%20in%20May%202019%2C%20where%20his%20videos%20and%20pictures%20drew%20sniggers%20from%20critics%20due%20to%20%E2%80%98access%E2%80%99%20provided%20to%20the%20unidentified%20cameraperson(s)%2C%20at%20this%20Pithoragarh%20shrine%2C%20too%2C%20the%20intrusive%20presence%20of%20the%20camera%20did%20not%20alter%20the%20tranquil%20expression%20he%20sported%20on%20his%20face%20throughout%20while%20performing%20rituals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20served%20as%20a%20reminder%20to%20an%20old%20aide%E2%80%99s%20observation%20made%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%3A%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20square%20inch%20outside%20his%20private%20room%20is%20a%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20quite%20like%20makeshift%20ones%20in%20his%20school%20in%20Vadnagar%2C%20which%20he%20went%20to.%20One%20of%20his%20teachers%20had%20provided%20a%20detail%3A%20He%20accepted%20only%20lead%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresentation%20of%20the%20self%20has%20been%20increasingly%20central%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20politics.%20An%20early%20user%20of%20social%20media%2C%20he%20became%20aware%20of%20how%20technology%20could%20enhance%20appeal%20of%20the%20aesthete.%20Through%20the%20power%20of%20his%20oratory%2C%20he%20conveys%20repeatedly%20that%20none%20of%20this%20is%20for%20himself%2C%20but%20only%20%E2%80%98for%E2%80%99%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20engagements%20for%20that%20day%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20how%20the%20religious%20or%20spiritual%20conjoined%20with%20the%20cultural%20and%20political.%20This%20was%20understandable%20because%20the%20amalgamation%20of%20the%20three%20is%20one%20of%20the%20foundational%20tenets%20of%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20culture%2C%20religion%2C%20and%20nationalism%20are%20interwoven%20and%20universal%20to%20the%20Indian%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20course%20of%20the%20day%2C%20Modi%20traipsed%20past%20assemblies%20of%20personnel%20of%20the%20Army%2C%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%20and%20Indo%20Tibetan%20Border%20Police%20besides%20the%20%3Cem%3Eaam%20janta%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20many%20of%20who%20were%20assembled%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20route%20he%20took%2C%20with%20a%20mandate%20to%20cheer%20and%20shower%20floral%20petals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPast%20these%20halts%2C%20Modi%20hopped%20off%20to%20another%20ancient%20Shiva%20temple%20in%20Jageshwar%20Dham%20in%20Almora%20district.%20In%20between%20he%20had%20time%20to%20address%20a%20public%20rally%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20never%20fails%20to%20wear%20his%20religiosity%20on%20his%20sleeves%20overtly%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20on%20this%20day%20or%20in%20May%202019%20in%20Kedarnath%2C%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20or%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2792xwvS7yg%26ab_channel%3DSansadTV%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20in%20December%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUTfKUQ-7P_A%5C%22%3EAugust%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThrough%20these%20acts%2C%20Modi%20projects%20himself%20not-so-subtly%20as%20a%20devout%20Hindu.%20However%20he%20remains%20a%20utopian%20figure%2C%20whose%20%E2%80%98perfection%E2%80%99%20is%20impractical%20for%20hoi%20polloi.%20Modi%20can%20at%20best%20be%20an%20aspiration%2C%20never%20fulfilled%20for%20no%20one%20can%20become%20or%20take%20his%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20he%20and%20his%20party%20publicised%20his%20OBC%20status%20but%20not%20anymore.%20Whenever%20he%20speaks%20on%20anything%20that%20has%20a%20resonance%20of%20the%20Hindu%2C%20Hinduism%20and%20Hinduness%20(Savarkar%20called%20this%20the%20near%20closest%20word%20to%20define%20Hindutva)%2C%20he%20blurs%20caste%2C%20class%20and%20regional%20lines%20%E2%80%93%20he%20is%20just%20a%20Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20separation%20between%20religion%20and%20state.%20Effectively%2C%20the%20latter%20has%20actually%20acquired%20a%20far%20deeper%20religious%20hue%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20every%20playacting%20of%20Modi%20is%20within%20a%20temple%20or%20religious%20precincts.%20On%20October%201%2C%20TV%20screens%20and%20social%20media%20platforms%20lit%20up%20with%20Modi%20with%20a%20broom.%20He%20did%20so%20not%20all%20by%20himself%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbroom-in-hand-modi-collaborates-with-influencer-for-swachh-drive%2Farticleshow%2F104092240.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Echose%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20prop%20in%20the%20singular%20%E2%80%93%20Ankit%20Baiyanpuria%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20new%20tribe%20of%20%E2%80%98influencers%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20field%20of%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20marked%20the%20second%20fortnight%20of%20September%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fswachhbharatmission.gov.in%2Fshs2023%2FSHS2023%2Findex.aspx%5C%22%3ESwachhata%20Hi%20Seva%3C%2Fa%3E%20(like%20most%20official%20programmes%2C%20the%20naming%20of%20this%20too%20was%20solely%20in%20Hindi).%20The%20campaign%20was%20to%20end%20on%20October%202%20%E2%80%93%20a%20day%20when%20the%20mandatory%20visit%20to%20Rajghat%20hogs%20time%20and%20space%20in%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20video%20clip%20was%20smartly%20released%20a%20day%20prior%20to%20this.%20Almost%20from%20the%20first%20shot%2C%20it%20is%20understandable%20that%20the%20production%20team%20was%20briefed%20that%20Modi%20was%20the%20star.%20The%20spotlight%20remained%20riveted%20on%20his%20face%2C%20while%20the%20%E2%80%98co-star%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20was%20often%20shrouded%20in%20darkness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20two%2C%20while%20Modi%20was%20dressed%20in%20kurta%20pyjamas%20with%20a%20white%20wrap%20as%20an%20accessory%2C%20draped%20or%20pinned%20strategically%20over%20his%20shoulder%2C%20Baiyanpuria%20was%20in%20a%20normal%20workout%20costume%20%E2%80%93%20tracksuit%20bottom%20and%20a%20round-neck%20T-shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20projects%20Modi%20as%20a%20leader%20who%20is%20also%20concerned%20about%20cleanliness%20or%20Swachhata%20and%20fitness%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20all%20about%20that%20Swachh%20and%20Swasth%20Bharat%20vibe%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20post%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShot%20in%20an%20open%20space%20with%20large%20trees%20providing%20the%20backdrop%20to%20simulate%20a%20park%2C%20shooting%20may%20even%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20backyard%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20intention%20is%20to%20publicise%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%20by%20personally%20picking%20up%20the%20broom.%20The%20two%20characters%20banter%20along%20%E2%80%93%20the%20contents%20aimed%20at%20furthering%20Modi-centric%20mythologies%20%E2%80%93%20Baiyanpuria%20says%20that%20he%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20Modi%20for%20his%20fitness%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20again%20the%20unattainable%20Modi%20who%20is%20the%20star%20of%20this%20widely%20viewed%20video.%20This%20social%20media%20influencer%20from%20Sonipat%20may%20have%204.9%20millions%20followers%20on%20Instagram%2C%20but%20all%20efforts%20would%20have%20come%20to%20a%20naught%20had%20he%20not%20been%20inspired%20by%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20becomes%20part%20of%20the%20people%20by%20articulating%20their%20sentiments%20and%20desires.%20He%20is%20part%20of%20the%20elite%20that%20people%20aspire%20to%20become%20part%20of%20with%20his%20style%20of%20dressing%20and%20through%20the%20raw%20political%20power%20he%20exudes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20has%20always%20been%20aware%20of%20the%20power%20of%20how%20the%20leader%20is%20%E2%80%98presented%E2%80%99.%20He%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20world%20for%20whom%20the%20template%20of%20a%20populist%20is%20apt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhere%20he%20scores%20over%20his%20peers%20is%20the%20additional%20flank%20of%20religion%20through%20which%20he%20makes%20inroads%20and%20creates%20a%20following%20for%20himself%20in%20the%20psyche%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20constant%20use%20of%20religion%20and%20the%20religious%20vocabulary%2C%20there%20is%20a%20perceived%20messianic%20zeal%20in%20his%20actions.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20recollect%20that%20on%20more%20than%20one%20occasion%2C%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fin-depth%2Felections-2014-narendra-modi-takes-charge%2Fstory%2Fi-have-been-chosen-by-god-says-narendra-modi-46973-2014-04-24%5C%22%3Ehas%20claimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20has%20been%20the%20%E2%80%98chosen%20one%E2%80%99.%20His%20claim%20fits%20in%20completely%20with%20what%20academic%20S.%20Vittorini%20termed%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccalculated%2C%20sharp%2C%20uncluttered%20style%20and%20saintly%20look%E2%80%9D%20that%20presents%20Modi%20to%20the%20people%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmessianic%2C%20super%20CEO%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENilanjan%20Mukhopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20latest%20book%20is%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Demolition%20and%20the%20Verdict%3A%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Project%20to%20Reconfigure%20India%3Cem%3E.%20His%20other%20books%20include%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20RSS%3A%20Icons%20of%20the%20Indian%20Right%20%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3ENarendra%20Modi%3A%20The%20Man%2C%20The%20Times%3Cem%3E.%20He%20tweets%20at%20%40NilanjanUdwin%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697809513000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20170741%2Fimage-1418.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-self-image-religion-politics-image%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Modi%20has%20always%20been%20aware%20of%20the%20power%20of%20how%20the%20leader%20is%20%E2%80%98presented%E2%80%99.%20Where%20he%20scores%20over%20his%20peers%20is%20the%20additional%20flank%20of%20religion%20through%20which%20he%20makes%20inroads%20and%20creates%20a%20following%20for%20himself%20in%20the%20psyche%20of%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-self-image-religion-politics-image%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%201300%20Writers%2C%20Publishers%20Decry%20Cancellation%20of%20Events%20Featuring%20Palestinian%20Authors%2C%20Artists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19123630%2FF8exa0MXQAAjnaV.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EOver%201%2C300%20writers%20and%20publishers%20from%20around%20the%20world%20have%20signed%20a%20letter%20of%20support%20for%20Palestinian%20literary%20voices%2C%20including%20author%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Faward-ceremony-at-frankfurt-book-fair-for-palestinian-author-adania-shibli-cancelled%5C%22%3EAdania%20Shibli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20reports%20emerged%20from%20across%20the%20world%20where%20events%20featuring%20Palestinian%20art%2C%20voices%2C%20and%20stories%20had%20been%20cancelled%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20terror%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20is%20the%20effort%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farablit.org%2F2023%2F10%2F16%2Fan-open-letter-in-support-of-adania-shiblis-minor-detail-and-palestinian-literary-voices%2F%5C%22%3EArabLit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20organisation%20which%20publishes%20%3Cem%3EArabLit%20Quarterly%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Emagazine%20featuring%20several%20translated%20works%20from%20Arabic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20recent%2C%20terrible%20days%20have%20seen%20%E2%80%93%20in%20several%20European%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20a%20closing-off%20and%20shutting%20down%20of%20cultural%20events%20that%20bring%20forward%20Palestinian%20art%2C%20voices%2C%20and%20stories%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farablit.org%2F2023%2F10%2F16%2Fan-open-letter-in-support-of-adania-shiblis-minor-detail-and-palestinian-literary-voices%2F%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20ArabLit%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20makes%20particular%20reference%20to%20award-winning%20Palestinian%20author%20Adania%20Shibli%2C%20wherein%20a%20ceremony%20scheduled%20for%20her%20to%20receive%20a%20prestigious%20award%20was%20cancelled%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShibli%2C%20who%20was%20a%20finalist%20for%20the%202020%20National%20Book%20Award%20for%20her%20book%C2%A0%3Ci%3EMinor%20Detail%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(New%20Directions%2FFitzcarraldo%2C%20translated%20by%20Elisabeth%20Jaquette)%2C%20was%20to%20receive%20Germany%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litprom.de%2Fen%2Fbest-books%2Fliberaturpreis%2Fthe-winner-2023%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520LiBeraturpreis%25202023%26amp%3Btext%3DPalestinian%2520author%2520Adania%2520Shibli%2520receives%2COrth%252C%2520published%2520by%2520Berenberg%2520Verlag.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E2023%20LiBeraturpreis%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20the%20same%20book%2C%20published%20in%20German%20as%C2%A0%3Ci%3EEine%20Nebensache%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(Berenberg%20Verlag%2C%20translated%20by%20G%C3%BCnther%20Orth)%20at%20the%202023%20Frankfurt%20Book%20Fair%2C%20which%20begins%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litprom.de%2Fen%2F%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20organisers%20of%20the%20prize%2C%20Litprom%2C%20which%20is%20funded%20in%20part%20by%20the%20German%20government%20and%20the%20Frankfurt%20Book%20Fair%2C%20said%20on%20October%2013%20that%20she%20would%20no%20longer%20receive%20the%20prize%20during%20the%20book%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%C2%A0a%20public%20discussion%20with%20Shibli%20and%20her%20translator%20G%C3%BCnther%20Orth%20at%20the%20book%20fair%20has%20also%20been%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20statement%20by%20Litprom%20wrongly%20claimed%20that%20Shibli%20was%20consulted%20before%20the%20decision.%20However%2C%20Shibli%20said%20it%20was%20not%20discussed%20with%20her%20before%20the%20release%20of%20the%20statement%2C%20but%20was%20only%20presented%20to%20her%20after%20the%20decision%20had%20already%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20of%20Frankfurt%20Book%20Fair%2C%20which%20funds%20Litprom%2C%20also%20said%20it%20stands%20in%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCyV_bnoouAw%2F%5C%22%3Ecomplete%20solidarity%20on%20the%20side%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20make%20Jewish%20and%20Israeli%20voices%20%E2%80%9Cespecially%20visible%20at%20the%20fair%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20also%20condemned%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffreedom_theatre%2Fstatus%2F1712440518880153934%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%3Ecancellation%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20play%20of%20Hassan%20Abdulrazzak%20%E2%80%98And%20Here%20I%20Am%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20mayor%20of%20%3Cspan%3EChoisy-le-Roi%2C%20a%20commune%20in%20France.%20Abdulrazzak%E2%80%99s%20play%20is%20around%20the%20coming-of-age%20story%20of%20actor-director%20Ahmed%20Tobasi%2C%20born%20in%20Jenin%20during%20the%20first%20intifada%20of%20Palestine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20launch%20of%20%3Cem%3EA%20Day%20in%20the%20Life%20of%20Abed%20Salama%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Nathan%20Thrall%E2%80%99s%20book%2C%20was%20cancelled%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20concerns%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20of%20support%20was%20signed%20by%2C%20among%20others%2C%20Nobel%20Prize%20laureates%20Abdulrazak%20Gurnah%2C%20Annie%20Ernaux%2C%20and%20Olga%20Tokarczuk%3B%20Booker%20Prize%20winners%20Anne%20Enright%2C%20Richard%20Flanagan%2C%20and%20Ian%20McEwan%3B%202021%20winner%20of%20the%20Litprom%20prize%20Pilar%20Quintana%20and%202015%20winner%20Madeleine%20Thien%3B%20dozens%20of%20publishers%20and%20literary%20agents%3B%20as%20well%20as%20many%20concerned%20writers%20from%20around%20the%20globe.%20There%20are%20now%20more%20than%201%2C300%20signatories%2C%20ArabLit%20said%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20the%20letter%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20shocking%20and%20tragic%20events%20that%20began%20on%20October%207th%20and%20are%20ongoing%20today%20have%20had%20repercussions%20all%20over%20the%20globe%2C%20including%20within%20the%20publishing%20world.%20Award-winning%20Palestinian%20author%20Adania%20Shibli%2C%20who%20was%20a%20finalist%20for%20the%202020%20National%20Book%20Award%20for%20her%20book%C2%A0%3Ci%3EMinor%20Detail%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(New%20Directions%2FFitzcarraldo%2C%20translated%20by%20Elisabeth%20Jaquette)%2C%20was%20to%20receive%20Germany%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litprom.de%2Fen%2Fbest-books%2Fliberaturpreis%2Fthe-winner-2023%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520LiBeraturpreis%25202023%26amp%3Btext%3DPalestinian%2520author%2520Adania%2520Shibli%2520receives%2COrth%252C%2520published%2520by%2520Berenberg%2520Verlag.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E2023%20LiBeraturpreis%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20the%20same%20book%2C%20published%20in%20German%20as%C2%A0%3Ci%3EEine%20Nebensache%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(Berenberg%20Verlag%2C%20translated%20by%20G%C3%BCnther%20Orth)%20at%20the%202023%20Frankfurt%20Book%20Fair%2C%20which%20begins%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2013%2C%20the%20organizers%20of%20the%20prize%2C%20Litprom%2C%20which%20is%20funded%20in%20part%20by%20the%20German%20government%20and%20the%20Frankfurt%20Book%20Fair%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litprom.de%2Fen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereleased%20a%20statement%20saying%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Shibli%20would%20no%20longer%20receive%20the%20prize%20during%20the%20book%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20a%20public%20discussion%20with%20Adania%20Shibli%20and%20her%20translator%20G%C3%BCnther%20Orth%20at%20the%20book%20fair%20has%20also%20been%20canceled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20originally%20said%20that%20this%20decision%20had%20been%20made%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20author%2C%20which%20was%20then%20relayed%2C%20without%20verification%2C%20by%20an%20article%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F13%2Fbooks%2Ffrankfurt-book-fair-cancels-award-adania-shibli.html%3Funlocked_article_code%3Dod51UV2wwU5LpwBzcCN5WjlbZ9MVwjVX7RjEuujfuCZGcwCdT522_QHNlGtz6lIds9cZyKEJ-cp5J_G3htLwXhM_pZ4LYTrq4AKa20DACp3JmqXwnTpFYs3lhCk8A58Wd8p0qrTBZzCUuT0bs1BcJl41dpPiimmqXUEOcC4aX8PzEdMDG_hnNUD0Y7zAYSmgeeax2JIu5ZSMTNYiHKrV7c2SFBTnukhHA1Y0b1epsIMRaMculAP-U01ZI_Jz0fgZugTdC2LeZ4Ia06tJISkvkFPsZjarGnlanOL4_ClwlkR5EQGmw5qcke-qOqNU3FofiYqdiklOQZ8lgYT2bkdmCPbxJeD58FXzQjXy0nMMWpW4rRzGt4ST%26smid%3Durl-share%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(now%20corrected).%20This%20is%20untrue%3B%C2%A0Adania%20Shibli%20has%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20not%20made%20with%20her%2C%C2%A0she%20was%20presented%20with%20the%20decision.%20If%20the%20ceremony%20were%20held%2C%20she%20said%2C%20she%20would%20have%20taken%20the%20opportunity%20to%20reflect%20on%20the%20role%20of%20literature%20in%20these%20cruel%20and%20painful%20times.%20(Litprom%20and%20The%20Times%20have%20since%20made%20corrections.)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShibli%E2%80%99s%20US%20publisher%2C%20Barbara%20Epler%20of%20New%20Directions%2C%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20editor%20of%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20which%20we%20excerpt%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EWith%20the%20unbelievable%20heartbreak%20that%20is%20now%20being%20suffered%20on%20all%20sides%2C%20it%20serves%20no%20one%20to%20put%20forward%20falsehoods%2C%20especially%20about%20the%20author%20of%20a%20novel%20about%20the%20Nakba%20that%20is%20so%20historically%20true.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ETo%20cancel%20the%20ceremony%20and%20so%20try%20to%20silence%20the%20voice%20of%20Adania%20Shibli%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Israel%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20is%20cowardly.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EBut%20to%20say%20Shibli%20agreed%20(amid%20all%20the%20suffering%20in%20Gaza)%20is%20worse.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20fair%20has%20issued%20a%20statement%20saying%20it%20wants%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCyV_bnoouAw%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emake%20Israeli%20voices%20%E2%80%9Cespecially%20visible%20at%20the%20fair%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0they%20are%20closing%20out%20the%20space%20for%20a%20Palestinian%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Shibli%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ci%3EMinor%20Detail%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0has%20been%20smeared%20as%20being%20anti-Semitic%20by%20two%20journalists%20and%20literary%20editors%2C%20other%20serious%20literary%20critics%20have%20clearly%20refuted%20this%20in%20the%20German%20press%20and%20elsewhere.%20The%20book%20makes%20reference%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2F2003-10-29%2Fty-article%2Fi-saw-fit-to-remove-her-from-the-world%2F0000017f-db62-d856-a37f-ffe2fa5b0000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewell-documented%20events%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0related%20to%20the%20rape%20of%20a%20Bedouin%20girl%20in%201949%20by%20an%20Israeli%20army%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShibli%E2%80%99s%20UK%20publisher%2C%20Jacques%20Testard%20of%20Fitzcarraldo%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20purposes%20of%20literature%20is%20to%20encourage%20understanding%20and%20dialogue%20between%20cultures.%20At%20a%20time%20of%20such%20horrific%20violence%20and%20heartbreak%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20book%20fair%20has%20a%20duty%20to%20champion%20literary%20voices%20from%20Palestine%20and%20Israel.%20We%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Adania%20Shibli%20and%20her%20German%20publishers%2C%20Berenberg%20Verlag.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20spirit%2C%20those%20of%20us%20involved%20in%20writing%2C%20translation%2C%20and%20publishing%20strongly%20assert%20that%20canceling%20cultural%20events%20is%20not%20the%20way%20forward.%20We%20recall%20the%20Frankfurt%20book%20fair%20supporting%20Turkish%20publishers%2C%20and%20how%20last%20year%20Ukrainian%20president%20Zelensky%20spoke%20to%20the%20fair%20in%20a%20pre-recorded%20address.%C2%A0The%20Frankfurt%20Book%20Fair%20has%20a%20responsibility%2C%20as%20a%20major%20international%20book%20fair%2C%20to%20be%20creating%20spaces%20for%20Palestinian%20writers%20to%20share%20their%20thoughts%2C%20feelings%2C%20reflections%20on%20literature%20through%20these%20terrible%2C%20cruel%20times%2C%20not%20shutting%20them%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20look%20for%20new%20language%20and%20new%20ideas%20in%20order%20to%20approach%20these%20bleak%20times%20in%20a%20new%20way.%20For%20this%2C%20we%20need%20writers%20%E2%80%93%20including%20Palestinian%20writers%20%E2%80%93%20more%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697807736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19123630%2FF8exa0MXQAAjnaV.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-1300-writers-publishers-decry-cancellation-of-events-featuring-palestinian-authors-artists%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20letter%20of%20support%2C%20signed%20by%20several%20Nobel%20laureates%20and%20Booker%20Prize%20winners%2C%20condemned%20the%20cancellation%20of%20events%20featuring%20Palestinian%20art%2C%20voices%2C%20and%20stories%20across%20Europe%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fover-1300-writers-publishers-decry-cancellation-of-events-featuring-palestinian-authors-artists%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Instagram%20sorry%20for%20adding%20'terrorist'%20to%20some%20Palestinian%20user%20bios%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697806607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1809A%2Fproduction%2F_131485489_gettyimages-1636801385-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67169228%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20says%20it%20fixed%20a%20problem%20%26quot%3Bthat%20briefly%20caused%20inappropriate%20translations%26quot%3B%20in%20some%20Instagram%20profiles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A169%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67169228%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67169228.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67169228.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Use%20are%20Token%20Policies%20for%20the%20Potters%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Kumhar%20Gram%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20151149%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-3.06.45-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Vishwakarma%20Scheme%2C%20a%20central%20government%20scheme%20meant%20to%20to%20provide%20end-to-end%20support%20to%20artisans%20and%20craftspeople%2C%20was%20launched%20on%20September%2017%2C%202023%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20The%20scheme%20covers%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.india.gov.in%2Fspotlight%2Fpradhan-mantri-vishwakarma-scheme%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eartisans%20and%20craftspeople%20engaged%20in%2018%20trades%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20including%20potters%20(%3Cem%3Ekumhars%3C%2Fem%3E).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20India%20has%20seen%20a%20large%20number%20of%20such%20government%20schemes%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98intention%E2%80%99%20to%20bolster%20the%20arts%20and%20crafts%20sector%20across%20India.%20Those%20engaged%20in%20the%20craft%20of%20pottery%20have%20also%20been%20connected%20to%20these%20schemes%20but%20have%20found%20find%20little%20support%20in%20their%20livelihood%2C%20or%20in%20terms%20of%20protecting%20the%20craft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20initiatives%20include%20a%20broad%20spectrum%20of%20objectives%2C%20from%20skill%20upgradation%20to%20facilitating%20the%20market%20for%20their%20final%20products.%20Falling%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Micro%2C%20Small%20and%20Medium%20Enterprises%20(MSME)%2C%20pottery%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20cherished%20and%20prioritised%20craft%20among%20all.%20Or%20so%20they%20say.%20While%20the%20expansion%20of%20these%20initiatives%20seems%20promising%20in%20theory%2C%20the%20on-ground%20reality%20offers%20a%20contrasting%20perspective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20field%20researchers%20as%20part%20of%20an%20ethnographic%20project%20undertaken%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40centreforneweconomicsstudi8523%2Fplaylists%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVisual%20Storyboard%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20team%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20masters%2C%20craftspeople%2C%20and%20entrepreneurs%20of%20Uttam%20Nagar%E2%80%99s%20potter%20colony.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20the%20long%20search%20of%20%E2%80%98actual%E2%80%99%20government%20support%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20our%20researchers%20asked%20the%20respondents%20whether%20they%20had%20received%20any%20assistance%20from%20the%20government%2C%20we%20received%20a%20unanimous%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eno%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Notably%2C%20the%20schemes%20available%20to%20these%20potters%20were%20limited%20to%20the%20ones%20designated%20for%20individuals%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENonetheless%2C%20it%20is%20incredibly%20vital%20to%20emphasise%20the%20stark%20absence%20of%20knowledge%20regarding%20the%20schemes%20made%20for%20them%20specifically.%20%E2%80%9CI%20personally%20feel%20that%20the%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20offer%20us%20any%20assistance%2C%20not%20even%20a%20rupee.%20Here%20in%20our%20community%2C%20all%20of%20us%20are%20self-reliant%20and%20dedicated%20to%20sustaining%20our%20businesses%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20we%20gain%20a%20profit%20or%20incur%20losses.%20We%20rarely%20seek%20external%20help%20or%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Narendra%20Kumar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kumhar%20Gram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20absolutely%20no%20government%20schemes%20that%20offer%20us%20any%20form%20of%20assistance.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20covering%20our%20electricity%20bills%20or%20medical%20expenses%20at%20hospitals%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20on%20our%20own.%20In%20case%20of%20medical%20emergencies%2C%20we%20resort%20to%20private%20hospitals%20which%20can%20be%20quite%20costly.%20Government%20hospitals%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20are%20overcrowded%20and%20busy%2C%20making%20it%20nearly%20impossible%20for%20us%20to%20access%20their%20services.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fbaked-in-the-sun-consumed-by-the-smoke-the-potters-of-delhis-kumhar-gram%5C%22%3EBaked%20In%20The%20Sun%2C%20Consumed%20By%20The%20Smoke%3A%20The%20Potters%20Of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Kumhar%20Gram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20is%20there%20such%20a%20significant%20disparity%20between%20the%20schemes%20that%20come%20from%20the%20government%20and%20those%20that%20reach%20the%20supposed%20beneficiaries%3F%20This%20is%20a%20classic%20%E2%80%98hope%20vs%20reality%E2%80%99%20conundrum%20that%20many%20potters%20fail%20to%20fathom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20our%20team%20inquired%20further%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20the%20issue%20was%20unawareness%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20stemmed%20from%20issues%20related%20to%20accessibility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIneffective%20enforcement%20of%20a%20scheme%20and%20unsupportive%20officials%20exacerbate%20the%20anxieties%20within%20the%20community.%20Difficulty%20in%20acquiring%20loans%20is%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20this%20problem%20manifests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENarendra%20Kumar%2C%20dubbed%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98terracotta%20%3Cem%3Eguru%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0within%20the%20community%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTill%20now%2C%20there%20has%20been%20little%20to%20no%20help%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20end%20to%20help%20us%20acquire%20loans.%20It%20almost%20seems%20like%20we%2C%20the%20entire%20community%20of%20Uttam%20Nagar%2C%20have%20been%20blacklisted%20by%20the%20banks.%20Banks%20frequently%20decline%20our%20loan%20applications%20without%20providing%20any%20valid%20justification.%20Private%20banks%20still%20might%20give%20us%20a%20loan%20after%20looking%20at%20our%20business%2C%20but%20we%20have%20no%20such%20hopes%20from%20public%20banks.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20to%20elaborate%20on%20the%20alleged%20blacklisting%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20exact%20cause%20of%20our%20blacklisting%20remains%20unclear.%20It%20could%20be%20due%20to%20a%20past%20instance%20where%20someone%20from%20our%20community%20may%20have%20defaulted%20on%20a%20loan.%20Another%20contributing%20factor%20may%20be%20that%20all%20of%20us%20who%20reside%20here%20have%20purchased%20and%20settled%20on%20the%20land%20independently%2C%20as%20it%20is%20not%20a%20government-designated%20colony.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEnvironmental%20concerns%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20one%20hand%2C%20national%20award%20winning%20potter%20Girraj%20Prasad%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.babushahi.com%2Ffull-news.php%3Fid%3D170846%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20garnered%20recognition%20by%20exhibiting%20terracotta%20craft%20at%20the%20G20%20Crafts%20Bazaar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%2C%20the%20community%20of%20potters%20residing%20in%20Uttam%20Nagar%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fphotos%2Findia-news%2Fngt-pollution-ban-looms-large-over-delhi-potter-s-colony%2Fphoto-NEqhZvsGfXg0GpRgVDdRmI-3.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20the%20edge%20of%20losing%20their%20livelihood%20over%20pollution%20concerns.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20potters%E2%80%99%20colony%20with%20its%20visible%20smoke%20is%20an%20obvious%20target%20because%20Delhi%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20pollution%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrequently%20under%20the%20national%20green%20tribunal%E2%80%99s%20(NGT%E2%80%99s)%20scanner%20for%20contributing%20to%20air%20pollution%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20community%20has%20something%20different%20to%20say%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98harms%E2%80%99%20caused%20by%20the%20fumes.%20Ramesh%20Kumar%20(50)%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20and%20even%20grandfather%2C%20worked%20in%20the%20same%20industry%20for%20several%20decades%20and%20they%20have%20never%20faced%20any%20health%20issues%20due%20to%20the%20work.%20Since%20we%20do%20not%20use%20any%20chemical%2C%20the%20smoke%20isn%E2%80%99t%20harmful.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20151307%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-3.05.30-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20151307%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-3.05.30-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20151307%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-3.05.30-PM-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20151307%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-3.05.30-PM-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681043%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPotter%E2%80%99s%20colony%20in%20Uttam%20Nagar.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20they%20employ%20clay%20ovens%20or%20kilns%20that%20are%20fueled%20by%20burning%20wood%20husk%20and%20cow%20dung%2C%20the%20potters%20assert%20that%20their%20production%20method%20may%20be%20regarded%20as%20entirely%20organic.%20On%20each%20side%20of%20the%20lane%20are%20dwellings%20made%20of%20clay%2C%20and%20the%20streets%20are%20covered%20in%20heaps%20of%20it.%20A%20certain%20family%20is%20responsible%20for%20each%20mound.%20The%20majority%20of%20the%20homes%20have%20two%20stories%2C%20and%20virtually%20all%20of%20them%20have%20kilns%2C%20either%20within%20or%20protruding%20from%20a%20higher%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20further%20inquiry%2C%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20smoke%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20wood%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20harm%20a%20human%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20rubber%20and%20chemicals%20that%20do.%20We%20only%20burn%20wood%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eburadda%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(wood%20flakes)%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbad%E2%80%9D%20smoke%20that%20comes%20as%20a%20by-product.%20Oil-based%20fire%20is%20harmful%20as%20well.%20There%E2%80%99s%20more%20dangerous%20smoke%20that%20gets%20released%20during%20stubble%20burning%20and%20forest%20fires%2C%20but%20no%20one%20talks%20about%20that.%20These%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebhattis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(kilns)%20are%20our%20livelihood%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20that%20an%20hour%20of%20us%20baking%20our%20products%20causes%20any%20damage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20evident%20by%20the%20precarious%20conditions%20of%20the%20potters%20it%20is%20not%20really%20their%20voices%20and%20concerns%20that%20are%20shaping%20these%20%E2%80%98reformatory%20policies.%E2%80%99%20They%20are%20the%20voices%20of%20the%201990s%20liberalisation%20policies%20which%20had%20the%20goal%20of%20making%20Delhi%20a%20metropolis%20of%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20potters%E2%80%99%20village%E2%80%99s%20future%20is%20unknown%2C%20there%20is%20no%20indication%20of%20unfavourable%20unrest%20on%20the%20streets.%20Every%20year%2C%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20Diwali%20are%20their%20busiest%20and%20business%20is%20brisk%20because%20in%20addition%20to%20serving%20the%20Indian%20market%2C%20they%20also%20export%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ediyas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20nations%20with%20sizable%20Indian%20diasporas%2C%20like%20Australia%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20there%20being%20a%20tremendous%20demand%20for%20their%20craft%20during%20the%20festive%20season%2C%20uncertainty%20continues%20to%20surround%20their%20livelihood.%20With%20the%20time%20commitment%20that%20the%20craft%20requires%2C%20it%20is%20unavoidably%20challenging%20for%20the%20artisans%20to%20chase%20behind%20every%20new%20policy%20and%20law%20reform.%20In%20the%20small%20alleys%20with%20mounds%20of%20mud%20and%20half-baked%20pots%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20general%20sense%20of%20unawareness%20and%20disunity%20attributable%20to%20their%20socio-economic%20backgrounds%2C%20historical%20and%20systematic%20marginalisation%2C%20and%20a%20pressure%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20such%20circumstances%2C%20the%20site%20of%20research%20for%20collecting%20data%20and%20policy-making%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmonoskop.org%2Fimages%2F4%2F4e%2FSaid_Edward_Orientalism_1979.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20Edward%20Said%20would%20argue%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20should%20refrain%20from%20the%20shadows%20of%20an%20institution%20that%20%E2%80%98makes%20statements%20about%20it%20%5Bthe%20orient%5D%2C%20authorising%20views%20of%20it%2C%20describing%20it%2C%20by%20teaching%20about%20it%2C%20settling%20it%2C%20ruling%20over%20it.%E2%80%99%20Instead%2C%20a%20complexly%20situated%20community%20of%20vulnerable%20artisans%20desires%20a%20body%20of%20knowledge%20that%20acknowledges%20the%20significance%20of%20their%20perspectives%20and%20attempts%20to%20account%20for%20how%2C%20and%20why%2C%20such%20perspectives%20may%20have%20developed%3B%20that%20would%20eventually%20affect%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20community%20to%20avail%20a%20positive%20flow%20of%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20artisans%20of%20India%2C%20we%20are%20far%20away%20from%20the%20realisation%20of%20rights%20that%20lead%20to%20the%20enhancement%20of%20their%20capabilities%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20provide%20meaning%20and%20purpose%20in%20their%20efforts%20to%20practice%20and%20conserve%20the%20craft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20article%20of%20a%20two-part%20series%20from%20CNES%E2%80%99%20Visual%20Storyboard%20team%20from%20a%20field%20project%20focusing%20on%20the%20lives-livelihoods%20of%20West%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20pottery%20makers%20and%20their%20endangered%20craft.%20You%20can%20read%20the%20first%20part%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fbaked-in-the-sun-consumed-by-the-smoke-the-potters-of-delhis-kumhar-gram%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cb%3ETavleen%20Kaur%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Senior%20Research%20Assistant%20and%20Team%20Lead%20of%C2%A0Swabhimaan%C2%A0and%C2%A0Visual%20Storyboard%C2%A0initiatives%20with%20CNES.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cb%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0is%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20and%20Director%2C%20CNES.%20He%20is%20currently%20an%20Honorary%20Research%20Fellow%20with%20Birkbeck%20College%2C%20University%20of%20London%20and%20a%20Visiting%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20at%20School%20of%20International%20Development%20and%20Global%20Studies%2C%20University%20of%20Ottawa%2C%20Canada.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cb%3EAnousha%20Singh%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Research%20Intern%20with%20CNES%20and%20a%20student%20of%20Delhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20Ramanujan%20College.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697805917000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20151149%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-3.06.45-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fwhat-use-are-token-policies-for-the-potters-of-delhis-kumhar-gram%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20expansion%20of%20these%20initiatives%20and%20schemes%20seem%20promising%20in%20theory%2C%20on-ground%20reality%20offers%20a%20contrasting%20perspective.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fwhat-use-are-token-policies-for-the-potters-of-delhis-kumhar-gram%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98If%20Only%20the%20Government%20Worked%20as%20Hard%20as%20Waste%20Pickers%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20124808%2Fimage-two-people.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBahadurgarh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Among%20the%20flurry%20of%20lush%20green%20farmlands%20at%20the%20Delhi-Haryana%20border%2C%20hundreds%20of%20scrap%20dealers%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20process%20of%20recycling%20nearly%20all%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20plastic%20waste%20tucked%20safely%20away%20from%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20kilometres%20from%20Tikri%20Kalan%E2%80%99s%20PVC%20market%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20legitimate%20plastic%20markets%20in%20Delhi%2C%20acres%20of%20agricultural%20land%20in%20Shiddipur%20and%20Lowa%20Kalan%20has%20been%20turned%20into%20an%20open%20plastic%20market.%20Each%20trader%20in%20this%20area%20deals%20with%20nearly%20300-500%20kg%20of%20plastic%20waste%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2F690-tonnes-added-daily-to-plastic-waste-mess%2Farticleshow%2F90001711.cms%5C%22%3Ereport%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Science%20and%20Environment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Delhi%20generates%20over%20600%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%20daily.%20Most%20of%20this%20waste%20is%20brought%20to%20plastic%20markets%20like%20the%20one%20at%20Tikri%20where%20these%20dealers%20or%20%3Cem%3Eaardhis%3C%2Fem%3E%20segregate%20and%20reduce%20it%20to%20shreds%20before%20selling%20it%20forward.%20They%20are%20the%20most%20important%20link%20in%20the%20plastic%20recycling%20chain%2C%20and%20also%20the%20ones%20facing%20the%20most%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERunning%20nearly%20entirely%20as%20an%20informal%20economy%2C%20aardhis%20have%20the%20skill%20and%20eye%20to%20sort%20the%20waste%20without%20any%20chemical%20testing%20or%20lab%20equipment.%20All%20they%20need%20is%20empty%20stretches%20of%20land.%20However%2C%20they%20are%20constantly%20caught%20in%20a%20cat-and-mouse%20chase%20with%20the%20authorities.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20we%20were%20removed%20from%20Mundka%2C%20then%20from%20Kamruddin%20Nagar%20and%20they%20are%20still%20chasing%20us%20away%20even%20after%20we%E2%80%99ve%20crossed%20the%20Delhi%20border%E2%80%9D%20said%2038-year-old%20Rajesh%2C%20an%20aardhi%20at%20the%20Shiddipur%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajesh%20and%20Bablu%20weren%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20%3Cem%3Eaardhis%3C%2Fem%3E%20angry%20with%20the%20government.%20The%20huddle%20of%20two%20gradually%20swelled%20to%20about%2015%20men%20and%20a%20few%20women%20all%20expressing%20their%20frustration%20at%20the%20treatment%20they%20receive%20from%20the%20municipal%20corporation%20and%20national%20green%20tribunal%20officials.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20come%20and%20raze%20our%20temporary%20structures%20whenever%20they%20feel%20like%20it.%20I%20want%20to%20quit%20this%20profession%20now.%20If%20the%20government%20worked%20as%20hard%20as%20the%20waste%20pickers%2C%20the%20country%20would%20be%20elsewhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%2055-year-old%20Mangeram%2C%20who%20lost%20most%20of%20his%20business%20when%20he%20left%20the%20market%20at%20Mundka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAardhis%20believe%20that%20they%20are%20not%20the%20problem%2C%20but%20a%20solution%20to%20a%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20plastic%20is%20not%20going%20to%20decompose%20itself.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20clean%20this%20mess%20then%20there%20will%20be%20heaps%20lying%20around%20in%20the%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%2025-year-old%20Sonu%2C%20who%20works%20with%20his%20father%20at%20the%20market%20in%20Lowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20aardhis%20told%20me%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20waste%20that%20makes%20it%20way%20to%20these%20plastic%20markets.%20The%20government%20imports%20plastic%20waste%2C%20charges%20a%20custom%20duty%20on%20it%20and%20then%20the%20dealers%20pay%20an%2018%25%20GST%20on%20subsequent%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20is%20trying%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20bigger%20factories%20contributing%20to%20pollution%20in%20broad%20daylight%20because%20their%20owners%20can%20pay%20off%20the%20officials.%20We%20are%20preventing%20pollution%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20but%20nobody%20cares%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%2036-year-old%20aardhi%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20traders%20work%20under%20the%20scorching%20sun%20without%20access%20to%20toilets%20or%20a%20clean%20resting%20place%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20refuge%20away%20from%20the%20piles%20of%20waste.%20While%20they%20pride%20themselves%20on%20keeping%20Delhi%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20coming%20to%20a%20standstill%2C%20trapped%20under%20its%20own%20garbage%E2%80%9D%2C%20most%20of%20them%20seem%20to%20have%20lost%20hope%20and%20plan%20to%20move%20back%20to%20their%20villages%20if%20they%20face%20further%20harassment%20by%20government%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20ironic%20that%20their%20contribution%20to%20waste%20management%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20guarantee%20them%20any%20financial%20or%20personal%20security.%20To%20quote%20Kaveri%20Gill%2C%20the%20author%20%3Cem%3EOf%20Plastic%20and%20Poverty%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20few%20to%20document%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20informal%20recycling%20markets%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20them%2C%20leave%20them%20alone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fekaansh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEkaansh%20Arora%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697805038000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20124808%2Fimage-two-people.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fonly-if-the-government-worked-as-hard-as-waste-pickers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hundreds%20of%20scrap%20dealers%20are%20recycling%20most%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20plastic%20waste%20while%20being%20on%20the%20run%20from%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fonly-if-the-government-worked-as-hard-as-waste-pickers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CDS's%20Undiplomatic%20Talk%20of%20Russian%20'Decline'%20Turns%20Focus%20on%20Weapon%20Procurement%20Challenges%20India%20May%20Face%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20153016%2Fimage-1417.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Should%20the%20Indian%20government%20take%20note%20of%20%E2%80%93%20and%20act%20upon%20%E2%80%93%20the%20geopolitical%20death%20knell%20of%20Russian%20power%20and%20influence%20that%20has%20been%20sounded%20publicly%20by%20its%20topmost%20soldier%2C%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20General%20Anil%20Chauhan%3F%20Or%20has%20the%20CDS%20spoken%20out%20of%20turn%20and%20been%20unduly%20alarmist%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPravinSawhney%2Fstatus%2F1713855705806176497%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPravinSawhney%2Fstatus%2F1713855705806176497%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1697861064113000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3kFd9c08QWJzFXp4P298_T%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cpeddling%20US%20propaganda%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20one%20defence%20analyst%20has%20claimed%3F%20The%20question%20is%20not%20an%20academic%20one%20as%20Russia%20is%20still%20India%E2%80%99s%C2%A0principal%20materiel%20supplier%20and%20%E2%80%98decoupling%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20essence%20of%20what%20the%20CDS%20seems%20to%20be%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelivering%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2FfIiH5%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2FfIiH5%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1697861064114000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3gzDtxpkF9GHoce09EBLu5%5C%22%3E14th%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20L.M.%20Katrememorial%20lecture%20in%20Bengaluru%20last%20weekend%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20General%20Chauhan%20declared%20that%20the%20geopolitical%20importance%20of%20Russia%20would%20decline%20in%20times%20to%20come%2C%20despite%20it%20being%20a%20nuclear%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Wagner%20rebellion%2C%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Moscow%E2%80%99s%20state-funded%20rogue%20private%20army%2C%20indicated%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20internal%20weakness%20and%20was%20indicative%20of%20what%20(adversity)%20may%20lie%20in%20store%20for%20its%20future%2C%20though%20he%20declined%20to%20elaborate%20on%20this%20point.%20The%20CDS%20further%20declared%20that%2C%20conversely%2C%20Beijing%E2%80%99s%20economic%20heft%20was%20now%20visible%20in%20the%20political%2C%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20domains%20and%20that%20the%20world%20would%20now%20see%20a%20more%20assertive%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20pessimistic%20and%20somewhat%20cynical%20public%20assessment%20regarding%20the%20future%20potential%20of%20a%20vital%20Indian%20ally%20and%20provider%20of%C2%A0%2045%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20defence%20equipment%20and%20over%2040%25%20of%20its%20oil%20imports%2C%20have%20been%20unfavourably%20received%20in%20official%20and%20diplomatic%20circles.%20Some%20media%20reports%20have%20asserted%20that%20this%20grouping%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20military%20personnel%20should%20not%20publicly%20make%20%E2%80%98inappropriate%E2%80%99%20statements%20and%20should%20not%20be%20making%20prophecies%20that%20have%20a%20major%20bearing%20on%20foreign%20policy%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20for%20decades%2C%20clearance%20by%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20Military%20Intelligence%20(MI)%20directorate%20was%20mandatory%20for%20all%20armed%20forces%20personnel%20before%20making%20any%20public%20statement%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20adverse%20%E2%80%93%20with%20regard%20to%20any%20other%20country%2C%20including%20Pakistan%2C%20as%20this%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20affect%20bilateral%20ties.%20It%20is%2C%20however%2C%20not%20known%20whether%20in%20recent%20years%20this%20stipulation%20remains%20valid%20or%2C%20like%20numerous%20other%20military%20protocols%2C%20has%20been%20dispensed%20with%2C%20especially%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20CDS%E2%80%99s%20public%20declarations%20on%20diplomatic%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20propriety%2C%20General%20Chauhan%20was%20voicing%20beliefs%20prevalent%20within%20domestic%20military%20circles%20regarding%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20declining%20power%20status%20and%20influence%2C%20following%20its%20ongoing%20catastrophic%20war%20with%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20consequent%20sanctions%20this%20had%20invited%20from%20the%20United%20States%20and%20its%20allies.%20Even%20though%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20vaunted%20military%20offensive%20has%20not%20altered%20the%20reality%20of%20Russian%20occupation%2C%20the%2020-month%20long%20war%20has%20effectively%20punctured%20the%20myth%20of%20Russian%20military%20indomitability%20and%20the%20competence%20of%20its%20varied%20platforms%20and%20equipment%20%E2%80%93%20a%20lot%20of%20which%20has%20proven%20operationally%20ineffective%20and%20inefficient%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20cross-section%20of%20serving%20and%20retired%20military%20officials%20privately%20doubted%20Moscow%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20maintain%20uninterrupted%20supplies%20of%20spares%2C%20components%20and%20sub-assemblies%20to%20India%20to%20sustain%20over%2065%25%20of%20in-service%20Russian%20equipment%2C%20and%20to%20deliver%20an%20assortment%20of%20platforms%20like%20air%20defence%20systems%2C%20frigates%2C%20a%20nuclear-powered%20attack%20submarine%20(SSN)%20and%20assault%20rifles%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20on%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20the%20services%20and%20officials%20in%20Moscow%20continue%20to%20put%20on%20a%20brave%20front%20by%20claiming%20that%20there%20are%20no%20hitches%20in%20bilateral%20military%20commerce%20between%20the%20two%20sides%2C%20problems%20endure%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20recently%20retired%20two-star%20Indian%20Army%20officer.%20These%20bottlenecks%20will%20continue%20to%20persist%2C%20and%20are%20likely%20to%20get%20worse%2C%20impinging%20negatively%20on%20our%20operational%20efficiency%2C%20he%20added%2C%20declining%20to%20be%20named%20given%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20military%E2%80%99s%20dependency%20on%20Moscow%20continues%20to%20be%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bulk%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%E2%80%99s%20(IAF)%2029-30%20fighter%20squadrons%20operate%20Russian%20platforms%20like%20260-odd%20multi-role%20%E2%80%98Flanker%E2%80%99%20Su-30MKIs%20fighters%2C%2084%20of%20which%20would%2C%20notably%2C%20be%20upgraded%20domestically%20to%20%E2%80%98Super%20Sukhoi%E2%80%99%20standards%20by%20fitting%20them%20with%205th%20generation%20features%20and%20rendering%20them%20capable%20of%20delivering%20a%20heavier%20weapons%20load.%20The%20IAF%20also%20employs%20some%2065%20retrofitted%20%E2%80%98Fulcrum%E2%80%99%20MiG-29UPG%20and%20around%2055-60%20%E2%80%98Fishbed%E2%80%99%20MiG%2021%20%E2%80%98Bis%E2%80%99%20ground%20attack%20combat%20aircraft%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20large%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Russian%20military%20transports%2C%20mid-air%20refuellers%20and%20varied%20helicopters%2C%20all%20of%20which%20frequently%20need%20spares%2C%20without%20which%20they%20are%20simply%20inoperable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlongside%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%E2%80%99s%20(IN)%20principal%20warships%20are%20predominantly%20Russian%20in%20both%20origin%20and%20design.%20These%20include%20%3Cem%3EINS%20Vikramaditya%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(ex-%3Cem%3EAdmiral%20Gorshkov%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20the%20retrofitted%2044%2C500%20tonne%20Kiev-class%20aircraft%20carrier%20and%20its%20combat%20air%20arm%20of%2016%20MiG-29K%2FKuB%20fighters.%20The%20force%20also%20has%20another%2028%20MiG-29Ks%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20temporarily%20comprise%20the%20combat%20fleet%20of%C2%A0the%20newly%20commissioned%20indigenous%20aircraft%20carrier%2C%20%3Cem%3EINS%20Vikrant%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20IN%20also%20deploys%20an%20assortment%20of%20Kamov%20%E2%80%98Helix%E2%80%99%20Ka-28%20and%20Ka-31%20airborne%20early%20warning%20and%20control%20(AEW%26amp%3BC)%20rotary%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IN%E2%80%99s%20underwater%20platforms%20too%20included%20nine%20%E2%80%98Kilo%E2%80%99-class%20Type%20877%20diesel-electric%20submarines%20of%20a%20total%20of%2016%20such%20boats%2C%20while%20Russia%20had%20also%20provided%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20assistance%20in%20designing%3Cem%3E%20INS%20Arihant%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20navy%E2%80%99s%20indigenously%20designed%20and%20built%20lead%20nuclear-powered%20ballistic%20missile%20submarine%20(SSBN)%20that%20joined%20service%20in%20August%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20also%20providing%20technical%20know-how%20to%20miniaturise%20the%2082.5MW%20reactor%20for%20the%204-5%20follow-on%20SSBN%E2%80%99s%20presently%20under%20construction%20at%20the%20classified%20Ship%20Building%20Centre%20at%20Visakhapatnam.%20No%20other%20country%20is%20willing%20to%20make%20such%20strategic%20technology%20transfers%20to%20India%2C%20but%20industry%20sources%20indicated%20that%20sanctions%20and%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20own%20needs%20could%20%E2%80%98thwart%E2%80%99%20Moscow%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20continue%20doing%20so%2C%20thereby%20imperilling%20the%20SSBN%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20over%2095%25%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%20fleet%20of%20around%203%2C000%20main%20battle%20tanks%20(MBTs)%20operated%20by%2067-odd%20armoured%20regiments%20were%20Russian%20T-72%20and%20T-90S%20variants%20%E2%80%93%20imported%20directly%20and%20licence%20built%20%E2%80%93%20whilst%20some%202%2C000-odd%20infantry%20combat%20vehicles%20or%20ICVs%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Boyevaya%20Mashina%20Pekhoty%20(BMP)%201%20and%202%20%E2%80%93%20were%20similarly%20sourced.%20The%20latter%20were%20presently%20being%20upgraded%20with%20Russian%20assistance%2C%20which%2C%20too%2C%20could%20summarily%20end%20or%20be%20adversely%20impacted%20by%20the%20ongoing%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecurity%20officials%20are%20also%20concerned%20over%20the%20symbiosis%20that%20has%C2%A0emerged%20in%20recent%20months%20between%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20whose%20army%20has%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20standoff%20with%20the%20Indian%20Army%20in%20Ladakh%20since%20May%202020.%20They%20said%20this%20burgeoning%20association%20anticipated%20Russia%20gravitating%20swiftly%20towards%20cash-rich%20China%20for%20assistance%20to%20overcome%20sanctions%20and%20embargoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20association%20could%20end%20up%20being%20a%20simple%20trade-off%20between%20advanced%20Russian%20military%20knowhow%20in%20exchange%20for%20Chinese%20cash%20and%20vast%20industrial%20manufacturing%20capacity%20of%20assorted%20defence%20equipment%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20Navy%20veteran.%20Such%20an%20arrangement%20would%20be%20one%20of%20mutual%20advantage%20to%20both%20sides%20and%20one%20that%20could%20easily%20be%20reached%2C%20if%20it%20had%20not%20already%20been%20concluded%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20veterans%20were%20of%20the%20view%20that%20such%20inescapable%20sanctions%20%E2%80%93%20busting%20endeavours%20by%20Russia%20%E2%80%93%20could%2C%20as%20%E2%80%98payback%E2%80%99%2C%20result%20in%20China%20eventually%20pressuring%20Moscow%20to%20stanch%2C%20if%20not%20altogether%20cease%20the%20supply%20of%20assorted%20materiel%20and%20related%20equipment%20to%20India%20which%2C%20ironically%2C%20Delhi%20had%20acquired%20over%20decades%20to%20deter%20Beijing%20and%20its%20military%20and%20nuclear%20ally%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reciprocal%20%E2%80%98no%20limits%E2%80%99%20friendship%20between%20Russia%20and%20China%20was%20on%20full%20display%20earlier%20this%20week%20in%20Beijing%2C%20where%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-67143322%5C%22%3Ehosted%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20130-nation%20jamboree%20to%20celebrate%20his%20signature%20decade-old%20global%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI).%20The%20BRI%20essentially%20envisages%20China%20investing%20in%20over%20150%20countries%20and%20international%20organisations%20to%20further%20its%20global%20strategic%20and%20financial%20influence%20to%20counter%20that%20of%20the%20US%20and%20the%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPutin%2C%20who%20has%20rarely%20left%20Russia%20after%20invading%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022%2C%20was%20the%20guest%20of%20honour%20at%20the%20meet.%20Speaking%20immediately%20after%20Xi%2C%20he%20pledged%20support%20to%20China%20and%20its%20BRI%20project%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20tune%20with%20Russian%20ideas%E2%80%9D%20and%20heaped%20lavish%20praise%20on%20Beijing%20for%20its%20achievements%20since%20the%20initiatives%20launched%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Beijing-Moscow%20axis%20that%20has%20been%20proliferating%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20is%20now%20poised%20to%20become%20firmer%2C%20posing%20a%20formidable%20threat%20to%20world%20peace%2C%20as%20both%20strive%20to%20aggressively%20carve%20out%20a%20new%20regional%20and%20global%20order%20based%20arbitrarily%20on%20financial%20and%20military%20might%20and%20the%20recent%20Israel-Gaza%20crisis%20had%20only%20worsened%20the%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Brigadier%20Rahul%20Bhonsle%20of%20the%20Security%20Risks%20consultancy%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20India%2C%20which%20had%20incrementally%20emerged%20as%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20proxy%20over%20the%20past%2015%20years%20to%20manage%20China%2C%20could%20well%20end%20up%20facing%20the%20brunt%20of%20this%20deadly%20security%20partnership%20between%20Moscow%2C%20Beijing%20and%20Islamabad%2C%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20veterans%20say%20General%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20forecast%20regarding%20Russia%20needs%20attention%2C%20it%20also%20presents%20the%20CDS%20and%20the%20three%20services%20with%20a%20further%20dilemma%20that%20somewhat%20bedevils%20easy%20resolution.%20And%20though%20defence%20diplomacy%20is%20part%20of%20the%20CDS%E2%80%99s%20overarching%20charter%2C%20making%20public%20statements%2C%20even%20if%20apposite%20and%20accurate%2C%20tend%20to%20constrict%20India%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20elbow%20room%20in%20the%20prevailing%20geopolitical%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20as%20the%20French%20statesman%20Georges%20Clemenceau%20memorably%20declared%3A%20%E2%80%98War%20is%20too%20serious%20a%20business%20to%20be%20left%20to%20the%20generals.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697804131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20153016%2Fimage-1417.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fcdss-undiplomatic-talk-of-russian-decline-turns-focus-on-weapon-procurement-challenges-india-may-face%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delivering%20the%2014th%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20L.M.%20Katrememorial%20lecture%20in%20Bengaluru%20last%20weekend%2C%20General%20Chauhan%20declared%20that%20the%20geopolitical%20importance%20of%20Russia%20would%20decline%20in%20times%20to%20come%2C%20despite%20it%20being%20a%20nuclear%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fcdss-undiplomatic-talk-of-russian-decline-turns-focus-on-weapon-procurement-challenges-india-may-face%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20charged%20after%20reported%20rape%20of%20British%20policewoman%20near%20Eiffel%20Tower%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-france-paris-eiffel-tower_6328202.jpg%3F20231020140252%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffrench-man-charged-after-