ons%20within%20Hamas%20(military%20and%20political)%20which%20are%20often%20at%20odds%20with%20each%20other.%20She%20believes%20that%20the%20October%207%20attack%20probably%20happened%20without%20the%20political%20division%20being%20aware%20or%20consulted.%20She%20also%20says%20that%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20Hamas%20is%20outside%20Gaza%20i.e.%20abroad%20and%20increasingly%20cut%20off%20from%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Gaza.%20She%20says%20there%20are%20also%20divisions%20between%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Hamas%20organisations%20in%20other%20parts%2C%20not%20just%20the%20West%20Bank%20but%20elsewhere%20too.%20She%20says%20Hamas%20has%20evolved%20in%20what%20it%20stands%20for%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20how%20it%20views%20Israel%20but%20also%20gone%20back%20and%20reversed%20itself.%20In%201987%2C%20when%20it%20was%20founded%2C%20it%20was%20committed%20to%20the%20elimination%20of%20Israel%2C%20including%20physically.%20The%20first%20signs%20of%20compromise%20happened%20in%202006-07%2C%20when%20Hamas%20won%20power%20in%20Gaza%20and%20became%20part%20of%20the%20institutional%20structure%20of%20politics.%20Reversal%20began%20to%20happen%20in%202011%2C%20when%201%2C027%20Hamas%20prisoners%20were%20released%20from%20Israeli%20jails%20and%20their%20influence%20radicalised%20the%20organization.%20A%20second%20compromise%20was%20apparent%20when%20Hamas%20changed%20its%20charter%20in%202017%20and%20accepted%20a%20sort%20of%20compromise%20whereby%20it%20was%20willing%20to%20live%20side%20by%20side%20with%20Israel%20but%20not%20recognise%20the%20existence%20of%20Israel.%20Since%20then%2C%20a%20reverse%20radicalisation%20has%20been%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWtGyBoVmbSI%3Fsi%3DJQrtKmoZryRQo4KH%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20complicated%20and%20difficult%20story%2C%20particularly%20for%20those%20who%20do%20not%20know%20Hamas%20and%20its%20history%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20different%20responses%20to%20Hamas%20and%20how%20the%20world%2C%20with%20its%20treatment%20of%20Hamas%2C%20has%20added%20to%20the%20complications.%20Paola%20Caridi%20attempts%20to%20explain%20all%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPaola%20Caridi%20also%20discusses%20how%20popular%20Hamas%20is%20in%20Gaza%2C%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20idea%20or%20an%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20asked%20the%20following%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E1)%20Forgive%20me%20if%20my%20questions%20seem%20basic%20and%20even%20rudimentary%2C%20but%20in%20India%20we%20know%20very%20little%20about%20Hamas.%20So%20can%20I%20start%20by%20asking%20how%20would%20you%20characterise%20or%20describe%20this%20organisation%3F%20At%20the%20moment%20most%20governments%20and%20media%20organisations%20call%20it%20a%20terrorist%20organisation.%20From%20your%20perception%20would%20that%20be%20correct%20or%20mistaken%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E2)%20What%20is%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20ideology%3F%20What%20are%20the%20principles%20and%20goals%20it%20stands%20for%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3)%20Now%20there%20are%20some%20reports%20that%20Israel%20has%20played%20a%20role%20in%20funding%20and%20supporting%20the%20founding%20of%20Hamas.%20I%20know%20that%20when%20he%20was%20military%20governor%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Gen%20Gonen%20Segev%20assisted%20and%20helped%20several%20religious%20based%20groups%20as%20a%20way%20of%20checking%20the%20secular%20PLO.%20Is%20that%20true%20of%20Hamas%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4)%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20original%20charter%20commits%20the%20organisation%20to%20work%20for%20the%20destruction%20or%20elimination%20of%20Israel%20but%20was%20there%20a%20significant%20change%20in%202017%20whereby%20without%20recognising%20Israel%20Hamas%20was%20prepared%20to%20accept%20its%20existence%20as%20a%20state%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E5)%20Since%202017%2C%20how%20would%20you%20describe%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20to%20Israel%20and%20how%20has%20it%20evolved%20between%202017%20and%202023%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E6)%20Hamas%20has%20fought%20several%20%E2%80%98wars%E2%80%99%20with%20Israel%20but%20the%20Israelis%20were%20convinced%20that%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%20at%20least%20that%20Hamas%20was%20focused%20on%20the%20development%20of%20Gaza%20and%20was%20no%20longer%20committed%20to%20overthrowing%20Israel.%20How%20serious%20a%20misreading%20of%20reality%20was%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E7)%20Do%20we%20know%20the%20specific%20reasons%20why%20Hamas%20launched%20this%20massive%20attack%20on%20October%207%3F%20And%20secondly%20what%20message%20was%20it%20sending%20by%20choosing%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Yom%20Kippur%20war%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E8)%20How%20popular%20is%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%3F%20We%E2%80%99re%20often%20told%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20represent%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20but%20does%20it%20or%20does%20it%20not%20represent%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E9)%20And%20what%20about%20the%20Palestinians%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%3F%20How%20do%20they%20view%20Hamas%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E10)%20Is%20Hamas%20misunderstood%20by%20the%20West%3F%20Even%20if%20understandable%2C%20is%20it%20seen%20through%20Israeli%20eyes%2C%20which%20are%20inevitably%20distorting%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E11)%20Is%20Hamas%20locked%20in%20a%20war%20with%20Israel%20that%20cannot%20be%20mediated%20and%20resolved%3F%20Or%20could%20Hamas%20agree%20to%20a%20two%20state%20solution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E12)%20Finally%20and%20I%E2%80%99ve%20deliberately%20left%20this%20to%20the%20end.%20Can%20Hamas%20be%20obliterated%20as%20Israel%20insists%3F%20In%20other%20words%20is%20it%20an%20idea%20or%20an%20organisation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E13)%20If%20it%E2%80%99s%20true%20that%20the%20Hamas%20security%20head%20has%20been%20killed%2C%20as%20the%20Palestine%20Authority%20has%20said%2C%20how%20serious%20a%20blow%20would%20this%20be%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E14)%20To%20what%20extent%20has%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20Palestine%20situation%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20prime%20minister%20made%20matters%20worse%20by%20adding%20to%20the%20problems%20with%20Hamas%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E15)%20Are%20there%20realists%20in%20Hamas%20who%20can%20identify%20what%20they%20can%20live%20with%20as%20a%20practical%20solution%3F%20It%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20everything%20they%20want%20but%20are%20there%20Hamas%20realists%20who%20agree%20on%20an%20outcome%20Israel%20can%20accept%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802335000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20165049%2FKT-20-b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-hamas-karan-thapar-paola-caridi-interview%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20Paola%20Caridi%2C%20the%20of%20author%20'Hamas%3A%20Resistance%20to%20Regime'%2C%20paints%20a%20complex%20and%20indeed%20complicated%20picture%20of%20the%20organisation%20responsible%20for%20the%20deadly%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-hamas-karan-thapar-paola-caridi-interview%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20conflict%3A%20Politicians%20are%20making%20matters%20worse%2C%20not%20better%20%7C%20Sean%20Bell%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F70x70%2Fskynews-sean-bell-teaser-gfximages_6329053.jpg%3F20231021000309%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-hamas-war-is-a-direct-result-of-a-failure-of-politics-and-diplomacy-and-politicians-are-making-things-worse-12988322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20explosion%20at%20t