y.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKarnataka%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Priyank%20Kharge%20also%20accused%20YouTube%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpreventing%20users%20from%20engaging%20with%20democratic%20voices.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHello%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYouTubeIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40YouTubeIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGoogleIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40GoogleIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20quite%20intriguing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20categorized%20the%20public%20speeches%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RahulGandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpriyankagandhi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40priyankagandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji%20as%20related%20to%20self-harm%20and%20suicide.%20Are%20you%20actively%20discouraging%2C%20dissuading%20and%20preventing%20viewers%20from%20engaging%20with%20democratic%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPPJsA6Qys8%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPPJsA6Qys8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Priyank%20Kharge%20%2F%20%E0%B2%AA%E0%B3%8D%E0%B2%B0%E0%B2%BF%E0%B2%AF%E0%B2%BE%E0%B2%82%E0%B2%95%E0%B3%8D%20%E0%B2%96%E0%B2%B0%E0%B3%8D%E0%B2%97%E0%B3%86%20(%40PriyankKharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPriyankKharge%2Fstatus%2F1715053462927601758%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20succumbing%20to%20pressure%20from%20the%20Central%20Government%20in%20making%20these%20decisions%2C%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20State%20Government%20is%20equally%20adept%20at%20this%20kind%20of%20maneuvering%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20w