ow%20one%20can%20set%20up%20their%20own%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%3C%2Fem%3E%20plant.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20that%20everyone%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20to%20invest%2050%20Lakhs%20in%20setting%20up%20the%20plant%2C%20so%20I%20made%20a%20plan%20that%20will%20help%20them%20do%20it%20with%20minimal%20investment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20comes%20with%20complete%20information%20on%20setting%20up%20of%20the%20plant.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20video%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20views%20and%20people%20started%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20me.%20The%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eway%20of%20making%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20by%20hand%2C%20but%20I%20have%20developed%20a%20machine%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20When%20a%20customer%20comes%20to%20us%2C%20we%20help%20them%20set%20up%20their%20factory%2C%20give%20them%20the%20machine%20and%20also%20train%20them%20in%20using%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20costs%20the%20people%20only%20about%20a%20percent%20of%20what%20Shobhit%20spent%20on%20setting%20up%20his%20plant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20watching%20the%20videos%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20aspiring%20people%20come%20to%20us%20to%20learn%20the%20process.%20Once%20we%20meet%20the%20client%2C%20a%20team%20goes%20to%20their%20location%20and%2C%20in%20a%20matter%20of%2010%20days%2C%20teaches%20them%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20scratch%20using%20our%20machinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20also%20helps%20them%20sell%20their%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20I%20have%20been%20in%20the%20business%20for%20some%20time%2C%20and%20also%20due%20to%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20video%2C%20I%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20calls%20from%20buyers%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20So%2C%20say%20a%20person%20from%20Karnataka%20wants%20to%20buy%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20will%20locate%20the%20plant%20set%20up%20in%20Karnataka%20and%