l%20information%2C%20and%20with%20that%20goal%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20started%20to%20research%20women%E2%80%99s%20representation%20in%20Indian%20electoral%20politics%20and%20began%20our%20work%20at%20Kuviraa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKuviraa%20is%20a%20nonpartisan%20initiative%20that%20works%20to%20build%20political%20leadership%20and%20civic%20action%20in%20adolescent%20girls%20across%20India.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20politics%20accessible%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F235373%2Findia-youth-young-inspiring-heroes-international-youth-day-innovation-bravery-courage-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20create%20spaces%20for%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20understand%20what%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F160414%2Fanudip-foundation-youth-skilling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20Indian%20%3C%2Fa%3Egirls%20thought%20of%20politics%20and%20if%20they%20were%20even%20interested%20in%20getting%20involved.%20Although%20there%20was%20some%20research%20done%20in%20the%20global%20context%2C%20we%20found%20no%20data%20on%20political%20interest%20or%20engagement%20among%20Indian%20adolescents%20to%20start%20off%20with.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThrough%20interviews%20with%20adolescent%20girls%2C%20parents%20and%20school%20leaders%2C%20we%20learnt%20that%20politics%20was%20not%20an%20aspirational%20career%20choice%20for%20many%20in%20India%20because%20of%20the%20stigma%20attached%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20found%20that%20schools%20and%20parents%20were%20even%20reluctant%20to%20speak%20to%20their%20children%20about%20politics.%20Some%20teachers%20whom%20we%20interviewed%20told%20us%20that%20we%20were%20welcome%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20students%20about%20policies%20but%20not%20politics%20as%20it%20could%20be%20divisive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20improve%20political%20representation%20and%20engagement%2C%20we%20need%20to%20spark%20political%20interest%20and%20civic%20action%20at%20a%20young%20age.%20For%20this%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20understand%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20decided%20to%20conduct%20a%20study%20with%20researchers%20from%20the%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fluskin.ucla.edu%2Fsocial-welfare%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20California%2C%20Los%20Angeles%E2%80%99%20Department%20of%20Social%20Welfare%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESara%20Wilf%2C%20the%20lead%20researcher%20on%20this%20study%2C%20explains%20how%20the%20study%20aims%20to%20fill%20the%20knowledge%20gap%20between%20gender%20disparities%20in%20political%20interest%20and%20engagement%20across%20adolescence%20and%20young%20adulthood%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20thrilled%20to%20work%20on%20this%20research%20with%20Kuviraa%20and%20their%20brilliant%20volunteers%20who%20care%20so%20deeply%20about%20this%20issue.%20I%E2%80%99m%20excited%20that%20this%20study%20both%20gives%20practical%20recommendations%20for%20parents%20and%20educators%20to%20increase%20female%20political%20engagement%2C%20and%20identifies%20many%20pathways%20for%20future%20research%20into%20a%20topic%20that%20is%20critical%20for%20equity%20and%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sara%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKey%20research%20findings%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20report%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kuviraa.org%2F_files%2Fugd%2F4457e5_dbf1d4b8dde54864ab517d0334954c45.pdf%5C%22%3ETalk%20Politics%20to%20Me%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eunpacks%20the%20concept%20of%20Gendered%20Political%20Socialisation%2C%20which%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20complexities%20of%20gender%20disparities%20in%20political%20interest%20and%20its%20influence%20by%20factors%20such%20as%20family%2C%20social%20media%20and%20news%2C%20among%20other%20important%20insights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20mother%20of%20a%2014-year-old%20girl%20from%20New%20Delhi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20avoid%20discussing%20politics%20with%20her%20because%20of%20how%20badly%20it%20is%20covered%20in%20the%20news%20and%20its%20tendency%20to%20address%20issues%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20social%20justice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20girls%20may%20encounter%20perceived%20limitations%20in%20their%20political%20aspirations%20due%20to%20gender%20stereotypes%20and%20societal%20expectations.%20Conversely%2C%20boys%20may%20be%20encouraged%20or%20empowered%20to%20take%20risks%2C%20leadership%20roles%20and%20engage%20more%20actively%20in%20politics.%20Addressing%20such%20influences%20at%20an%20early%20age%20is%20crucial%20to%20foster%20inclusive%20political%20participation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20had%20a%20school%20trustee%20from%20Chennai%20tell%20us%20that%20a%20class%2010%20student%20from%20their%20school%20aspired%20to%20be%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20New%20Zealand%20as%20she%20saw%20Jacinda%20Adern%20as%20a%20role%20model.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20extremely%20sad%20that%20young%20girls%20in%20our%20country%20think%20it%20is%20more%20achievable%20to%20become%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20a%20country%20other%20than%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%2016-year-old%20girl%20who%20took%20our%20survey%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20the%20misconception%20that%20only%20men%20can%20be%20politicians%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20women%20don%E2%80%99t%20put%20a%20thought%20into%20becoming%20a%20politician.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%2017-year-old%20female%20respondent%20to%20our%20survey%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGetting%20nominated%20by%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20party%20members%20itself%20is%20difficult%20to%20begin%20with%20for%20a%20woman%20due%20to%20the%20general%20preconceived%20notion%20that%20a%20man%20does%20the%20job%20better%20without%20any%20emotional%20connect.%20People%20trust%20a%20man%20more%20than%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20position%20of%20power%20and%20they%20believe%20that%20a%20woman%20isn%E2%80%99t%20mentally%20strong%20enough%20to%20tackle%20issues%20and%20work%20on%20par%20with%20her%20male%20counterparts.%20Hence%2C%20even%20if%20nominated%2C%20getting%20the%20public%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20woman%20is%20difficult%20because%20of%20their%20low%20trust%20in%20a%20female%20figure%20of%20authority%20due%20to%20their%20stereotypical%20views%20and%20an%20inherently%20patriarchal%20mindset.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%2017-year-old%20male%20respondent%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20more%20difficult%20for%20female%20politicians%20to%20be%20successful%20since%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F69190%2Fyouth-india-org-social-activism-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eequal%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20men%20and%20even%20if%20they%20were%20to%20be%20on%20the%20same%20platform%2C%20Indians%2C%20including%20women%20themselves%2C%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20look%20at%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cinferior%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cweak%E2%80%9D%20compared%20to%20men.%E2%80%9D%20This%20sentiment%20was%20also%20echoed%20by%20another%2018-year-old%20male%20participant%20of%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20interesting%20part%20of%20the%20study%20was%20that%20our%20team%20of%20research%20volunteers%20consisted%20of%20young%20girls%20and%20women%20between%20ages%2015-%2021%2C%20who%20worked%20on%20the%20analysis%20of%20open-ended%20responses.%20This%20helped%20us%20identify%20trends%20in%20the%20responses%20of%20their%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20gears%20up%20for%20a%20general%20election%20in%202024%2C%20educators%2C%20the%20civil%20society%20and%20philanthropists%20must%20come%20together%20to%20create%20an%20enabling%20environment%20for%20future%20and%20first-time%20voters%20as%20we%20cannot%20have%20a%20truly%20functional%20democracy%20without%20the%20youths%E2%80%99%20participation%20and%20engagement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742-300x153.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742-500x255.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742-768x392.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742-150x77.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332517%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22612%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecommendations%20for%20parents%20and%20caregivers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20recommendations%20for%20what%20parents%2C%20schools%20and%20caregivers%20can%20do%20to%20increase%20political%20interest%20and%20engagement%20among%20adolescents%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreate%20safe%20spaces%20for%20dialogue%20on%20politics%20at%20home%20and%20school%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20found%20that%20youth%20had%20higher%20political%20engagement%20if%20their%20parents%20encouraged%20them%20to%20participate%20in%20politics.%20Young%20men%20are%20more%20likely%20than%20young%20women%20to%20be%20socialised%20by%20their%20parents%20and%20society%20to%20think%20about%20politics%20as%20a%20career%20