%20without%20skipping%20a%20beat.%20That%20day%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20just%20talk%E2%80%A6and%20the%20strength%20that%20lies%20in%20the%20power%20of%20listening%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2025%2C%20Raj%20Dagwar%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Listener%E2%80%99s%20Army%2C%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F129357%2Fcorporate-india-northeast-floods-caf%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20non-profit%20organisation%3C%2Fa%3E%20helping%20people%20deal%20with%20mental%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20what%20our%20name%20suggests%20%E2%80%94%20we%20listen.%20Our%20generation%20has%20been%20the%20most%20isolated%20and%20the%20best%20thing%20one%20can%20do%20is%20listen.%20If%20a%20person%20needs%20professional%20help%2C%20we%20refer%20them%20to%20our%20psychologists%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Raj.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98A%20dark%20pit%20that%20can%20swallow%20you%20whole%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20happy%20family%2C%20Raj%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331526%2Fpune-startup-innovates-ai-based-technology-screen-tuberculosis-within-seconds-innovation-in-healthcare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Pune%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20engineering%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Pune%20when%20things%20started%20to%20go%20downhill.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20a%20person%20and%20it%20did%20not%20work%20out.%20I%20was%20not%20doing%20good%20at%20college%20either.%20Suddenly%2C%20life%20felt%20hard%20and%20I%20felt%20alone%20in%20all%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20adding%20that%20he%20felt%20helpless.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%2