Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuffering%20silently%2C%20Raj%20could%20not%20communicate%20with%20either%20his%20friends%20or%20family%20about%20how%20he%20was%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20start%20feeling%20depressed%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20scary.%20It%20was%20very%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20talk%20about%20what%20I%20was%20feeling.%20When%20I%20did%20speak%20to%20my%20parents%2C%20they%20were%20not%20able%20to%20understand%20it.%20They%20would%20say%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98sir%20dard%20hai%20to%20dawai%20lele%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(if%20you%20have%20a%20headache%2C%20take%20medicine).%20It%20was%20very%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20understand%20that%20depression%20is%20different%20from%20physical%20illnesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20failed%20to%20get%20support%20from%20his%20parents%2C%20Raj%20says%20he%20became%20even%20more%20closed%20off.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20to%20keep%20to%20myself%20and%20my%20head%20would%20keep%20buzzing%20with%20thoughts%20of%20ending%20my%20life.%20I%20would%20always%20look%20at%20it%20as%20a%20relief%20from%20this%20silent%20suffering.%20Soon%20enough%2C%20thoughts%20of%20harming%20myself%20and%20suicide%20became%20stronger%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20professor%20in%20his%20college%20who%20noticed%20Raj%E2%80%99s%20behaviour%20and%20advised%20him%20to%20see%20the%20campus%20therapist.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315631%2Fbengaluru-punita-mittal-mahak-maheshwari-soulup-mental-health-online-support-platform%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseeing%20a%20therapist%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20like%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20for%20me%20as%20I%20had%20made%20up%20my%20mind%20that%20there%20was%20no%20end%20to%20the%20suffering.%20In%20that%20two-hour%20long%20session%2C%20I%20just%20vented%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20therapist%20was%20a%20great%20listener%20and%20he%20helped%20me%20realise%20that%20I%20have%20to%20talk%20through%20my%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20So%20Raj%20continued%20to%20visit%20the%20therapist%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317358%2Fmodel-dinesh-mohan-silver-fox-narrates-battle-with-eating-disorder-and-depression%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20fight%20depression%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFighting%20depression%20is%20not%20a%20linear%20journey%3B%20it%20is%20not%20like%20you%20are%20in%20and%20then%20out%20of%20it.%20It%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20relapses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98There%20is%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxasLGkv9Ni%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxasLGkv9Ni%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxasLGkv9Ni%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Listeners%20Army%20%7C%20Mental%20health%20%7C%20Lets%20talk%20(%40listeners_army)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20I%20was%20still%20in%20therapy%20and%20was%20trying%20my%20best%20to%20keep%20myself%20healthy.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20to%20help%20people%20like%20me%2C%20but%20I%20was%20not%20sure%20how%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20when%20Raj%20found%20a%20video%20on%20the%20internet.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20man%20who%20was%20paying%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20money%20to%20people%20to%20tell%20their%20stories.%20I%20decided%20to%20replicate%20the%20same%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20the%20world%20opened%20its%20doors%20again%20and%20Raj%20was%20back%20at%20his%20college%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20stand%20outside%20his%20college%20with%20a%20sign%20that%20read%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CTell%20me%20your%20story%20and%20I%20will%20give%20you%20Rs%2010.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20some%20out%20of%20curiosity%20and%20some%20out%20of%20their%20sheer%20need%20to%20talk.%20I%20also%20started%20to%20post%20about%20my%20initiative%20online%20on%20Instagram.%20Within%20a%20few%20days%2C%20I%20was%20flooded%20with%20DMs%20%5Bdirect%20messages%5D%20and%20requests%20from%20both%20people%20who%20wanted%20to%20talk%20and%20people%20who%20wanted%20to%20listen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20overwhelming%20response%20made%20Raj%20realise%20that%20his%20initiative%20could%20be%20converted%20into%20a%20forum%20of%20listeners.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20the%20Listener%E2%80%99s%20Army%20started.%20Today%20our%20non-profit%20is%20around%20600%20listeners%20strong%20who%20are%20all%20volunteers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20volunteers%20or%20listeners%20and%20the%20people%20who%20want%20to%20tell%20their%20stories%20are%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELending%20a%20compassionate%20ear%20to%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20a%20person%20can%20become%20a%20listener%2C%20Raj%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stories%20and%20incidents%20that%20people%20share%20can%20be%20quite%20taxing%20and%20overwhelming.%20This%20is%20why%20every%20person%20who%20wants%20to%20become%20a%20listener%20has%20to%20undergo%20a%20small%20evaluation%2C%20conducted%20by%20psychologists%20and%20therapists%20who%20collaborate%20with%20us.%20Once%20the%20volunteers%20are%20cleared%20by%20the%20therapist%2C%20we%20let%20them%20in%20our%20army%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22So%20far%2C%20Raj%20has%20amassed%20a%20following%20of%20more%20than%2018%2C000%20on%20Instagram.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-2-1697611990-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332492%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESo%20far%2C%20